\h Yosuwe
\toc3 YOS
\toc2 Yosuwe
\toc1 Taruku ta Yosuwe
\mt1 Yosuwe
\imt1 K…ôb…õr…õ: Toloku nt…õ Kanu k…ônaloku AŇčnabi Yosuwe m…Ē
\ip Moloku m…õlar…ôm teta k…ôtabu kaŇčk…õ, ancic…ôs taruku ta aka Yisrayel d…ôc…ôtabu c…ôlar…ôm disr…õ. D…ôTawureta Musa ancop. Afum ap…ĒŇč a Yisrayel, AŇčnabi Abraham, AŇčnabi Siyaka, AŇčnabi Yakuba, k…Ē awut …Ēn w…ôco k…Ē m…õr…ôŇč (12) f…ôp faŇčan d…ôk…ôtabu k…ôc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē ka Tawureta Musa aŇčn…ôŇčk pi, mp…õ aŇčwe ¬ęD…ôk…ôcop¬Ľ m…Ē. D…ôk…ôl…ôps…ôr da k…ôtabu kaŇčk…Ē dement…ôr su t…Ēk…Ē aka Yisrayel Ňčanab…ôp at…Ēf Ňča Misira m…Ē.
\ip K…ôtabu ka m…õr…ôŇč ka Tawureta Musa nk…õ aŇčwe ¬ęK…ôwur¬Ľ m…Ē, taruku ta AŇčnabi Musa …Ē toncop. K…Ē Kanu k…ôs…ĒŇč…õ k'aŇčkom k…Ē at…Ēf Ňča Misira, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ p…ôwur…õ afum a Yisrayel dacar m…Ē.
\ip Nt…õ aka Yisrayel Ňčancali K…ôba ka C…ôŇčk…Ēlma k…ômar ka mes m…õw…õy-w…õy mm…õ Kanu k…ônament…ôr m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčamb…õr…õ d…ôt…õgb…ôr…õ. At…Ēf Ňča KanaŇč Ňč…Ē Kanu k…ônafaŇč k…ôkek…ôr…õ Ňča, nde k…ônad…õrm…õ aYisrayel k…ôs…ĒŇč Ňča m…Ē. K…ôtabu ka maas ka Tawureta Musa ¬ęBuk ba AloŇčn…õ¬Ľ, ka maŇčk…ôl…õ ¬ęK…ôl…Ēm¬Ľ, k…Ē ka k…ôcam…ôt ¬ęSariy…õ sa M…õr…ôŇč¬Ľ, c…ôtabu canc…õ f…ôp c…ôloku teta mar…ônt ma aka Yisrayel nt…õ MARIKI k…ônawur…õ Ňča dacar nde Misira m…Ē. K…ôwon ka afum aka Yisrayel d…ôt…õgb…ôr…õ k…ônas…Ēt…Ē meren w…ôco maŇčk…ôl…õ a Ňčadeb…ôp at…Ēf Ňča KanaŇč. K…ôt…ĒlaŇč k…ôŇčan k…ônas…ĒŇč…õ Ňča k…ôwon di.
\ip Nt…õ Ňčanay…õf…õ k…ôcali k…ôŇčgb…Ēk…Ē ka Yurd…õn, Ňčab…õr…õ at…Ēf Ňča KanaŇč m…Ē, k…Ē Kanu k…ôloku aka Yisrayel a Yosuwe p…ôy…Ēn…õ Ňča w…ôkiriŇč d…ôk…ôc…ôm…õ da AŇčnabi Musa. K…Ē AŇčnabi Yosuwe …õncal…õn…õ Ňča k…ôŇčgb…Ēk…Ē ka Yurd…õn k…ômar ka mes m…õw…õy-w…õy ma Kanu, p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē Musa …õnacal…õn…õ Ňča K…ôba ka C…ôŇčk…Ēlma m…Ē.
\ip Nt…õ tat…Ēk…Ē tencep…ôr m…Ē, k…Ē AŇčnabi Yosuwe …õnt…õf…ôrn…õn…õ Ňča at…Ēf Ňča KanaŇč, Ňčak…Ē Ňčasut…õn…õ nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ Ňčas…Ēt…Ē t…Ēf yay…Ēk…Ē m…Ē. Kanu k…ônafaŇč k…ôs…ĒŇč Ňča t…Ēf yay…Ēk…Ē teta danapa daŇčan k…Ē k…ôd…õr…ôm k…ôŇčk…Ē …õnad…õrm…õ Ňča k…ôs…ĒŇč Ňča yi m…Ē. Ti disr…õ k…Ē Kanu k…ômar Ňča k…ôwan kaŇčk…Ē disr…õ haŇč k…Ē aKanaŇč f…ôp Ňčanes…õ Ňča. K…Ē cusuŇčka nc…õ w…ôco k…Ē m…õr…ôŇč ca Yisrayel f…ôp c…ôs…Ēt…Ē s…ôdare. K…Ē Kanu k…ôs…ĒŇč Ňča t…Ēf yay…Ēk…Ē y…Ēy…Ēn…õ Ňča k…õ.
\ip Taruku tant…õ f…ôp acic pi k…ôtabu kaŇčk…õ disr…õ, k…ôy…õf…õ t…õm nt…õ aka Yisrayel Ňčanacali k…ôŇčgb…Ēk…Ē ka Yurd…õn m…Ē, haŇč t…õm nt…õ Ňčanatam s…ôdare sa KanaŇč f…ôp m…Ē. Ti disr…õ aŇčn…ôŇčk f…ôn…Ēnt…ôr fa Kanu bel-bel. Kanu k…ômb…Ēt…ôr afum …Ēn. K…ôd…õr…ôm nk…õ o nk…õ k…ônd…õrm…õ Ňča m…Ē, k…ôŇčlas ki f…ôn…Ēnt…ôr k…Ē teta danapa daŇčan. Tat…Ēk…Ē t…ĒŇčy…Ēn…õ su totubucn…õ t…Ēt…Ēt. K…Ē s…ôna s…ôy…Ēn…õ s…Ē afum a Kanu-…õ, k…ôŇčmar…õ su f…ôn…Ēnt…ôr f…Ēn tecep…ôr…õn…õ tosu doru, p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē k…ônad…õrm…õ su m…Ē. Kanu k…ômar su, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ pane moloku mam…õ, palaŇč s…Ē mi m…Ē.
\ip Amina
\c 1
\s1 Kanu k…ôloku Yosuwe a p…ôb…õr…õ ant…Ēf Ňča k…õ nde KanaŇč
\p 
\v 1 Nt…õ defi da AŇčnabi Musa w…ôcar w…ôka Mariki dencep…ôr m…Ē, k…Ē Mariki oloku Yosuwe wan ka Nun w…ômar…ôs ka Musa:
\v 2 ¬ęW…ôcar kem Musa efi. Nd…õk…ôl oŇč m…ôy…õf…õ, m…ôcali k…ôŇčgb…Ēk…Ē ka Yurd…õn kaŇčk…õ, m…ôna k…Ē afum akaŇč…õ f…ôp. N…ôk…Ē nde at…Ēf nŇč…õ indes…ĒŇč aka Yisrayel m…Ē.
\v 3 Nn…Ē o nn…Ē m…ônc…ômb…ôr k…ôc…ôk m…Ē, is…ĒŇč un di p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē inaloku ti Musa m…Ē.
\v 4 C…ôl…ônc…ôr conu c…ôndey…õf…õ nde d…ôt…õgb…ôr…õ k…Ē LibaŇč dand…õ, haŇč nde k…ôŇčgb…Ēk…Ē k…ôp…ĒŇč ka ∆źf…ôrat, k…ôy…õf…õ ka at…Ēf Ňča aka Hitit, haŇč nde K…ôba K…ôp…ĒŇč ntende dec d…õŇčkal…õ m…Ē.
\v 5 Ali fum …Ēf…Ēc…ôm'am f…Ēr kiriŇč k…ôyi kam doru f…ôp. Isol'am p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē inasol…õ Musa m…Ē. If…Ēdesak …ôm, if…Ēc'am.
\v 6 M…ôyeŇčk dis, m…ôb…ôkn…õ! Bawo m…ôn'endek…Ēt…õn…õ afum a Yisrayel k…ôbaŇč at…Ēf Ňča k…õ nŇč…õ inad…õr…ôm k…ôs…ĒŇč atem aŇčan m…Ē.
\v 7 M…ôyeŇčk dis gbaŇč, m…ôb…ôkn…õ! M…ôgb…ôtn…õ m…ôk…Ēt sariy…õ ns…õ Musa w…ôcar kem omboc'am m…Ē: Ta m…ôgbaym…õ si k…ôca k…ôt…Ēt, ta m…ôgbaym…õ k…ôca k…ômeriya, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč'am k…ôtam mes f…ôp nn…Ē o nn…Ē m…ôŇčk…Ē m…Ē.
\v 8 Ta buk ba sariy…õ mb…õ b…Ēb…Ēl'am d…ôkusu! M…ôckaraŇč bi daŇč k…Ē pibi nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ m…ôgb…ôtn…õ, m…ôk…Ēt t…Ēk…Ē ancic buk bamb…õ disr…õ m…Ē, it…Ē m…ôŇčsoln…õ d…Ēp…Ē d…Ēt…Ēt, it'…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ m…ôtam mes f…ôp.
\v 9 Ind…õm f'am: M…ôyeŇčk dis, m…ôb…ôkn…õ ba? Awa, ta m…ônes…õ, ta dis d…Ēl…Ēl …ôm, bawo Mariki, Kanu kam k…ôsol'am nn…Ē o nn…Ē m…ôŇčk…Ē m…Ē.¬Ľ
\s1 Yosuwe k…ôlomp…ôs k…Ēn k…ôcali ka Yurd…õn
\p 
\v 10 K…Ē Yosuwe osom ti akiriŇč:
\v 11 ¬ęN…ôk…Ēt afan disr…õ f…ôp, n…ôloku afum nt…õ: ‚ÄĻN…ôd…õmn…õ yeri, bawo mata maas m…õnc…ôm…õ k…ôcali ka Yurd…õn yay…õ, n…ôk…ĒbaŇč at…Ēf nŇč…õ Mariki, Kanu konu k…ôs…ĒŇč un m…Ē.‚Äļ¬Ľ
\v 12 K…Ē Yosuwe oloku aRuben, aKadu k…Ē aka kusuŇčka dac…Ē ka Manase:
\v 13 N…ôm…õŇčk…ôrn…õ d…ôs…ôbomp t…Ēk…Ē Musa w…ôcar ka Mariki …õnasom'un m…Ē, p…ôcloku: ¬ęMariki, Kanu konu k…ôs…ĒŇč'un k…ôŇčes…ôm, k…ôs…ĒŇč un at…Ēf nŇč…õ.¬Ľ
\v 14 Aran anu, awut anu, k…Ē y…Ēc…Ēl yonu yendeyi at…Ēf nŇč…õ Musa …Ēs…ĒŇč un nde Yurd…õn k…ôs…ôk ntende dec d…õmp…õ m…Ē. Mba n…ôna arkun aŇč…õ n…ôŇčy…õf…ôr…õn…õ n…ôt…Ēmp…ôr yosutn…õn…õ yonu m…Ē, n…ôn'endek…ĒnuŇčk…õn…õ k…ôcali k…ôŇčgb…Ēk…Ē. N…ômar aw…õnc un aŇča,
\v 15 haŇč Mariki p…ôs…ĒŇč aw…õnc un aŇča k…ôŇčes…ôm p…ôm…Ē n…ôna, Ňča s…Ē Ňčas…Ēt…Ē at…Ēf nŇč…õ Mariki, Kanu konu k…ôs…ĒŇč Ňča m…Ē. K…Ē telip-…õ, n…ôluks…ôrn…õ n…ôder n…ôl…õk at…Ēf Ňča k…õ nŇč…õ Ňč…Ēy…Ēn…õ Ňčonu m…Ē. Musa w…ôcar ka Mariki …Ēs…ĒŇč un Ňči Yurd…õn k…ôca k…ôŇčk…Ē ntende dec d…õmp…õ m…Ē.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 16 K…Ē Ňčaloku Yosuwe: ¬ęS…ôndey…Ē nt…õ o nt…õ m…ôŇčsom su m…Ē: S…ôndek…Ē s…Ē nn…Ē o nn…Ē m…ôndekek…ôr…õ su m…Ē.
\v 17 S…ôndec…ôŇčk…ôl'…ôm p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē s…ônac…ôŇčk…ôl Musa m…Ē. Tes tin gb…ôc…ôr…ôm t…õbas su: Mariki, Kanu kam k…ôsol'am p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē k…ônasol…õ Musa m…Ē!
\v 18 Nw…õ o nw…õ endetaŇč…ôr'…ôm al…ôŇč…ôs, p…ôyeŇčk…ôr dim dam domp m…Ē, andif k…Ē. M…ôyeŇčk dis gbaŇč, m…ôb…ôkn…õ!
\c 2
\s1 Yosuwe k…ôsom k…Ēn afum m…õr…ôŇč Yeriko
\p 
\v 1 K…Ē Yosuwe wan ka Nun osom afum m…õr…ôŇč dim dant…Ēf k…ôy…õf…õ ka Sitim, p…ôcloku Ňča: ¬ęN…ôk…Ē, n…ôk…Ēkc…õ ant…Ēf ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē k…Ē dare da Yeriko! K…Ē afum akak…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē Ňčab…õr…õ nde k…ôl…Ē ka w…ôran w…ôyamayama, pacwe k…Ē Rahab, k…Ē Ňčancep…ôr…õn…õ pibi nde nd…Ēr…Ēn.
\v 2 K'aloku w…ôb…õ ka Yeriko: ¬ęAwa, n…ôgb…ôtn…õ nt…õ arkun aka Yisrayel Ňčanderna nn…Ē pibi k…ôdefen-feni at…Ēf Ňčosu m…Ē!¬Ľ
\v 3 K…Ē w…ôb…õ w…ôka Yeriko osom pak…Ēloku Rahab: ¬ęM…ôwur…õn…õ afum ak…Ē Ňčayi nn…Ē ndaram m…Ē, aŇč…õ Ňčamb…õr…õ nde k…ôl…Ē kam m…Ē, bawo k…ôfen-feni ka at…Ēf f…ôp k…Ē Ňčander…õn…õ.¬Ľ
\v 4 K…Ē w…ôran nw…õ eŇčkek…ôr…õ arkun aŇč…õ m…õr…ôŇč k'…ĒŇčk…Ē p…ôm…õŇčk, k'oloku asom a w…ôb…õ: ¬ęKance k…Ē, arkun aŇč…õ m…õr…ôŇč Ňčandersa nn…Ē k…ôl…Ē kem, mba inc…ôr…õsa f…õ aka nn…Ē Ňčay…Ēn…õ m…Ē.
\v 5 Nendisna t…õm nt…õ dec d…õŇčkal…õsa pack…Ē k…ôgb…ôt kumba ka dare d…ôkusu m…Ē, k…Ē arkun aŇč…õ Ňčawur nn…Ē, mba inc…ôr…õ f…õ nde ŇčaŇčk…Ēsa m…Ē. N…ôb…õlk…ôr n…ôc…ôm…õ Ňča dar…ôŇč, n…ôŇčk…Ēb…ôp Ňča!¬Ľ
\v 6 Nt…õ t…õnayi m…Ē, …õnap…õn…õ Ňča nde k…ôl…Ē darenc, k'…õm…õŇčk Ňča nde sek ya c…ôŇčk…Ēlma dac…Ē, nc…õ …õnad…õt nde k…ôl…Ē darenc m…Ē.
\v 7 K…Ē afum Ňčasump…ôr d…Ēp…Ē da Yurd…õn k…ôb…õl…ôr Ňča haŇč nde d…ôk…ôt…ônta. K'aŇčgb…ôt kumba ka dare d…ôkusu nt…õ afum ab…õl…ôr aŇčan Ňčanawur m…Ē.
\p 
\v 8 Ta acik…ôra at…õn mes Ňčantadir…õ-…õ, k…Ē Rahab …õmp…õ k…ôk…Ēb…ôp Ňča nde k…ôl…Ē darenc.
\v 9 K…Ē w…ôran nw…õ oloku arkun aŇč…õ: ¬ęInc…ôr…õ a Mariki …Ēs…ĒŇč un at…Ēf ŇčaŇč…õ. P…ôl…õc p…Ēk…Ē n…ôfaŇč…õ su m…Ē p…Ēs…Ēt…Ē su, ayek-yek Ňč…õŇčgb…ôp…ôrn…õ afum f…ôp, Ňčayi k…ônes'on.
\v 10 Bawo s…ône a Mariki k…ônawos…ôr'on domun da K…ôba ka C…ôŇčk…Ēlma nt…õ n…ônawur Misira m…Ē. S…ône s…Ē t…Ēk…Ē n…ônadif ab…õ a Am…Ēr m…õr…ôŇč aŇč…õ Ňčanayi k…ôŇčgb…Ēk…Ē ka Yurd…õn k…ôs…ôk ntende dec d…õmp…õ m…Ē: Sih…ĒŇč k…Ē Oku.
\v 11 S…ône ti, it…Ē mim mowur…õ su, k…Ē nw…õ o nw…õ eŇčgbiŇč kifir nn…Ē n…ôyi m…Ē, bawo Mariki, Kanu konu, k…ôy…Ēn…õ Kanu ka darenc, k…Ē d…ônt…Ēf.
\v 12 Nd…õk…ôl oŇč, n…ôd…õrm'em nn…Ē Mariki eyi m…Ē, a m…ôndelas…õ afum a k…ôl…Ē kem layidi p…ôm…Ē d…Ēk…Ē iy…Ēn'on m…Ē. N…ôs…ĒŇč im paka mp…õ pendes…ĒŇč em k…ôlaŇč a n…ôntiŇčk…ôr f'em m…Ē.
\v 13 A n…ôndesak iya kem, papa kem, aw…õnc im aŇča arkun, aran, k…Ē afum alp…ôs aŇč…õ Ňčay…Ēn…õ ak…ôŇčan m…Ē f…ôp. N…ôsak su s…ômulp…ôr defi, n…ôf…Ēdedif su.¬Ľ
\v 14 K…Ē arkun aŇč…õ Ňčaloku w…ôran nw…õ: ¬ęS…ôwos…õ k…ôfin…õ tetam, mba ta m…ôdeloku afum t…Ēk…Ēt…õn…õ tosu de! K…Ē Mariki k…ôndes…ĒŇč su at…Ēf-…õ, s…ôndeb…Ēt mera s…ôlas…õn…õ s…Ē layidi nn…Ē m…ôyi m…Ē.¬Ľ
\v 15 K'…Ēs…ĒŇč Ňča k…ôb…ônda k…Ē Ňčantor…õn…õ ki nde d…ôwund…õr, bawo k…ôl…Ē k…Ēn k…ônayi disr…õ k…ôgb…ôc…õn…õ k…Ē damba da saŇčka sa dare.
\v 16 K…Ē w…ôran nw…õ oloku Ňča: ¬ęN…ôk…Ē ta d…ôm…Ēr…Ē k…Ē p…ôyi f…õ ti-…õ, n…ômb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē ab…õl…ôr anu. N…ôgb…Ēpn…õ d…ôndo haŇč mata maas, t…õnt…ôŇčn…õ ab…õl…ôr anu Ňčalukus, a n…ôna n…ôdesump…ôr d…Ēp…Ē donu k…ôk…Ē!¬Ľ
\v 17 K…Ē arkun aŇč…õ Ňčaloku k…Ē: ¬ęNt…õ tendes…ĒŇč…õ su k…ôlas k…ôd…õr…ôm nk…õ m…ôs…ĒŇč…õ su k…ôd…õrm'am m…Ē:
\v 18 Awa, m…ôc…ôŇčk…ôl im! T…õm nt…õ s…ôndeb…õr…õ dare m…Ē, m…õn…õ m…ôkot…ôr taf…ôc peyim nde wund…õr w…Ēk…Ē m…ônator…õn…õ su m…Ē. M…ôc…ômb…ôr…ôrn…õ iya w…ôkam, papa w…ôkam, aw…õnc'…ôm aŇča arkun aran, afum am f…ôp nde k…ôl…Ē kam.
\v 19 Nw…õ o nw…õ …õncali kusuŇčka kaŇčk…Ē a p…ôwur m…Ē, …õsar…õ teta mecir m…Ēn, k…Ē s…ôna, s…ônc…ôr…õ f…õ! Mba kaŇčk…Ē pagbuŇč…õn…õ w…ôkin nu dac…Ē nde k…Ēl…Ē kam disr…õ-…õ, s…ôsar…õ teta mecir ma w…ôkayi!
\v 20 K…Ē m…ôloku afum t…Ēk…Ēt…õn…õ tosu-…õ, t…õm tat…Ēk…Ē s…ôŇčsikili t…õt…ôŇčn…õ tosu k…Ē m…ôna.¬Ľ
\v 21 K…Ē w…ôran nw…õ oloku: ¬ęKanu k…ôs…ĒŇč…õ teyi p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē n…ôloku ti m…Ē!¬Ľ K…Ē w…ôran nw…õ …õsak arkun aŇč…õ k…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē. K…Ē w…ôran nw…õ oŇčkot taf…ôc p…ôyim nde wund…õr w…Ēn.
\p 
\v 22 K…Ē arkun aŇč…õ ŇčaŇčk…Ē ta d…ôm…Ēr…Ē, k…Ē ŇčaŇčgb…Ēpn…õ di mata maas, haŇč k…Ē ab…õl…ôs aŇčan Ňčalukus. Ab…õl…ôr aŇčan Ňčact…õn Ňča d…Ēp…Ē, mba Ňčanan…ôŇčk f…õ Ňča.
\v 23 K…Ē afum aŇč…õ m…õr…ôŇč Ňčande Ňčator d…ôm…Ēr…Ē, k…Ē Ňčancali Yurd…õn. K…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē Ňčab…ôp Yosuwe wan ka Nun, k…Ē Ňčal…Ēm…ôr k…Ē t…Ēk…Ē Ňčanas…Ēt…Ē nde anasom Ňča m…Ē.
\v 24 K…Ē Ňčaloku Yosuwe: ¬ęP…ôwur…õn…õ p…ôm…Ē Mariki …Ēs…ĒŇč su at…Ēf ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē f…ôp. Ayek-yek Ňč…õŇčgb…ôp…ôrn…õ afum f…ôp, Ňčayi k…ônes…õ su.¬Ľ
\c 3
\s1 K…ôcali ka Yurd…õn
\p 
\v 1 Yosuwe …õy…õf…õ b…ôtb…ôt suy, nk…Ēn k…Ē aka Yisrayel f…ôp, k…Ē Ňčay…õf…õ Sitim k…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē haŇč k…ôŇčgb…Ēk…Ē ka Yurd…õn. D…ôndo Ňčayekti saŇčka, k…Ē Ňčandir…õ di, Ňčantacali f…õ k…ôr…õsna.
\v 2 Tataka ta maas, k'akiriŇč ŇčaŇčk…Ēt…õn…õ d…ôsaŇčka f…ôp.
\v 3 K…Ē Ňčaloku afum nt…õ: ¬ęK…Ē n…ônden…ôŇčk kaŇčk…ôra ka danapa da Mariki, Kanu konu, aloŇčn…õ aLewy aŇč…õ ŇčagbaŇčn…õ ki-…õ, n…ôy…õf…õ nde n…ôyi m…Ē, n…ôc…ôm…õ ki dar…ôŇč.
\v 4 Mba n…ôb…Ēl…õn…õ ki cururu wul m…õr…ôŇč, ta n…ôl…Ēt…ôrn…õ ki de! T…õm tat…Ēk…Ē, n…ônc…ôr…õ d…Ēp…Ē d…Ēk…Ē p…ômar a n…ôk…Ē m…Ē, bawo n…ôntacep…ôr f…õ d…Ēp…Ē dand…õ t…Ēc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 5 K…Ē Yosuwe oloku afum: ¬ęN…ôs…Ēk…ôsn…õ, bawo Mariki k…ôŇčy…Ē alna mes m…Ēp…ĒŇč nn…Ē n…ôyi m…Ē.¬Ľ
\v 6 K…Ē Yosuwe oloku aloŇčn…õ: ¬ęN…ôl…õk kaŇčk…ôra k…ôs…õl…õŇč ka danapa da Kanu nk…õ n…ôgbaŇčn…õ, n…ôcep…ôr afum f…Ēr kiriŇč.¬Ľ K…Ē aloŇčn…õ Ňčal…õk kaŇčk…ôra, k…Ē Ňčancep…ôr afum f…Ēr kiriŇč.
\p 
\v 7 K…Ē Mariki oloku Yosuwe: ¬ęM…Ēk…Ē incop k…ôlel…ôs'…ôm nn…Ē afum aka Yisrayel Ňčayi m…Ē, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ Ňčac…ôr…õ a indesol am, p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē inasol…õ Musa m…Ē.
\v 8 K…Ē m…ôna, m…ôsom aloŇčn…õ aŇč…õ ŇčaŇčgbaŇčn…õ kaŇčk…ôra k…ôs…õl…õŇč ka danapa Kanu m…Ē nt…õ: K…Ē n…ôŇčk…Ēb…ôp k…ôŇčgb…Ēk…Ē ka Yurd…õn-…õ, n…ôc…ômb…ôr…ôs domun disr…õ.¬Ľ
\v 9 K…Ē Yosuwe oloku aka Yisrayel: ¬ęN…ôc…ĒŇčn…õ nn…Ē, n…ôc…ôŇčk…ôl moloku ma Mariki, Kanu konu!¬Ľ
\v 10 K…Ē Yosuwe oloku: ¬ęNt…õ t…Ē n…ôndec…ôr…õ a Kanu K…ôp…ĒŇč k…ôy'un dac…Ē, ki k…ôŇčk…Ēb…õl…ôs nu f…Ēr kiriŇč aka KanaŇč, aHit, aHiwy, aPerisi, aKirkasa, aka Am…Ēr, k…Ē aYebus.
\v 11 Awa n…ôgb…ôtn…õ nt…õ: KaŇčk…ôra k…ôs…õl…õŇč ka danapa da Mariki ma doru f…ôp k…ôndecali k…ôŇčgb…Ēk…Ē ka Yurd…õn f…Ēr yonu kiriŇč m…Ē.
\v 12 Nd…õk…ôl oŇč n…ôl…õk afum w…ôco k…Ē m…õr…ôŇč cusuŇčka ca Yisrayel disr…õ, fum w…ôkin kusuŇčka o kusuŇčka.
\v 13 K…Ē aloŇčn…õ aŇč…õ ŇčagbaŇčn…õ kaŇčk…ôra k…ôs…õl…õŇč ka danapa da Mariki, Mariki ma doru f…ôp Ňčanadegb…ôt w…õc…ôk domun da Yurd…õn, k…Ē domun da Yurd…õn deŇčgbint…ôr, k…Ē s…ôbo s…ôsak k…ôtor…õ domun, k…Ē doŇčloŇčkan…õ tofo tin.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 14 Nt…õ afum Ňčanawur d…ôc…ôbal k…ôk…Ēcali k…ôŇčgb…Ēk…Ē ka Yurd…õn m…Ē, aloŇčn…õ agbaŇčn…õ kaŇčk…ôra k…ôs…õl…õŇč ka danapa da Kanu m…Ē Ňčancep…ôr afum f…Ēr kiriŇč.
\v 15 Nt…õ agbaŇčn…õ kaŇčk…ôra k…ôs…õl…õŇč Ňčamb…ôp Yurd…õn k…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ētor…õ w…õc…ôk d…ôromun m…Ē, k…Ē Yurd…õn yompurur c…ôŇčgb…Ēk…Ē c…ôk…Ē kat…õla kaŇčk…Ē f…ôp
\v 16 k…Ē domun nd…õ d…õŇčy…õf…õ d…ôs…ôbo m…Ē d…õnc…ôm…õ, k…Ē doloŇčkan…õ k…ôfo kin p…ôbolu p…ôm…Ē aboŇč…ôn ntende dare da Adam nŇč…õ Ňčeyi CartaŇč k…ôs…ôk, k…Ē d…Ēk…Ē dontor k…ôca ka k…ôba ka Araba, k…ôba K…ôdok…ôt, k…Ē s…ôbo sas…Ēk…Ē f…ôp s…ôncop…ôr domun. K…Ē afum Ňčancali k…ôŇčgb…Ēk…Ē Ňčat…õf…ôrn…õ dare da Yeriko.
\v 17 AloŇčn…õ aŇč…õ ŇčanagbaŇčn…õ kaŇčk…ôra k…ôs…õl…õŇč ka danapa da Marki m…Ē Ňčac…ôm…õ ant…Ēf Ňčowosu f…ôr k…ôroŇč k…ôŇčgb…Ēk…Ē ka Yurd…õn dac…Ē. K…Ē afum a Yisrayel f…ôp Ňčalip k…ôcali k…ôŇčgb…Ēk…Ē ant…Ēf Ňčowosu k…ôroŇč.
\c 4
\s1 Aka Yisrayel Ňčanc…ômb…ôr masar p…ôy…Ēn…õ t…õn…õp…ôl…õ taŇčan ta k…ôcali ka Yurd…õn
\p 
\v 1 Nt…õ afum a Yisrayel f…ôp Ňčalip k…ôcali Yurd…õn m…Ē, k…Ē MARIKI k…ôloku Yosuwe:
\v 2 ¬ęM…ôy…õk-y…õk at…õmp w…ôco k…Ē m…õr…ôŇč afum dac…Ē, kusuŇčka o kusuŇčka fum w…ôkin.
\v 3 M…ôloku Ňča: ‚ÄĻN…ôk…Ē n…ôl…õk masar w…ôco k…Ē m…õr…ôŇč nde ant…Ēf Ňčowosu f…ôr k…ôŇčgb…Ēk…Ē ka Yurd…õn dac…Ē, k…ôfo nk…õ aloŇčn…õ Ňčanc…ôm…õ m…Ē. N…ôl…õk mi n…ôk…õr…õ n…ôk…Ē n…ôboc mi nde k…ôfo nk…õ n…ôndenacep…ôr…õn…õ pibi m…Ē.‚Äļ¬Ľ
\v 4 K…Ē Yosuwe ewe afum aŇč…õ w…ôco k…Ē m…õr…ôŇč aŇč…õ anay…õk-y…õk aka Yisrayel dac…Ē m…Ē, kusuŇčka o kusuŇčka fum w…ôkin.
\v 5 K…Ē Yosuwe oloku Ňča: ¬ęN…ôcep…ôr kaŇčk…ôra ka danapa da MARIKI Kanu konu f…Ēr kiriŇč, n…ôsoln…õ c…ôr k…ôk…Ē ka Yurd…õn dac…Ē, nw…õ o nw…õ p…ôgbaŇčn…õ tasar tin, k…ôl…Ēm ka cusuŇčka ca Yisrayel,
\v 6 nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ t…Ēy…Ēn…õ t…õn…õp…ôl…õ tonu m…Ē. K…Ē awut anu Ňčandeyif un d…Ēs…Ēk d…Ēl…Ēma-…õ: ‚ÄĻAke masar mam…õ m…õfaŇč k…ôloku su-…õ?‚Äļ
\v 7 n…ôloku Ňča f…Ē domun da Yurd…õn d…õnacop…ôr f…Ēr ya kaŇčk…ôra ka danapa da MARIKI kiriŇč nt…õ k…ônccali Yurd…õn m…Ē, k…Ē k…ôŇčgb…Ēk…Ē ka Yurd…õn k…ôncop…õ domun. Masar mam…õ mende k…ôcc…õm-c…õm…ôs aka Yisrayel doru o doru.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 8 K'aka Yisrayel Ňčay…Ē t…Ēk…Ē Yosuwe …õnaloku Ňča m…Ē. K…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē Ňčal…õk masar w…ôco k…Ē m…õr…ôŇč nde k…ôŇčgb…Ēk…Ē ka Yurd…õn dac…Ē p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē MARIKI k…ônaloku ti Yosuwe m…Ē, k…ôl…Ēm ka cusuŇčka ca aYisrayel. K…Ē Ňčal…õk masar mam…Ēk…Ē k…Ē Ňčancal…õn…õ nde Ňčanac…ômb…ôr c…ôbal k…ôr…õsna m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčamboc.
\v 9 K…Ē Yosuwe omboc s…Ē masar w…ôco k…Ē m…õr…ôŇč k…ôŇčgb…Ēk…Ē ka Yurd…õn dac…Ē, k…ôfo nk…õ aloŇčn…õ agbaŇčn…õ a kaŇčk…ôra ka danapa Ňčanac…ômb…ôr w…õc…ôk m…Ē. Masar mam…Ēk…Ē m…Ēs…Ēr…Ēyi di haŇč m…Ēk…Ē.
\p 
\v 10 AloŇčn…õ aŇč…õ ŇčanagbaŇčn…õ kaŇčk…ôra k…ôs…õl…õŇč m…Ē, Ňčanacep…õ f…õ d…ôk…ôc…ôm…õ daŇčan k…ôŇčgb…Ēk…Ē ka Yurd…õn disr…õ haŇč k…Ē aka Yisrayel Ňčalip k…ôy…Ē ka t…Ēk…Ē MARIKI k…ônasom Yosuwe a p…ôloku Ňča m…Ē, k…Ē Yosuwe …Ēy…Ē mes f…ôp p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē Musa …õnasom k…Ē ti m…Ē. K…Ē aka Yisrayel Ňčamb…õlk…ôr k…ôcali.
\v 11 Nt…õ afum f…ôp Ňčalip k…ôcali m…Ē, kaŇčk…ôra ka MARIKI k…Ē aloŇčn…õ ak…Ē ŇčanagbaŇčn…õ ki m…Ē Ňčancali s…Ē, k…Ē Ňčancep…ôr s…Ē afum kiriŇč.
\v 12 K…Ē aka Yisrayel al…Ēma aka cusuŇčka ca Ruben, Kadu k…Ē kusuŇčka dac…Ē ka Manase Ňčancep…ôr aka Yisrayel kiriŇč p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē Musa …õnaloku Ňča ti m…Ē.
\v 13 Antam k…ôloku f…Ē d…Ēs…Ēk dad…Ēk…Ē as…Ēdar m…õc…ôp w…ôco maŇčk…ôl…õ, at…Ēmp…ôr yosutn…õn…õ Ňčancep…ôr MARIKI kiriŇč, Ňčalip k…ôlomp…ôsn…õ k…ôk…Ēsut…õn…õ, nde aranta Ňča Yurd…õn.
\v 14 D…Ēs…Ēk dad…Ēk…Ē, k…Ē MARIKI k…ômb…õk…ôs Yosuwe aka Yisrayel f…ôp dac…Ē, k…Ē Ňčalel…ôs k…Ē p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē Ňčanalel…ôs Musa kiyi k…Ēn doru f…ôp m…Ē.
\p 
\v 15 K…Ē MARIKI k…ôloku Yosuwe:
\v 16 ¬ęM…ôloku aloŇčn…õ aŇč…õ ŇčagbaŇčn…õ kaŇčk…ôra nk…õ k…ôy…Ē sariy…õ ns…õ s…ôd…õrm…õn…õ danapa dosu m…Ē, Ňčap…õn…õ ki Yurd…õn.¬Ľ
\v 17 K…Ē Yosuwe oloku aloŇčn…õ: ¬ęN…ôp…õ Yurd…õn!¬Ľ
\v 18 Nt…õ aloŇčn…õ agbaŇčn…õ a kaŇčk…ôra ka danapa da MARIKI Ňčanadep…õ k…ôŇčgb…Ēk…Ē ka Yurd…õn k…Ē ŇčandeŇč w…õc…ôk d…ôp…ôwosu m…Ē, k…Ē domun da k…ôŇčgb…Ēk…Ē ka Yurd…õn doncop s…Ē k…ôk…Ēt s…ôbo sayi p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē m…õnc ma fraŇčsuwa m…õŇčy…õf…õ m…Ē.
\v 19 K…Ē afum Ňčancali Yurd…õn tataka ta w…ôco ta Ňčof Ňč…Ēc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē, k…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē Ňčayekti saŇčka nde Kilkal, ntende dec d…õmp…õ Yeriko m…Ē.
\p 
\v 20 Masar w…ôco k…Ē m…õr…ôŇč mm…õ Ňčanal…õk k…ôŇčgb…Ēk…Ē ka Yurd…õn disr…õ m…Ē, k…Ē Yosuwe …õnc…ômb…ôr mi Kilkal.
\p 
\v 21 K…Ē Yosuwe oloku aka Yisrayel: ¬ęAlna k…Ē awut anu Ňčandeyif un: ‚ÄĻMasar ma ake m…Ē mam…õ-…õ?‚Äļ
\v 22 n…ôcloku Ňča f…Ē: ‚ÄĻAka Yisrayel Ňčanacali k…ôŇčgb…Ēk…Ē ka Yurd…õn k…ôwos…ôr domun.‚Äļ
\v 23 MARIKI Kanu konu k…ônawos…ôr…õ nu domun da k…ôŇčgb…Ēk…Ē ka Yurd…õn haŇč k…Ē aka Yisrayel Ňčalip k…ôcali p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē MARIKI Kanu konu k…ônay…Ēn…õ su ti K…ôba ka C…ôŇčk…Ēlma haŇč k…Ē s…ôncali ki m…Ē.
\v 24 Ti tendes…ĒŇč…õ afum a doru f…ôp k…ôc…ôr…õ a k…ôca ka MARIKI k…ôy…Ē f…ôn…Ēnt…ôr. T…Ēs…ĒŇč'on s…Ē k…ônes…õ MARIKI Kanu konu kiyi konu doru f…ôp.¬Ľ
\c 5
\p 
\v 1 Nt…õ ab…õ a Am…Ēr f…ôp aŇč…õ Ňčayi ntende dec d…õŇčkal…õ Yurd…õn m…Ē, k…Ē ab…õ aKanaŇč aŇč…õ Ňčayi agb…õp Ňča K…ôba K…ôp…ĒŇč m…Ē, Ňčane a MARIKI k…ônawos…ôs…ôr…õ aka Yisrayel k…ôŇčgb…Ēk…Ē ka Yurd…õn haŇč k…Ē Ňčancali ki, b…ôk…ôc y…Ēf…Ēr f…õ Ňča s…Ē, k…Ē Ňčanes…õ aka Yisrayel p…ôp…ĒŇč.
\p 
\v 2 T…õm tat…Ēk…Ē k…Ē MARIKI k…ôloku Yosuwe: ¬ęM…ôpat s…ôfaka sa masar, k…Ē t…õy…õf…õ d…ônda-…õ, m…ôk…ônc aka Yisrayel.¬Ľ
\v 3 K…Ē Yosuwe …õmpat…õn…õ s…ôfaka sa masar, k'…õŇčk…ônc aka Yisrayel nde T…Ēr…Ē ta C…ôrot.
\v 4 Nt…õ t…õnas…ĒŇč…õ Yosuwe p…ôk…ônc…õ Ňča: Nt…õ afum a Yisrayel Ňčancwur Misira m…Ē, arkun abeki f…ôp, aŇč…õ Ňčanctam k…ôsut…õn…õ m…Ē anak…ônc Ňča, mba afum akak…Ē f…ôp Ňčanafi nde d…ôt…õgb…ôr…õ, nt…õ Ňčanck…Ēt m…Ē. Awut arkun aŇč…õ anakom oŇč t…õlp…ôs m…Ē, Ňčanat…Ēk…ônc, it…Ē Yosuwe …õnak…ônc…õ Ňča.
\v 5 Arkun aŇč…õ Ňčanay…õf…õ Misira m…Ē f…ôp anak…ônc Ňča, mba awut arkun aŇč…õ anakom d…ôt…õgb…ôr…õ d…Ēp…Ē nt…õ Ňčanawur Misira Ňčanck…Ēt m…Ē, anak…ônc f…õ akak…Ē ali w…ôkin.
\v 6 Aka Yisrayel Ňčanak…Ēt meren w…ôco maŇčk…ôl…õ d…ôt…õgb…ôr…õ, haŇč afum ak…Ē Ňčanatam k…ôsut…õn…õ nt…õ Ňčancy…õf…õ Misira m…Ē Ňčalip k…ôfi d…Ēp…Ē, bawo Ňčanac…ôŇčk…ôl f…õ dim da MARIKI. MARIKI k…ônad…õr…ôm k…ôt…Ē-s…ĒŇč…õ Ňča k…ôn…ôŇčk ant…Ēf nŇč…õ Ňč…õŇčgb…ôl…ôr m…õs…õ ma wana k…Ē m…õs…õ ma c…ôme haŇč moctoŇč, Ňč…Ēk…Ē nk…Ēn MARIKI k…ônad…õr…ôm k…ôs…ĒŇč ka atem aŇčan m…Ē.
\v 7 Awut aŇčan Ňčanab…õk oŇč k…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē Ňčand…õ d…ôk…ônd…õ daŇčan. K…Ē Yosuwe …õŇčk…ônc Ňča, bawo anak…ônc f…õ Ňča d…Ēp…Ē.
\v 8 Nt…õ alip k…ôk…ônc ka afum f…ôp m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčand…õ d…ôndo d…ôsaŇčka haŇč k…Ē Ňčantamn…õ.
\p 
\v 9 K…Ē MARIKI k…ôloku Yosuwe: ¬ęM…Ēk…Ē, imbiŇčk…ôli malap monu ma Misira k'imb…Ēl…õn'on.¬Ľ It…Ē as…Ēr…Ēwen…õ k…ôfo kaŇčk…Ē Kilkal\f + \fr 5:9 \fq Kilkal\ft = c…ôHeb…ôru ¬ęk…ôbiŇčk…ôli.¬Ľ\f* haŇč m…Ēk…Ē.
\s1 K…ôsata ka Pak p…Ēc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē nde KanaŇč
\p 
\v 10 K…Ē aka Yisrayel Ňčand…õ Kilkal k…Ē Ňčamboc di k…ôsata ka Pak tataka ta w…ôco k…Ē maŇčk…ôl…õ ta Ňčof, dec d…Ēr…Ēf…Ēy, nde aranta Ňča Yeriko.
\v 11 D…Ēck…Ēs…Ēk da Pak k…Ē Ňčandi yeri ya d…Ēt…Ēf, c…ôcom nc…õ ant…Ēn…ĒŇčk…ôl lebin m…Ē, k…Ē m…õŇčgb…õn m…õkak…ôl.
\v 12 K…Ē c…ôcom nc…õ ancwe ¬ęman¬Ľ m…Ē c…ôsak k…ôwur d…Ēck…Ēs…Ēk nd…õ Ňčanadi yeri ya d…Ēt…Ēf m…Ē. K…ôren kaŇčk…Ē aka Yisrayel Ňčasak k…ôdi man, mba Ňčacdi oŇč yeri ya at…Ēf Ňča KanaŇč.
\s1 Yosuwe k…ôb…ôp…ôn…õ k…Ēn k…Ē w…ôkiriŇč w…ôka as…Ēdar a MARIKI
\p 
\v 13 D…Ēs…Ēk d…Ēl…Ēma Yosuwe p…ôl…Ēt…ôrn…õ Yeriko, k'…õmp…õn…õ f…Ēr darenc, k'…Ēm…Ēm…ôn, k…Ē fum owur k'…õnc…ôm…õ k…Ē f…Ēr kiriŇč, p…ôwur…õ dakma d…Ēn dobom p…ôt…Ēmp…ôr. K…Ē Yosuwe …Ēl…Ēt…ôrn…õ k…Ē, k'eyif k…Ē: ¬ęS…ôna Ňč…Ē m…ôyin…õ ba, ka ater…õn…õ asu Ňč…Ē m…ôyin…õ-…õ?¬Ľ
\v 14 K…Ē fum w…ôkak…Ē oloku: ¬ęAla, f…Ēt…Ē in…Ēy…Ēn…õ w…ôkiriŇč ka as…Ēdar a MARIKI, int…õp k…ôcder.¬Ľ K…Ē Yosuwe ontontn…õn…õ k…Ē, k'…õnc…ôp…õ k…Ē tobu d…ônt…Ēf, k'eyif k…Ē: ¬ęC…ôke c…Ē Mariki endeloku w…ôcar k…Ēn-…õ?¬Ľ
\v 15 K…Ē w…ôb…õ ka as…Ēdar a MARIKI oloku Yosuwe: ¬ęM…ôwur…õ c…Ēfta cam d…ôw…õc…ôk, bawo k…ôfo kaŇčk…Ē m…ônc…ôm…õ m…Ē, k…ôs…Ēk.¬Ľ K…Ē Yosuwe owur…õ c…Ēfta.
\c 6
\s1 K…ôbaŇč ka Yeriko
\p 
\v 1 AnakaŇčk…ôla d…ôk…ôb…õr…õ da Yeriko, pab…õŇčk…ôr-b…õŇčk…ôr di teta aka Yisrayel. Fum o fum oncwur f…õ, fum …õncb…õr…õ f…õ.
\v 2 K…Ē MARIKI k…ôloku Yosuwe: ¬ęIl…õk Yeriko, w…ôb…õ k…ôŇčan k…Ē as…Ēdar aŇčan ayeŇčki dis, k'imb…õr'…ôm d…ôwaca.
\v 3 Awa as…Ēdar f…ôp Ňčan…ĒŇčk…ôr dare. Ňäan…ĒŇčk…ôr dare katin d…Ēs…Ēk o d…Ēs…Ēk haŇč mata cam…ôt-tin.
\v 4 AloŇčn…õ cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč Ňčat…Ēmp…ôr l…õn ya Ňčkesiya cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč d…ôwaca, Ňčayi kaŇčk…ôra ka danapa kiriŇč. Mba tataka ta cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč, n…ôn…ĒŇčk…ôr dare cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč, t…õm nt…õ aloŇčn…õ Ňčacfula l…õn.
\v 5 K…Ē Ňčandenafula k…ôl…õn ka aŇčkesiya-…õ, n…ôck…Ēnane k…ôl…õn dim, afum f…ôp Ňčakul…õ-kul…õ sim sa k…ôwan. K…Ē damba da dare d…õnt…õmp…õn…õ di s…ôrka-…õ, as…Ēdar am Ňčab…õr…õ oŇč t…õm tat…Ēk…Ē, nw…õ o nw…õ nde …õnt…õf…ôrn…õ m…Ē.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 6 K…Ē Yosuwe wan ka Nun ewe aloŇčn…õ, k'oloku Ňča: ¬ęN…ôl…õk kaŇčk…ôra ka danapa k…ôs…õl…õŇč, aloŇčn…õ cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč Ňčant…Ēmp…ôr l…õn ya Ňčkesiya cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč Ňčayi aloŇčn…õ at…Ēmp…ôr a kaŇčk…ôra k…ôs…õl…õŇč ka danapa da MARIKI kiriŇč.¬Ľ
\v 7 K'oloku as…Ēdar: ¬ęN…ôk…Ē n…ôn…ĒŇčk…ôr dare, ak…Ē Ňčant…Ēmp…ôr yosutn…õn…õ m…Ē Ňčayi kaŇčk…ôra ka MARIKI kiriŇč.¬Ľ
\v 8 K…Ē afum Ňčay…Ē t…Ēk…Ē Yosuwe …õnaloku Ňča m…Ē. AloŇčn…õ cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč aŇč…õ Ňčanat…Ēmp…ôr l…õn cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč ya Ňčkesiya m…Ē Ňčayi MARIKI kiriŇč, Ňčancep…ôr k…Ē Ňčafula l…õn. K…Ē kaŇčk…ôra ka danapa da MARIKI k…ôc…ôm…õ Ňča dar…ôŇč.
\v 9 As…Ēdar at…Ēmp…ôr yosutn…õn…õ Ňčayi aloŇčn…õ afula l…õn tekiriŇč, aloŇčn…õ agbaŇčn…õ kaŇčk…ôra k…ôs…õl…õŇč m…Ē Ňčac…Ēnc afula l…õn, as…Ēdar al…Ēma Ňčayi kaŇčk…ôra tadar…ôŇč, Ňčack…Ēt Ňčacsur…õn…õ k…ôl…õn dim.
\v 10 Mba Yosuwe …õnaloku afum: ¬ęTa n…ôk…Ēkul…õ-kul…õ de! Ta n…ôk…Ēy…Ē pane nu sim de! Ta nw…õ o nw…õ p…ôk…Ēloku toloku haŇč d…Ēs…Ēk nd…õ indeloku nu a n…ôkul…õ-kul…õ m…Ē! T…õm tat…Ēk…Ē n…ôkul…õ-kul…õ sim sa k…ôwan .¬Ľ
\v 11 K…Ē kaŇčk…ôra ka MARIKI k…ôn…ĒŇčk…ôr dare katin, k…Ē Ňčamb…õr…õ d…ôsaŇčka, k…Ē Ňčancep…ôr…õn…õ pibi.
\p 
\v 12 K…Ē Yosuwe …õy…õf…õ b…ôtb…ôt suy, k…Ē aloŇčn…õ Ňčal…õk s…Ē kaŇčk…ôra k…ôs…õl…õŇč ka MARIKI.
\v 13 As…Ēdar at…Ēmp…ôr yosutn…õn…õ Ňčanayi kiriŇč, aloŇčn…õ cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč at…Ēmp…ôr l…õn ya Ňčkesiya Ňčacfula Ňčac…Ēnc Ňča, aloŇčn…õ at…Ēmp…ôr kaŇčk…ôra ka danapa da Kanu Ňčayi afula l…õn tadar…ôŇč, k…Ē as…Ēdar alp…ôs Ňčayi kaŇčk…ôra tadar…ôŇč.
\v 14 K…Ē Ňčan…ĒŇčk…ôr dare katin tataka ta m…õr…ôŇč, k…Ē Ňčalukus nde d…ôsaŇčka. K…Ē Ňčay…Ē ti mata cam…ôt-tin.
\v 15 Tataka ta cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč k…Ē Ňčay…õf…õ p…ôpanpan k…Ē Ňčan…ĒŇčk…ôr dare cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč. Mba d…Ēs…Ēk din dad…Ēk…Ē gb…ôc…ôr…ôm d…Ē Ňčanan…ĒŇčk…ôr dare cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč.
\v 16 K…ôn…ĒŇčk…ôr ka cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč k…Ē aloŇčn…õ Ňčafula l…õn, k…Ē Yosuwe oloku afum: ¬ęN…ôkul…õ-kul…õ sim sa k…ôwan, bawo MARIKI k…ôs…ĒŇč un dare dand…õ!
\v 17 K…ôl…ôs…ôr k'ander dare dand…õ k…Ē ca c…ôk…Ē c…ôyi d…õ m…Ē f…ôp. Rahabu w…ôran w…ôyamayama sona gboŇč k…Ē afum …Ēn aŇč…õ Ňčayi nde k…ôl…Ē k…Ēn disr…õ m…Ē Ňč…Ē andesak, bawo …õnawos…õ k…ôm…õŇčk…õ su afum ak…Ē s…ônasom y…Ēky…Ēk k…ôdet…õn…ôs mes ma at…Ēf ŇčaŇč…õ m…Ē.
\v 18 Mba n…ôk…õmb…ôrn…õ k…ôl…õk paka pin mp…õ Kanu k…ônam…Ēn…õ m…Ē, bawo daka f…ôp nd…õ n…ôŇčs…Ēt…Ē d…ôk…ôwan m…Ē, m…õn…õ n…ômb…õr…õn…õ di daka da Kanu. K…Ē n…ôm…õŇčk…ôrn…õ paka pin, n…ôndes…ĒŇč p…ôl…õc saŇčka sa Yisrayel.
\v 19 K…ôy…õf…õ gbeti, k…õma, ca ca k…Ēp…ôr f…ôp fayi, MARIKI k…ôy…Ē y…Ēs…Ēt…Ē ya d…ôk…ôwan f…ôp. P…ômar padeb…õr…õn…õ yi daka da MARIKI.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 20 K'afula l…õn ya Ňčkesiya, nt…õ afum Ňčane l…õn dim m…Ē, k…Ē Ňča s…Ē Ňčawur…õ sim sa k…ôwan p…ôp…ĒŇč, k…Ē damba da saŇčka sa dare d…õnt…õmp…õn…õ di s…ôrka, k…Ē afum Ňčamb…õr…õ dare disr…õ. Nw…õ o nw…õ p…ôsoln…õ nde …õnt…õf…ôrn…õ m…Ē, k…Ē ŇčambaŇč dare.
\v 21 K…Ē Ňčandif…ôt…õ afum k…Ē y…Ēc…Ēl y…Ēk…Ē y…õnayi dare disr…õ m…Ē f…ôp sakma s…ôŇčan, k…ôy…õf…õ w…ôrkun, w…ôran, wanf…õt, w…ôbeki, wana, aŇčkesiya, s…Ēfale.
\p 
\v 22 Yosuwe …õnaloku afum ak…Ē m…õr…ôŇč aŇč…õ Ňčanak…Ē k…ôt…õn…ôs y…Ēky…Ēk mes ma at…Ēf ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē m…Ē: ¬ęN…ôk…Ē ndena w…ôran w…ôyamayama w…ôkak…Ē, n…ôk…Ē n…ôwur…õn…õ k…Ē, k…Ē afum …Ēn f…ôp, p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē n…ônad…õrm…õ k…Ē m…Ē.¬Ľ
\v 23 K…Ē at…õmp m…õr…ôŇč aŇč…õ Ňčanak…Ē Ňčat…õn mes y…Ēky…Ēk nde at…Ēf ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē m…Ē, ŇčaŇčk…Ē Ňčawur…õn…õ Rahabu, papa w…ôk…Ēn, iya w…ôk…Ēn, aw…õnc aŇča, k…Ē afum …Ēn f…ôp. K…Ē Ňčawur…õn…õ afum …Ēn f…ôp aŇč…õ Ňčanab…ôp nde k…ôl…Ē k…Ēn m…Ē, k…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē Ňčad…ôs Ňča tofo t…Ēt…Ēt saŇčka sa Yisrayel tadar…ôŇč.
\v 24 K…Ē Ňčanc…Ēf dare k…Ē ca c…ôk…Ē y…õnayi di m…Ē f…ôp, m…õn…õ gbeti, k…õma, k…Ē ca ca k…Ēp…ôr k…Ē f…õc, ny…õ Ňčanab…õr…õn…õ daka da k…ôl…Ē ka MARIKI m…Ē.
\v 25 Yosuwe …õnadif f…õ Rahabu w…ôran w…ôyamayama k…Ē afum a k…ôl…Ē k…Ēn f…ôp. K'…õnd…õ aka Yisrayel dac…Ē haŇč m…Ēk…Ē, bawo nk…Ēn …õnawos…õ k…ôm…õŇčk ka at…õn mes y…Ēky…Ēk, aŇč…õ Yosuwe …õnasom k…ôk…Ēt…õn…ôs mes ma Yeriko m…Ē.
\p 
\v 26 T…õm tat…Ēk…Ē k…Ē Yosuwe …õnd…õr…ôm:
\q1 ¬ęIntolan…õ fum p…ôl…õc
\q1 nw…õ endey…õf…õ a dare da Yeriko doŇčlomp…ôs m…Ē.
\q1 W…ôkayi p…ôck…Ēnakay k…ôd…Ēf ka togbu p…Ēc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē,
\q1 t…Ēy…Ēn…õ k…ôway ka wan k…Ēn coco.
\q1 K'…Ēnck…Ēnab…õr kumba ka dare-…õ,
\q1 t…Ēy…Ēn…õ k…Ē k…ôway ka wan k…Ēn w…ôlp…ôs.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 27 MARIKI k…ônasol…õ Yosuwe, k…Ē tewe t…Ēn t…õmb…õk t…Ēf f…ôp.
\c 7
\s1 Fum w…ôkin k…ôy…Ē k…Ēn p…ôl…õc k…ôs…ĒŇč aka Yisrayel f…ôp p…ôl…õc
\p 
\v 1 K…Ē aka Yisrayel ŇčaŇčluks…õ k…ôc…ôm…õ MARIKI dar…ôŇč nt…õ k…ônam…Ēn…õ Ňča k…ôl…õk ka daka da dare m…Ē. K…Ē AkaŇč wan ka Karmi, wan ka Sabidi, wan ka Sera, w…ôka kusuŇčka ka Yuda, …õŇčkiy…õ ca c…ôl…Ēma daka da dare dac…Ē, k…Ē p…ônt…õl…õ MARIKI nn…Ē aka Yisrayel Ňčayi m…Ē.
\p 
\v 2 K…Ē Yosuwe osom afum k…ôy…õf…õ Yeriko k…ôk…Ē dare da Hay nde p…ôl…Ēt…ôr…õn…õ Bet Aw…õn ntende dec d…õmp…õ Betel m…Ē. K'oloku Ňča: ¬ęN…ôp…õ n…ôk…Ē n…ôt…õn mes y…Ēky…Ēk d…Ēt…Ēf.¬Ľ K…Ē afum akak…Ē Ňčamp…õ k…ôk…Ēt…õn mes y…Ēky…Ēk Hay.
\v 3 K…Ē Ňčaluks…ôrn…õ nn…Ē Yosuwe eyi m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčaloku k…Ē: ¬ęTa afum f…ôp Ňčap…õ de! Afum m…õc…ôp m…õr…ôŇč, k…Ē p…ôyi f…õ ti-…õ, afum m…õc…ôp maas Ňčap…õ, Ňča Ňčantam k…ôsut Hay! Ta n…ôl…Ēl…ôs afum dis, bawo ak…Ē p…ômar a pay…õf…ôr…õn…õ m…Ē, Ňčala f…õ.¬Ľ
\v 4 K…Ē afum m…õc…ôp maas Ňčamp…õ k…ôk…Ēsut…õn…õ k…Ē aka Hay, mba Ňčanatam f…õ, k…Ē afum akak…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē Ňčay…õks…ôr aka Hay.
\v 5 K…Ē afum aka Hay Ňčandif…ôr Ňča afum w…ôco maas k…Ē cam…ôt-tin. K…Ē Ňčay…õf…õ k…ôb…õl…ôs Ňča k…ôy…õf…õ dare d…ôkusu haŇč Sabarim\f + \fr 7:5 \fq Sabarim\ft = ¬ęK…ôfo nk…õ aŇčkay masar m…Ē¬Ľ\f*, k…Ē Ňčasut Ňča p…ôt…ômb…ôl…ôr pa t…Ēr…Ē. K…Ē afum Ňčanes…õ k…ôsut…õn…õ k…Ē dis d…õŇčd…õnc…õ Ňča.
\p 
\v 6 K…Ē Yosuwe …õwal-wali yamos y…Ēn, k'…õf…ônt…ôr…õ k'…õnc…ôp…õ kaŇčk…ôra ka MARIKI tobu d…ônt…Ēf haŇč d…Ēf…Ēy. K…Ē abeki a Yisrayel ŇčaloŇč…ôrn…õ s…Ē k…ôbof d…ôs…ôbomp.
\v 7 K…Ē Yosuwe oloku: ¬ęMARIKI W…ôb…õ kem, ta ake t…Ē m…ônc…ĒŇčs…õ afum k…ôcali ka k…ôŇčgb…Ēk…Ē ka Yurd…õn-…õ k…ôdel…õk su m…ôb…õr aka Am…Ēr d…ôwaca, k…ôm…ôl…ôk su k…Ē m…ôfaŇč? K…ôyi kosu Yurd…õn ntende dec d…õmp…õ m…Ē k…ôncep…ôr su k…ôder ka nn…Ē!
\v 8 M…ôŇčaŇč…õn…õn'em Mariki! C…ôke c'ideloku oŇč-…õ?: ‚ÄĻYisrayel Ňčay…õks…ôr ater…õn…õ aŇčan.‚Äļ
\v 9 K…ôy…õf…õ aka KanaŇč haŇč afum alp…ôs aŇč…õ f…ôp Ňčayi d…Ēt…Ēf m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčandene ti-…õ, Ňčandeb…õr…õn…õ, ŇčapaŇčn…õ su Ňčasut, Ňčam…ôl…ôk su doru. C…ôke c…Ē m…ôndement…ôr oŇč debeki dam-…õ?¬Ľ
\p 
\v 10 K…Ē MARIKI k…ôloku Yosuwe: ¬ęM…ôy…õf…õ, ta ake t…Ē m…ônc…ôp…õn…õ tobu d…ônt…Ēf-…õ?
\v 11 Aka Yisrayel Ňčanciya! Ňäal…ôs…ôr temer p…Ēk…Ē inas…ĒŇč Ňča m…Ē. ∆źy, Ňčal…õk…ôrn…õ ca c…ôl…Ēma ny…õ inaloku Ňča k…ôb…õr…õn…õ yi daka dem m…Ē. ŇäaŇčkiy…õ Ňča yati, k…Ē Ňčam…õŇčk ca c…ôl…Ēma d…ôy…õsar…õ yaŇčan.
\v 12 Ti disr…õ, aka Yisrayel Ňčaf…Ētam k…ôsut…õn…õ k…Ē ater…õn…õ aŇčan. M…õn…õ Ňčay…õks…ôr Ňča, bawo Ňča Ňč…Ē p…ômar oŇč pam…ôl…ôk. If…Ētam k…ôyi tes tin k…Ē n…ôna k…Ē n…ônt…Ēwur…õn…õ nu dac…Ē ca nc…õ inam…Ēn…õ nu k…ôl…õk m…Ē de!
\v 13 M…ôy…õf…õ, m…ôk…Ē, m…ôloŇčka afum. M…ôloku Ňča: ¬ęN…ôs…Ēk…ôsn…õ alna. MARIKI, Kanu ka Yisrayel k…ôsom im ti k…ôdelok'un: Ca nc…õ inam…Ēn'on m…Ē, yey'un d…ôwaca.‚Äļ Aka Yisrayel n…ôf…Ētam k…ôy…õf…ôr…õn…õ k…Ē ater…õn…õ anu k…Ē n…ônt…Ēwur…õ ca cac…Ēk…Ē nu dac…Ē-…õ.
\v 14 Alna b…ôtb…ôt, n…ôder nn…Ē f…Ēr ya Kanu kiriŇč, n…ôm…õnt…ôrn…õ Ki cusuŇčka cusuŇčka. KusuŇčka nk…õ Kanu k…ônc…Ēk…ôr m…Ē k…ôc…ĒŇčn…õ d…ôcor d…ôcor. Kor nk…õ k…ôndec…Ēk…ôr m…Ē k…ôc…ĒŇčn…õ w…Ēl…Ē w…Ēl…Ē. K…ôl…Ē nk…õ Kanu k…ôndec…Ēk…ôr m…Ē afum aŇč…õ Ňčadec…ĒŇčn…õ akin akin.
\v 15 Nw…õ o nw…õ andebonc k…ôt…Ēmp…ôr ka ca nc…õ Kanu k…ôm…Ēn…õ m…Ē, amb…õr k…Ē d…ôn…õnc, nk…Ēn k…Ē afum a k…ôl…Ē k…Ēn f…ôp. Nk…Ēn …õp…ôt…ôs danapa da MARIKI bawo nk…Ēn …Ēy…Ē tes nt…õ t…Ēnt…Ētes…õ m…Ē nt…õ t…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ aka Yisrayel k…ôlap…ôrn…õ m…Ē.
\p 
\v 16 K…Ē Yosuwe …õy…õf…õ b…ôtb…ôt suy, k'…Ēnc…ĒŇč…õn…õ aka Yisrayel cusuŇčka cusuŇčka. K…Ē MARIKI k…ônc…Ēk…ôr aka kusuŇčka ka Yuda.
\v 17 K…Ē Yosuwe …Ēnc…ĒŇč…õn…õ Yuda cor cor, k'…Ēnc…Ēk…ôr kor ka Sera. K'…Ēnc…ĒŇč…õn…õ kor ka Sera w…Ēl…Ē w…Ēl…Ē, k'…Ēnc…Ēk…ôr k…ôl…Ē ka Sabidi.
\v 18 K'anc…ĒŇč…õn…õ k…ôl…Ē ka Sabidi akin akin, k'…Ēnc…Ēk…ôr AkaŇč, wan ka Karmi, wan ka Sabidi, wan ka Sera w…ôka kusuŇčka ka Yuda.
\v 19 K…Ē Yosuwe oloku AkaŇč: ¬ęWan kem m…ôlel…ôs MARIKI, Kanu ka Yisrayel, m…ôyek-yek…ôs ki! M…ôlok'im ma t…Ēk…Ē m…ôy…Ē m…Ē, ta m…ôm…õŇčk…ôr'im ti de!¬Ľ
\v 20 K…Ē AkaŇč oloku Yosuwe: ¬ę∆źy, kance k…Ē, in'eciya MARIKI, Kanu ka Yisrayel. Il…Ēm…ôr'…ôm nt…õ iy…Ē m…Ē:
\v 21 Y…Ēs…Ēt…Ē yosu disr…õ, inan…ôŇčk duma da Mesopotami, duma dad…Ēk…Ē dentes…õ decep…ôr…ôr, k…Ē gbeti masar m…õr…ôŇč, k…Ē anc…ômb…ôl Ňča k…õma Ňči sona gboŇč Ňčelel…õ kilo dac…Ē. K…Ē ca cac…ôk…Ē y…õmbas'im, it…Ē inal…õk…õ yi. Mba inam…ôt yi d…ônt…Ēf, im…õŇčk yi nde abal Ňčem disr…õ gbeti beyi tant…Ēf.¬Ľ
\v 22 K…Ē Yosuwe osom afum, k…Ē Ňčay…õks…õ k…ôk…Ēm…Ēm…ôn abal Ňča AkaŇč disr…õ, k…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē Ňčab…ôp ca yay…Ēk…Ē f…ôp gbeti b…õf…ônt…ôr…õ yi tant…Ēf.
\v 23 K…Ē Ňčal…õk yi f…ôp, k…Ē ŇčaŇčken…õ Yosuwe k…Ē aka Yisrayel f…ôp, k…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē Ňčaboc yi f…Ēr ya MARIKI kiriŇč.
\p 
\v 24 K…Ē Yosuwe …õl…õk AkaŇč wan ka Sera, k…Ē gbeti, duma, anc…ômb…ôl Ňča k…õma, awut …Ēn arkun k…Ē aran, c…ôna c…Ēn, s…Ēfale s…Ēn, y…Ēc…Ēl y…Ēn y…õf…õt y…õf…õt, abal Ňč…Ēn k…Ē ca c…Ēk…Ē y…õnay…Ēn…õ y…Ēn m…Ē f…ôp. K…Ē aka Yisrayel f…ôp Ňčasol k…Ē Yosuwe, k…Ē Ňčamp…õn…õ AkaŇč nde m…Ēr…Ē dac…Ē, nde aŇčwe ¬ęAranta Ňča P…ôl…õc m…Ē¬Ľ.
\v 25 K…Ē Yosuwe oloku: ¬ęTa ake t…Ē m…ôy…Ēn…õ su p…ôl…õc pamp…õ-…õ? M…ôna s…Ē k…ôy…Ē'm k…Ē MARIKI k…ônder p…ôl…õc m…Ēk…Ē.¬Ľ K…Ē aka Yisrayel f…ôp Ňčancacas k…Ē masar haŇč k'efi. K…Ē Ňčancacas afum …Ēn f…ôp masar, k…Ē Ňčanc…Ēf Ňča f…ôp d…ôn…õnc.
\v 26 K'amboc Ňča k…ôroŇč t…õp…õsa p…Ēp…ĒŇč pa masar, mp…õ p…Ēs…Ēr…Ēyi haŇč m…Ēk…Ē m…Ē, k…Ē ab…ôk…ôc Ňčedetor MARIKI. It…Ē awen…õ k…ôfo kaŇčk…Ē tewe ta ¬ęAranta Ňča P…ôl…õc¬Ľ haŇč m…Ēk…Ē.
\c 8
\s1 Aka Yisrayel k…ôtam k…ôŇčan aka Hay
\p 
\v 1 K…Ē MARIKI k…ôloku Yosuwe: ¬ęTa m…ônes…õ, ta m…ôyikc…õ! M…ôl…õk as…Ēdar am f…ôp, m…ôy…õf…õ m…ôk…Ēsut…õn…õ k…Ē aka Hay. M…ôn…ôŇčk, is…ĒŇč …ôm w…ôb…õ ka Hay, k'imb…õr'…ôm k…Ē d…ôwaca, nk…Ēn k…Ē afum …Ēn, k…Ē dare d…Ēn, k…Ē at…Ēf Ňč…Ēn.
\v 2 M…ôŇčk…Ēy…Ē w…ôb…õ ka Hay p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē m…ônay…Ē w…ôb…õ ka Yeriko k…Ē dare d…Ēn m…Ē. Mba d…ôndo taŇč, n…ôntam k…ôl…õk y…Ēc…Ēl k…Ē ca c…ôlp…ôs f…ôp nc…õ n…ôŇčk…Ēs…Ēt…Ē d…ôndo m…Ē. N…ôgb…Ēpn…õ dare tadar…ôŇč, n…ôw…õk…ôrn…õ Ňča.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 3 K…Ē Yosuwe …õy…õf…õ k…Ē as…Ēdar …Ēn f…ôp k…ôp…õ ka Hay. K…Ē Yosuwe …õy…õk-y…õk as…Ēdar ayeŇčki dis m…õc…ôp w…ôco maas, k'oloku Ňča k…ôk…Ē Hay pibi.
\v 4 K'oloku Ňča: ¬ęN…ôk…õmb…ôrn…õ, n…ôgb…Ēpn…õ dare dar…ôŇč haŇč t…õm nt…õ andenaloku a n…ôw…õk…ôrn…õ Ňča m…Ē. Ta n…ôb…Ēl…õ dare p…ôlar…ôm de! N…ôlomp…ôsn…õ k…ôsut…õn…õ!
\v 5 Ina k…Ē afum aŇč…õ isol…õ m…Ē f…ôp, s…ôna s…ôŇčk…Ēl…Ēt…ôrn…õ dare. T…õm nt…õ aka Hay Ňčandenawur k…ôk…Ēs…õt…ôr su p…ôm…Ē t…Ēc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē m…Ē, s…ôŇčk…ĒbaŇč…õn…õ k…ôy…õks…ôr Ňča.
\v 6 T…õm tat…Ēk…Ē Ňčandec…ôm…õ su dar…ôŇč k…ôb…õl…ôs, s…ôŇčkek…ôr…õ Ňča haŇč s…ôwur…õn…õ Ňča dare, bawo Ňčande k…ôcloku: ‚ÄĻK…ôy…õks…ôr su k…Ē Ňčand…õ s…Ē p…ôm…Ē t…Ēc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē.‚Äļ T…Ēy…Ēn…õ f…Ē s…ôna s…ôyi k…ôy…õks…ôr s…ôcder nn…Ē n…ôyi m…Ē,
\v 7 n…ôwur…ôr Ňča, n…ôbaŇč katina dare. MARIKI Kanu konu, k…ôŇčk…Ēb…õr un dare dad…Ēk…Ē d…ôwaca.
\v 8 N…ôck…Ēnasump…ôr dare, n…ôb…õr di n…õnc. N…ôy…Ē mes p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē MARIKI k…ôloku m…Ē. N…ôk…õmb…ôrn…õ tat…Ēk…Ē ilok'un m…Ē.¬Ľ
\v 9 K…Ē eŇčkek…ôr…õ Ňča, d…ôk…ôliŇč…õ dare da Hay. K…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē Ňčagb…Ēpn…õ Betel k…Ē Hay dac…Ē, k…ôca nk…õ dec d…õŇčkal…õ Hay m…Ē. K…Ē Yosuwe encep…ôr…õn…õ pibi k…ôfo kaŇčk…Ē k…Ē as…Ēdar …Ēn.
\p 
\v 10 D…Ēck…Ēs…Ēk k…Ē Yosuwe …õy…õf…õ b…ôtb…ôt suy, k'oloŇčka as…Ēdar …Ēn, nk…Ēn k…Ē abeki aka Yisrayel, k…Ē Ňčancep…ôr as…Ēdar kiriŇč k…ôk…Ē ka Hay.
\v 11 As…Ēdar ak…Ē …õnasol…õ m…Ē f…ôp k…Ē Ňčamp…õ, k…Ē Ňčal…Ēt…ôrn…õ nt…õ Ňčanadet…õf…ôrn…õ dare m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčanc…ômb…ôr saŇčka nde dec d…õŇčkal…õ m…Ē k…ôca k…ôt…Ēt. Aranta Ňč…õnayi Hay k…Ē as…Ēdar dac…Ē.
\v 12 K…Ē Yosuwe …õl…õk as…Ēdar afum m…õc…ôp k…ôcam…ôt, k'…õnc…ômb…ôr Ňča Betel k…Ē Hay dac…Ē, ŇčacliŇč…õ ntende dec d…õŇčkal…õ m…Ē.
\v 13 Nt…õ as…Ēdar Ňčalip k…ôc…ômb…ôr saŇčka f…ôp ntende k…ôca k…ômeriya ka nde dec d…õmp…õ dare da Hay m…Ē, k…Ē Yosuwe encep…ôr pibi pap…Ēk…Ē nde d'aranta.
\p 
\v 14 Nt…õ w…ôb…õ ka Hay endec…ôr…õ ti m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčamb…õlk…ôr k…ôy…õf…õ k…Ē as…Ēdar …Ēn k…Ē afum a dare Ňčawur, k…ôk…Ēb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē aka Yisrayel k…ôsut…õn…õ nde p…ôt…ômb…ôl…ôr p…Ēk…Ē p…õt…õf…ôr…õn…õ k…Ē Araba m…Ē, mba w…ôb…õ ka Hay …õnac…ôr…õ f…õ a k…ôliŇč…õ Ňča k…Ē aka Yisrayel Ňčand…õ ntende dare tadar…ôŇč.
\v 15 Yosuwe k…Ē aka Yisrayel f…ôp Ňčay…õl waca Hay f…Ēr kiriŇč, k…Ē Ňčay…õf…õ k…ôy…õks…ôr aka Hay, Ňčasoln…õ d…Ēp…Ē da nde d…ôt…õgb…ôr…õ.
\v 16 K'aloku aka Hay a Ňčab…õl…ôs Ňča. K…Ē Ňčamb…õl…ôs Yosuwe k…Ē afum …Ēn haŇč k…Ē Ňčamb…Ēl…õn…õ dare da Hay.
\v 17 Ali fum anasak f…õ Hay k…Ē Betel nw…õ …õnat…Ē-wur k…ôk…Ēb…õl…ôs aka Yisrayel m…Ē. K…ôb…õlk…ôr k…ôb…õl…ôs aka Yisrayel k…ônas…ĒŇč…õ ta aŇčgb…ôt cumba ca dare-…õ.
\v 18 K…Ē MARIKI k…ôloku Yosuwe: ¬ęM…ôtuk…ôr dakma dam dad…Ēk…Ē m…ônt…Ēmp…ôr m…Ē k…ôca ka Hay, bawo il…õk Hay, k'imb…õr'…ôm d…ôwaca.¬Ľ K…Ē Yosuwe ontuk…ôr k…ôŇčgbasar k…ôŇčk…Ē …õnat…Ēmp…ôr m…Ē Hay.
\v 19 K…Ē aliŇč…õ Ňčawur kat…ôna kat…ôna nde Ňčanagb…Ēp…ôsn…õ m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčay…õks…õ k…ôk…Ē dare, k…Ē Ňčamb…õr…õ, k…Ē Ňčasump…ôr dare k…Ē Ňčanc…Ēf di kat…ôna kat…ôna.
\p 
\v 20 Aka Hay Ňčandeluks…ôrn…õ, k…Ē ŇčaŇčgb…ôtn…õ nt…õ: Kinim…õ ka dare k…ôcp…õ haŇč k…ôsump…ôr darenc. Ňäas…Ēt…Ē f…õ s…Ē t…õy…õks…õ Ňčak…Ē k…ôca k…ôt…Ēt, k…Ē p…ôyi f…õ ti-…õ, k…ôca k…ômeriya. As…Ēdar aka Yisrayel ak…Ē ŇčanabaŇč…õn…õ k…ôy…õks…ôr aka Hay m…Ē, ŇčaŇčkaf…ôl…õ k…ôk…Ēsut…õn…õ k…Ē Ňča.
\v 21 Nt…õ Yosuwe k…Ē asol …Ēn aka Yisrayel f…ôp Ňčan…ôŇčk f…Ē aŇč…õ ŇčacliŇč…õ dare m…Ē Ňčasump…ôr di, k…Ē kinim…õ k…ôyi k…ôp…õ dare, k…Ē ŇčaŇčkaf…ôl…ôrn…õ aka Hay k…ôsut…õn…õ, k…Ē Ňčasut Ňča.
\v 22 Ak…Ē ŇčanabaŇč dare Ňčanc…õps…õ aka Hay dar…ôŇč, k…Ē t…Ēy…Ēn…õ f…Ē aŇčkuc-kuc…õn…õ aka Hay, ali w…ôkin …õnatam f…õ k…ômulp…ôr aka Yisrayel.
\v 23 K…Ē Ňčasump…ôr w…ôb…õ ka Hay p…ôyi w…ôyeŇč, k…Ē ŇčaŇčken…õ k…Ē Yosuwe.
\v 24 Nt…õ aka Yisrayel Ňčalip k…ôdif aka Hay nde d…ôt…õgb…ôr…õ m…Ē, akak…Ē Ňčanac…ôm…õ aka Yisrayel dar…ôŇč k…ôb…õl…ôs m…Ē, k'andif…õ Ňča f…ôp sakma. K…Ē aka Yisrayel f…ôp Ňčander Hay k…Ē Ňčande Ňčadif Ňča f…ôp.
\v 25 D…Ēs…Ēk dad…Ēk…Ē anadif afum m…õc…ôp w…ôco k…Ē m…õr…ôŇč (12.000), k…ôy…õf…õ arkun haŇč aran, f…ôp f…ôŇčan aka Hay.
\v 26 Yosuwe ontor…õ f…õ dakma dad…Ēk…Ē …õnatuk…ôr Hay m…Ē haŇč k…Ē aka Yisrayel Ňčalip k…ôdif…ôt Ňča.
\v 27 K…Ē aka Yisrayel Ňčal…õk y…Ēc…Ēl y…õf…õt y…õf…õt, k…Ē ca c…ôl…Ēma ya dare p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē MARIKI k…ônasom ti Yosuwe m…Ē.
\v 28 K…Ē Yosuwe …Ēnc…Ēf Hay, k…Ē t…Ēy…Ēn…õ f…Ē haŇč m…Ēk…Ē tofo t…õt…õy…õ t…Ē, t…Ēy…Ēn…õ nde d…ôt…õgb…ôr…õ.
\v 29 K…Ē Yosuwe …õŇčgb…õk w…ôb…õ w…ôka Hay d…ôk…ôt…Ēk haŇč d…Ēf…Ēy. Dec dendekaf…ôl…õ, k…Ē Yosuwe oloku a pator…õ w…ôfi. K'aŇčk…Ē pagbal k…Ē nde dare d…ôkusu, k'andeŇč…ôs…ôr k…Ē masar m…Ēp…ĒŇč k…ôroŇč mm…õ m…Ēs…Ēr…Ēyi di haŇč m…Ēk…Ē m…Ē.
\p 
\v 30 K…Ē Yosuwe …õnc…ômb…ôr…õ Mariki tetek toloŇčn…õ Kanu ka aka Yisrayel nde t…Ēr…Ē ta Ebal.
\v 31 P…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē Musa w…ôcar ka Mariki …õnasom ti aka Yisrayel m…Ē, p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē ancic ti nde buk ba sariy…õ sa Musa m…Ē: Tetek toloŇčn…õ Kanu ta masar m…Ēt…Ēpat mp…õ af…õc ŇčontogbuŇč…õn…õ m…Ē, n…ôndek…Ē n…ôkek…ôr…õ y…Ēc…Ēl y…Ēc…Ēf…õ Mariki. ŇäaloŇčn…õ di k…ôloŇčn…õ ka p…ôforu.
\v 32 D…ôndo aka Yisrayel f…ôp f…Ēr kiriŇč Yosuwe …ĒŇčgb…Ēk…ôr…õ s…Ē k…ôcic…ôs masar mam…Ēk…Ē k…ôroŇč sariy…õ ns…õ Musa …õnacic…ôs m…Ē.
\v 33 Aka Yisrayel f…ôp, abeki aŇčan, akiriŇč aŇčan, aboc aŇčan kiti, acik…ôra k…Ē aYisrayel Ňčanc…ôm…õ kaŇčk…ôra k…ôca k…ôt…Ēt k…Ē k…ômeriya. Ňäat…õf…ôr…õn…õ k…Ē aloŇčn…õ aLewy aŇč…õ ŇčanagbaŇčn…õ kaŇčk…ôra k…ôs…õl…õŇč ka danapa da MARIKI k…Ē aka Yisrayel m…Ē. Afum dac…Ē Ňčanayi k…ôca ka t…Ēr…Ē ta Karisim, k…Ē dac…Ē Ňčanayi k…ôca ka t…Ēr…Ē ta Ebal, p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē Musa w…ôcar ka MARIKI …õnasom ti, a patolan…õ aka Yisrayel t…Ēc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē m…Ē.
\v 34 K…Ē Yosuwe oloku moloku ma sariy…õ f…ôp, k…ôtolan…õ p…ôt…Ēt k…Ē p…ôl…õc, p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē anacic ti d…ôbuk ba sariy…õ m…Ē.
\v 35 Ali toloku ta Musa tin Yosuwe …õnasak f…õ nt…õ …õnat…Ē-loku aka Yisrayel f…ôp f…Ēr kiriŇč m…Ē, k…ôb…ôp aran, awut, haŇč acik…ôra aŇč…õ Ňčanand…õ Ňča dac…Ē m…Ē.
\c 9
\s1 K…ôsek danapa k…Ē aka Kabay…ĒŇč
\p 
\v 1 Nt…õ toloku ta k…ôder ka as…Ēdar aYisrayel t…õmb…ôp ab…õ aŇč…õ Ňčanand…õ Yurd…õn k…ôs…ôk ntende dec d…õŇčkal…õ d…ôm…Ēr…Ē k…Ē nde p…ôtils…ôrn…õ t…Ēf ya tant…Ēf m…Ē, ab…õ aŇč…õ Ňčanad…õs-nd…õs k…ôba k…ôs…ôk m…Ē f…ôp, haŇč at…Ēf Ňča LibaŇč k…ôs…ôk: Aka Hit, aka Am…Ēr, aKanaŇč, aPerisi, aHiwy, k…Ē aYebus,
\v 2 k…Ē Ňčamb…õr…õn…õ k…ôk…Ēsut…õn…õ k…Ē Yosuwe k…Ē aka Yisrayel.
\p 
\v 3 K…Ē aka Kabay…ĒŇč Ňčane s…Ē nt…õ Yosuwe …õnay…Ē aka Yeriko k…Ē Hay m…Ē.
\v 4 K…Ē Ňča s…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē k…ôk…Ēy…Ē aka Yisrayel k…Ē Yosuwe c…ômp…ônp…ôn. K…Ē Ňčal…õk l…Ēba y…õl…õc, k…Ē ŇčandeŇč…ôr s…Ēfale s…ôŇčan k…Ē c…ôbunt…ôl…õ ca member c…ôl…õc c…ôfut…õ-fut…õ.
\v 5 K…Ē ŇčaŇčb…õr…ôsn…õ c…Ēfta c…ôl…õc c…ôl…õc c…ôwal…õ-wal…õ, pas…Ēt…ôs ci, Ňčab…õr…ôsn…õ suma s…ôwal…õ-wal…õ. C…ôcom nc…õ Ňčanam…õŇčk…ôrn…õ k…ôk…Ēs…Ēm m…Ē f…ôp c…ônawos, c…ôputk…õ.
\v 6 K…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē Ňčab…ôp Yosuwe nde saŇčka sa Kilkal k…Ē Ňčaloku k…Ē k…Ē afum aka Yisrayel: ¬ęAt…Ēf Ňč…Ēb…Ēl…õ Ňč…Ē s…ôy…õf…õ. S…ôfaŇč f…Ē s…ôsek danapa k…Ē n…ôna.¬Ľ
\v 7 Mba k…Ē afum aka Yisrayel Ňčaloku Ňča: ¬ęAn…Ē'c…ôr…õ-…õ? T…Ēl…Ēma s…ôna Ňč…Ē n…ônd…õ dac…Ē. C…ôke c…Ē antam k…ôsek danapa k…Ē n…ôna-…õ?¬Ľ
\v 8 K…Ē Ňčaloku Yosuwe: ¬ęAcar anu Ňč…Ē s…ôy…Ēn…õ.¬Ľ K…Ē Yosuwe eyif Ňča: ¬ęAre Ňč…Ē n…ôy…Ēn…õ-…õ? Deke n…ôy…õf…õ-…õ?¬Ľ
\v 9 K…Ē Ňčaloku Yosuwe: ¬ęAt…Ēf Ňčobol-bolu Ňč…Ē acar am Ňčay…õf…õ, bawo tewe ta MARIKI t…Ē s…ône, Kanu kam, bawo s…ône k…Ē tewe k…Ē t…Ēk…Ē …õnay…Ē Misira m…Ē f…ôp,
\v 10 k…Ē t…Ēk…Ē …õnay…Ē ab…õ a Am…Ēr m…õr…ôŇč nde Yurd…õn k…ôs…ôk ntende dec d…õmp…õ m…Ē: Sih…ĒŇč w…ôb…õ w…ôka Hesbon, k…Ē Oku w…ôb…õ w…ôka Basan nw…õ …õnayi Astarot m…Ē.
\p 
\v 11 Abeki asu k…Ē afum asu f…ôp aka d…Ēt…Ēf Ňčaloku su: ¬ęN…ôl…õk yeri yonu ya d…Ēp…Ē, n…ôk…Ē n…ôfayn…õ Ňča. N…ôk…Ē n…ôloku Ňča: ‚ÄĻAcar anu Ňč…Ē s…ôy…Ēn…õ! Nd…õk…ôl oŇč n…ôsek danapa k…Ē s…ôna!
\v 12 C…ôcom cosu canc…õ c…ônawon…õ t…õm nt…õ s…ôndenal…õk ci d…õk…õr k…ôder t…Ēmp…ôrn…õ d…Ēp…Ē m…Ē, k…ôy…õf…õ d…Ēs…Ēk nd…õ s…ôy…õf…õ nn…Ē ndorosu k…ôder nn…Ē n…ôyi m…Ē. Awa n…ôgb…ôtn…õ nt…õ: Ic…Ē canc…õ c…ôwos…ôr…õn…õ k…Ē c…ômputk…õ m…Ē.
\v 13 K…Ē c…ôbunt…ôl…õ canc…õ s…ônal…õk ci c…ôfu, n…ôgb…ôtn…õ nt…õ ic…Ē canc…õ c…ômp…Ēr…õ-p…Ēr…õ m…Ē! N…ôn…ôŇčk yamos yosu k…Ē c…Ēfta cosu, d…Ēp…Ē dobolu d…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ yi k…ôl…õc…õ.‚Äļ¬Ľ
\v 14 K…Ē afum a Yosuwe Ňčam…Ēm…ôn ca ya acik…ôra ta Ňčayif ti MARIKI-…õ.
\v 15 K…Ē Yosuwe …õncaŇč…ôs k…ôt…ôŇčn…õ k…Ē afum aŇč…õ, k…Ē Ňčant…ôŇčn…õ p…ôforu, k…Ē Ňčas…ĒŇč Ňča temer ta k…ôsak Ňča Ňčayi doru, k…Ē akiriŇč a k…ôloŇčkan…õ ka Yisrayel Ňčand…õrm…õ Ňča moloku mam…Ēk…Ē Ňčanat…ôŇčn…õ m…Ē.
\p 
\v 16 Mata maas disr…õ nt…õ Ňčalip k…ôcaŇč…ôs ka danapa k…Ē Ňča m…Ē, k…Ē aka Yisrayel Ňčande Ňčane a and…õ aŇčan Ňč…Ē, afum aŇč…õ Ňčan…ĒŇčk…ôl…õn…õ k…ônd…õ.
\v 17 K…Ē aka Yisrayel ŇčaŇčk…Ē nde dare daŇčan, tataka ta maas k…Ē Ňčamb…õr…õ di. S…ôdare sas…Ēk…Ē s…ônat…ôŇčn…õ Kabay…ĒŇč, Kefira, Beyerot, k…Ē Kiriyat-Yeyarim.
\v 18 Aka Yisrayel Ňčanadif f…õ Ňča teta k…ôd…õr…ôm k…ôŇčk…Ē akiriŇč a k…ôloŇčkan…õ Ňčanad…õrm…õ Ňča tewe ta MARIKI, Kanu ka Yisrayel m…Ē. K…Ē afum a Yisrayel f…ôp Ňčay…õf…õ k…ôbup…ôr…õ moloku ma akiriŇč aŇčan.
\v 19 Mba k…Ē akiriŇč Ňčaloku k…ôloŇčkan…õ ka aYisrayel f…ôp: ¬ęS…ônad…õrm…õ Ňča MARIKI, Kanu ka Yisrayel. Af…Ēs…Ētam k…ôgbuŇč…õn…õ Ňča.
\v 20 Nt…õ t…Ē andey…Ē Ňča: Andece Ňča Ňčayi doru, ta padewern…õ m…õt…õl…õ ma MARIKI teta k…ôd…õr…ôm nk…õ anad…õrm…õ Ňča m…Ē.
\v 21 Ňäayi doru, t…Ēy…Ē f…õ tes! Mba aŇčk…Ēc…ômb…ôr Ňča k…ôk…õt…ôs ka domun, k…Ē k…ôgb…õs ka t…Ēk ya k…ôloŇčkan…õ ka Yisrayel.¬Ľ It…Ē akiriŇč a Yisrayel Ňčanaloku afum aŇčan.
\v 22 K…Ē Yosuwe ewe aka Kabay…ĒŇč, k'oloku Ňča: ¬ęTa ake t…Ē n…ôyemb…ôr…õ su n…ôcloku a n…ômb…Ēl…õn…õ k…Ē s…ôna-…õ, a k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…Ē s…ôn…ĒŇčk…ôl…õn…õ k…ônd…õ k…Ē n…ôna-…õ?
\v 23 Nd…õk…ôl oŇč, p…ôl…õc p…ônc…ôm'on dar…ôŇč! Ali w…ôkin …Ēf…Ēs…Ē-wur dacar. N…ôna ande k…ôck…õt…ôs domun, n…ôcgb…õs t…Ēk ya k…ôl…Ē ka Kanu kem.¬Ľ
\v 24 K…Ē aka Kabay…ĒŇč Ňčaloku Yosuwe: ¬ęAl…Ēm…ôr acar am teta aka Yisrayel tin tin tin a MARIKI Kanu kam k…ônasom w…ôcar k…Ēn Musa a k…ôs…ĒŇč un ant…Ēf ŇčaŇč…õ f…ôp, a n…ôl…ôs…ôr and…õ a Ňči f…ôp f…Ēr yonu kiriŇč. Awa k…ôder konu k…ôs…ĒŇč…õ su k…ônes…õn…õ s…ôbomp sosu, it…Ē s…ôy…Ēn…õ tant…õ.
\v 25 Nd…õk…ôl oŇč, s…ôyi'm d…ôwaca. M…ôy…Ē su t…Ēk…Ē tentes'am m…Ē, m…ôy…Ē su ti p…ôlompu disr…õ.¬Ľ
\v 26 It…Ē Yosuwe …õnay…Ē Ňča, k'…õmbaŇč…ôr Ňča aka Yisrayel aŇč…õ Ňčanat…Ēs…Ē-dif Ňča m…Ē.
\v 27 K…Ē Yosuwe …õnc…ômb…ôr Ňča k…ôy…õf…õ d…Ēs…Ēk dad…Ēk…Ē k…ôgb…õs t…Ēk, k…Ē k…ôk…õt…ôs domun da afum k…Ē da tetek toloŇčn…õ ta Mariki. HaŇč m…Ēk…Ē, awut-s…Ē aŇčan Ňčas…Ēr…Ēb…ôc y…õb…ôc yay…Ēk…Ē nde at…Ēf Ňča Yisrayel.
\c 10
\s1 Yosuwe k…Ē aYisrayel k…ôtam k…ôŇčan ab…õ Am…Ēr
\p 
\v 1 K…Ē Adoni C…õd…õk w…ôb…õ w…ôka Yerusal…õm ene a Yosuwe …õmbaŇč Hay, k'endif afum aka di f…ôp, k'…Ēy…Ē aka Hay k…Ē w…ôb…õ k…ôŇčan p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē …õnay…Ē Yeriko k…Ē w…ôb…õ k…ôŇčan m…Ē. K'ene s…Ē aka Kabay…ĒŇč Ňča Ňčasek danapa k…Ē aka Yisrayel, k…Ē Ňčayi k…ôfo kin.
\v 2 K…Ē k…ônes…õ k…ôp…ĒŇč k…ônder Ňča, bawo Kabay…ĒŇč dare d…Ēp…ĒŇč d…õnayi, p…ôm…Ē dare da ab…õ. D…õnab…õk d…õtas Hay, afum a di ŇčayeŇčk dis.
\v 3 K…Ē Adoni C…õd…õk w…ôb…õ w…ôka Yerusal…õm osom pak…Ēloku Hoham w…ôb…õ w…ôka Heb…ôr…ĒŇč, Piram w…ôb…õ w…ôka Yarmut, Yafiya w…ôb…õ w…ôka Lakis, k…Ē Debir w…ôb…õ w…ôka Ekil…ĒŇč:
\v 4 ¬ęN…ôder n…ômar'im nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ itam k…ôsut Kabay…ĒŇč, bawo Ňčant…ôŇčn…õ k…ôsek danapa k…Ē Yosuwe k…Ē aka Yisrayel.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 5 K…Ē Ňčamb…õr…õn…õ ab…õ k…ôcam…ôt nde at…Ēf Ňča Am…Ēr: W…ôb…õ w…ôka Yerusal…õm, w…ôb…õ w…ôka Heb…ôr…ĒŇč, w…ôb…õ w…ôka Yarmut, w…ôb…õ w…ôka Lakis, k…Ē w…ôb…õ w…ôka Ekil…ĒŇč. K…Ē Ňčamp…õ f…ôp faŇčan k…Ē as…Ēdar aŇčan, k…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē Ňčac…ômb…ôr saŇčka s…ôŇčan Kabay…ĒŇč kiriŇč k…Ē Ňčaw…õk…ôrn…õ Ňča.
\p 
\v 6 K…Ē aka Kabay…ĒŇč Ňčasom pak…Ēloku Yosuwe nde saŇčka sa Kilkal: ¬ęTa m…ôsak acar am, m…ôp…õrn…õ nn…Ē s…ôyi m…Ē kat…ôna! Ta m…ôbaŇč…ôr acar am k…ômar kam, bawo ab…õ Am…Ēr f…ôp, aŇč…õ Ňčanand…õ nde d…ôm…Ēr…Ē m…Ē, Ňčamb…õr…õn…õ k…ôdey…õf…ôr…õn…õ k…Ē s…ôna.
\v 7 K…Ē Yosuwe …õmp…õ Kilkal k…Ē as…Ēdar …Ēn f…ôp k…Ē afum …Ēn ayeŇčki dis f…ôp.
\p 
\v 8 K…Ē MARIKI k…ôloku Yosuwe: ¬ęTa m…ônes…õ Ňča, bawo il…õk Ňča k'imb…õr'…ôm d…ôwaca. Ali fum k…ôŇčan w…ôkin …Ēf…Ētam k…ôc…ôm'am f…Ēr kiriŇč.¬Ľ
\v 9 K…Ē Yosuwe …ĒŇčk…Ēt pibi pap…Ēk…Ē f…ôp k…ôy…õf…õ ka Kilkal, k'…ĒŇčk…Ē p…ôb…õr…ôr Ňča.
\v 10 K…Ē MARIKI k…ôs…ĒŇč…õ Ňča k…ôy…õks…ôr aka Yisrayel. K…Ē Ňčasut Ňča p…ôp…ĒŇč Kabay…ĒŇč, k…Ē Ňčanc…ôm…õ k…ôb…õl…ôs Ňča d…Ēp…Ē nd…õ d…õmp…õ Bet Horon m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčandif…ôt aka Am…Ēr haŇč s…ôdare sa Aseka k…Ē Makeda.
\v 11 K…ôy…õks…ôr k…ôŇčan Yisrayel, nt…õ aka Am…Ēr Ňčanab…ôp p…ôt…ômb…ôl…ôr pa Bet Horon m…Ē, k…Ē MARIKI k…ôy…õf…õ k…ôtor…ôr Ňča cul ya let…ôr y…Ēp…ĒŇč haŇč Aseka, k…Ē Ňčafi. AŇč…õ cul ya let…ôr y…õnadif m…Ē Ňčanala Ňčatas ak…Ē aka Yisrayel Ňčanadif…õ sakma s…ôŇčan m…Ē.
\p 
\v 12 K…Ē Yosuwe oloku MARIKI d…Ēs…Ēk nd…õ k…ônal…õk aka Am…Ēr k…ôb…õr aka Yisrayel d…ôwaca m…Ē, k'oloku aka Yisrayel f…Ēr kiriŇč:
\q1 ¬ęM…ôna Dec, m…ôc…ômb…ôr…ôs Kabay…ĒŇč!
\q1 K…Ē m…ôna Ňäof, m…ôc…ômb…ôr…ôs nde aranta Ňča Ayalon!¬Ľ
\m 
\v 13 K…Ē dec d…õnc…ôm…õ tofo tin k…Ēm dac…Ē k…Ē d…õfati k…ôk…Ēt k…ôl…Ēt…ôs ka d…Ēs…Ēk din camcam, k…Ē Ňčof Ňči s…Ē Ňč…õc…ôm…õ haŇč t…õm nt…õ aka at…Ēf Ňča Yisrayel Ňčanalip k…ôluks…õ ater…õn…õ aŇčan ay…õk m…Ē. Ancic f…õ ti nde Buk ba W…ôlompu ba?
\v 14 D…Ēs…Ēk d…õntayi f…õ p…ôm…Ē d…Ēs…Ēk dad…Ēk…Ē, t…Ēc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē t…õlp…ôs t…õnayi. MARIKI k…ônac…ôŇčk…ôl dim da fum, bawo MARIKI Yisrayel Ňč…Ē k…ôncsutn…õn…õ d…Ēs…Ēk dad…Ēk…Ē.
\p 
\v 15 Yosuwe k…Ē aka Yisrayel f…ôp Ňčalukus d…Ēs…Ēk dad…Ēk…Ē nde saŇčka sa Kilkal.
\s1 Yosuwe k…ôdif…ôt k…Ēn ab…õ k…ôcam…ôt
\p 
\v 16 K…Ē ab…õ aŇč…õ k…ôcam…ôt Ňčay…õks…õ k…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē Ňčagb…Ēpn…õ d…ôt…Ēgb…Ēk…õn…õ nde Makeda.
\v 17 K'aŇčk…Ē paloku ti Yosuwe: ¬ęAb…õ ak…Ē k…ôcam…ôt ŇčaŇčk…Ē Ňčagb…Ēpn…õ nde t…Ēgb…Ēk…õn…õ ta Makeda.¬Ľ
\v 18 K…Ē Yosuwe oloku: ¬ęN…ôbiŇčk…ôli masar m…Ēp…ĒŇč, n…ôk…Ē n…ôsunc…õ mi kusuŇčka ka t…Ēgb…Ēk…õn…õ tat…Ēk…Ē, n…ôc…ômb…ôr di afum Ňčacbum.
\v 19 Ta n…ôsak k…ôc…ôm…õ ater…õn…õ anu dar…ôŇč, n…ôgbint…ôrn…õ Ňča d…Ēp…Ē, ta n…ôsak Ňča Ňčab…õr…õ dare daŇčan de! MARIKI k…ôl…õk Ňča k…Ē k…ômb…õr un d…ôwaca!¬Ľ
\v 20 Nt…õ Yosuwe k…Ē awut aka Yisrayel Ňčalip k…ôsut Ňča, mba Ňčabut k…ôm…ôl…ôk Ňča f…ôp m…Ē, m…õn…õ afum akin akin ak…Ē Ňčanay…õks…õ-y…õks…õ Ňčak…Ē s…ôdare sa saŇčka s…ôk…Ē s…ônal…Ēt…ôrn…õ Ňča m…Ē.
\v 21 K…Ē afum f…ôp Ňčalukus b…ôk…ôc yoforu disr…õ nde saŇčka sa Makeda, nde Yosuwe …õnayi m…Ē. Ali fum …õnayeŇčk f…õ ab…ôk…ôc k…ôlok…õ ka aka Yisrayel tes t…Ēl…Ēma.
\p 
\v 22 K…Ē Yosuwe oloku: ¬ęN…ôfeni d…ôk…ôb…õr…õ da t…Ēgb…Ēk…õn…õ ta t…Ēr…Ē tant…õ, n…ôwur…õn…õ ab…õ akaŇč…õ k…ôcam…ôt n…ôk…õr'em ma!¬Ľ
\v 23 K…Ē awur…õ k…Ē ab…õ akaŇč…õ k…ôcam…ôt d…ôndo d…ôt…Ēgb…Ēk…õn…õ, k'aŇčken…õ k…Ē: W…ôb…õ w…ôka Yerusal…õm, w…ôb…õ w…ôka Heb…ôr…ĒŇč, w…ôb…õ w…ôka Yarmut, w…ôb…õ w…ôka Lakis, k…Ē w…ôb…õ w…ôka Ekil…ĒŇč.
\v 24 Nt…õ awur…õn…õ ab…õ aŇč…õ k'aŇčken…õ Yosuwe m…Ē, k…Ē Yosuwe ewe afum aka Yisrayel f…ôp, k'oloku ab…õ …Ēn aka d…ôk…ôwan aŇč…õ Ňčanck…Ē d…ôk…ôsut…õn…õ m…Ē: ¬ęN…ôc…ĒŇčn…õ n…ôna n…ôgb…ôc…õ ab…õ akaŇč…õ k…ôcam…ôt mera w…õc…ôk wonu.¬Ľ K…Ē afum aŇč…õ Ňčal…Ēt…ôrn…õ k…Ē ŇčaŇčgb…ôc…õ ab…õ aŇč…õ k…ôcam…ôt mera, w…õc…ôk waŇčan.
\v 25 K…Ē Yosuwe oloku: ¬ęTa n…ônes…õ, ta n…ôyikc…õ! N…ôyeŇčk dis, n…ôb…ôkn…õ, bawo tant…õ t…Ē MARIKI k…ôndek…Ēy…Ē ater…õn…õ anu f…ôp aŇč…õ n…ôyi k…ôsut…õn…õ m…Ē.¬Ľ
\v 26 Nt…õ tencep…ôr m…Ē, k…Ē Yosuwe osut Ňča, k'endif. K'…õŇčgb…õk Ňča t…Ēk k…ôcam…ôt darenc, k…Ē Ňčand…õts…õ t…Ēk yay…Ēk…Ē darenc haŇč d…Ēf…Ēy.
\v 27 Dec d…Ēr…Ēf…Ēy, k…Ē Yosuwe oloku a padeti Ňča d…ôt…Ēk d…ôndo anagb…õk Ňča m…Ē. K'aŇčk…Ē pagbal Ňča d…ôndo Ňčanagb…Ēpn…õ m…Ē, k'asunc…õ kusuŇčka ka t…Ēgb…Ēk…õn…õ tat…Ēk…Ē masar m…Ēp…ĒŇč. Tat…Ēk…Ē t…Ē p…ôs…Ēr…Ēyi d…ônda haŇč m…Ēk…Ē.
\s1 Yosuwe k…ôtam k…Ēn afum a s…ôdare s…ôl…Ēma
\p 
\v 28 K…Ē Yosuwe …õmbaŇč s…Ē dare da Makeda d…Ēs…Ēk din dad…Ēk…Ē, k'osut Ňča k'endif…õ Ňča dakma d…Ēn, k…ôl…õk…õn…õ w…ôb…õ k…ôŇčan. K…Ē Yosuwe endif aka Makeda f…ôp, k…Ē y…Ēc…Ēl yaŇčan y…Ēk…Ē y…õnayi di m…Ē, ali fum …õnamulp…ôr f…õ Ňča. K'…Ēy…Ē w…ôb…õ ka Makeda t…Ēk…Ē …õnay…Ē w…ôb…õ ka Yeriko m…Ē.
\p 
\v 29 Yosuwe k…Ē aka Yisrayel f…ôp Ňčancep…ôr Makeda k…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē Libana, k…Ē Ňčaw…õk…ôrn…õ aka Libana.
\v 30 K…Ē MARIKI k…ôl…õk s…Ē Libana k…Ē w…ôb…õ k…ôŇčan k…Ē k…ômb…õr Ňča aka Yisrayel d…ôwaca. K…Ē aka Yisrayel Ňčandif…ôt…õ Ňča sakma s…ôŇčan, k…Ē afum ak…Ē Ňčanayi di m…Ē f…ôp. Ali fum …õnamulp…ôr f…õ Ňča, k…Ē Ňčay…Ē s…Ē w…ôb…õ w…ôka Libana p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē Ňčanay…Ē w…ôb…õ w…ôka Yeriko m…Ē.
\p 
\v 31 Yosuwe k…Ē aka Yisrayel f…ôp Ňčay…õf…õ Libana k…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē Lakis. K…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē Ňčac…ômb…ôr di saŇčka s…ôŇčan f…Ēr yaŇčan kiriŇč, k…Ē Ňčaw…õk…ôrn…õ Ňča.
\v 32 K…Ē MARIKI k…ôl…õk Lakis k…Ē k…ômb…õr aka Yisrayel d…ôwaca tataka ta m…õr…ôŇč nt…õ, k…Ē aka Yisrayel Ňčandif…ôt…õ Ňča sakma s…ôŇčan, k…Ē afum ak…Ē Ňčanayi di m…Ē f…ôp, p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē Ňčanay…Ē aka Libana m…Ē.
\v 33 K…Ē Horam w…ôb…õ w…ôka Keser …õmp…õ k…ôk…Ēmar aka Lakis. K…Ē Yosuwe osut k…Ē k…Ē afum …Ēn, ali w…ôkin …õnasak f…õ.
\p 
\v 34 Yosuwe k…Ē afum …Ēn Ňčancep…ôr Lakis, k…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē Ekil…ĒŇč. K…Ē Ňčanc…ômb…ôr di saŇčka s…ôŇčan f…Ēr yaŇčan kiriŇč, k…Ē Ňčaw…õk…ôrn…õ Ňča.
\v 35 K…Ē MARIKI k…ôl…õk aka Ekil…ĒŇč k…Ē k…ômb…õr aka Yisrayel d…ôwaca d…Ēs…Ēk din dad…Ēk…Ē. K…Ē Ňčandif…ôt…õ Ňča sakma s…ôŇčan, k…Ē afum ak…Ē Ňčanayi di m…Ē f…ôp. K…Ē Yosuwe endif Ňča f…ôp d…Ēs…Ēk din dad…Ēk…Ē, p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē …õnay…Ē aka Lakis m…Ē.
\p 
\v 36 Yosuwe k…Ē aka Yisrayel f…ôp Ňčay…õf…õ Ekil…ĒŇč k…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē Heb…ôr…ĒŇč, k…Ē Ňčaw…õk…ôrn…õ Ňča.
\v 37 K…Ē MARIKI k…ôl…õk aka Heb…ôr…ĒŇč k…Ē k…ômb…õr Ňča d…ôwaca. K…Ē Ňčandif…ôt…õ Ňča sakma s…ôŇčan k…ôb…ôp ka w…ôb…õ k…ôŇčan k…Ē afum ak…Ē Ňčanayi di m…Ē f…ôp, p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē Ňčanay…Ē Ekil…ĒŇč m…Ē. Ali fum …õnamulp…ôr f…õ Yosuwe, k'endif Ňča k…ôl…õk…õn…õ afum ak…Ē Ňčanayi di m…Ē f…ôp.
\p 
\v 38 Yosuwe k…Ē aka Yisrayel ŇčaŇčkaf…ôl…ôrn…õ aka Debir, k…Ē Ňčaw…õk…ôrn…õ Ňča.
\v 39 K…Ē MARIKI k…ôl…õk Debir k…Ē w…ôb…õ k…ôŇčan k…Ē k…ômb…õr aka Yisrayel d…ôwaca. K…Ē Ňčandif…ôt…õ Ňča sakma s…ôŇčan, k…Ē Ňčandif afum ak…Ē Ňčanayi di m…Ē f…ôp. Ali fum …õnamulp…ôr f…õ Ňča. K…Ē Yosuwe …Ēy…Ē aka Debir k…Ē w…ôb…õ k…ôŇčan p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē …õnay…Ē Heb…ôr…ĒŇč, Libana k…Ē ab…õ aŇčan m…Ē.
\p 
\v 40 K…Ē Yosuwe osut aka m…Ēr…Ē k…ôroŇč akak…Ē f…ôp, at…Ēf Ňča N…õk…õf nde k…ôca k…ôt…Ēt ka nde dec d…õmp…õ m…Ē, p…ôtils…ôrn…õ di at…Ēf Ňča tant…Ēf, k…Ē at…Ēf nŇč…õ Ňčeyi m…Ēr…Ē k…Ē aranta dac…Ē m…Ē, k…ôl…õk…õn…õ ka ab…õ aŇčan f…ôp. Ali fum …õnasak f…õ. K'endif ca ny…õ yencŇčes…ôm m…Ē f…ôp, p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē MARIKI Kanu ka Yisrayel, k…ônasom k…Ē ti m…Ē.
\v 41 K…Ē Yosuwe …õntam afum k…ôy…õf…õ ka Kad…õs-Barneya haŇč Kasa, k…Ē k…ôy…õf…õ ant…Ēf Ňča Kos…õŇč f…ôp haŇč Kabay…ĒŇč.
\v 42 K…Ē Yosuwe …õmbaŇč t…Ēf yay…Ēk…Ē f…ôp, k…Ē ab…õ a t…Ēf yay…Ēk…Ē, bawo MARIKI, Kanu aka Yisrayel, k…ôncsutn…õn…õ Yisrayel.
\v 43 Yosuwe k…Ē aka Yisrayel f…ôp Ňčalukus nde saŇčka s…ôŇčan nde Kilkal.
\c 11
\s1 Yisrayel k…ôsut…õn…õ k…ôŇčan nde Mer…Ēm
\p 
\v 1 Nt…õ toloku t…õmb…ôp Yabin w…ôb…õ w…ôka Hac…Ēr m…Ē, k'osom afum nda ab…õ al…Ēma: Yobab w…ôb…õ w…ôka Mad…ĒŇč, w…ôb…õ ka Simr…ĒŇč, w…ôb…õ ka Aksaf,
\v 2 ab…õ a k…ôca k…ômeriya ka nde dec d…õmp…õ d…ôm…Ēr…Ē m…Ē, nde Araba, k…ôca k…ôt…Ēt ka ntende dec d…õmp…õ Kinarot m…Ē, nde p…ôntils…ôrn…õ pa t…Ēf ya tant…Ēf, ant…Ēf Ňča d…ôm…Ēr…Ē Ňča D…Ēr nde dec d…õŇčkal…õ m…Ē,
\v 3 aka KanaŇč k…ôy…õf…õ nde dec d…õmp…õ m…Ē k…Ē aka nde dec d…õŇčkal…õ m…Ē, aka Am…Ēr, aHit, aPerisi, aYebus nde d…ôm…Ēr…Ē, k…Ē aHiwy nde t…Ēr…Ē ta H…õrm…ĒŇč tant…Ēf nde ant…Ēf Ňča Mispe.
\v 4 K…Ē Ňčawur f…ôp k…Ē as…Ēdar aŇčan, k…Ē Ňčay…Ēn…õ afum akin ayi, Ňčanala p…ôm…Ē as…ônc nŇč…õ Ňčeyi nde k…ôba k…ôs…ôk m…Ē. F…ôl…õs k…Ē cibil ca k…ôwan y…õnala.
\v 5 K…Ē ab…õ akaŇč…õ f…ôp ŇčaloŇčkan…õ, k…Ē Ňčander Ňčac…ômb…ôr saŇčka s…ôŇčan nde domun da Mer…Ēm k…ôs…ôk, Ňčadesut…õn…õ k…Ē aka Yisrayel.
\p 
\v 6 K…Ē MARIKI k…ôloku Yosuwe: ¬ęTa m…ônes…õ Ňča, bawo dec dand…õ alna indes…ĒŇč…õ Ňča k…ôfi f…ôp f…Ēr ya aka Yisrayel kiriŇč. M…ôcopu b…ônta ya f…ôl…õs yaŇčan, m…ôc…Ēf cibil c…ôŇčan.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 7 Yosuwe k…Ē as…Ēdar …Ēn Ňčantor…ôr Ňča katina d…ôndo domun da Mer…Ēm, k…Ē Ňčaw…õk…ôrn…õ Ňča.
\v 8 K…Ē MARIKI k…ôl…õk Ňča k…Ē k…ômb…õr aka Yisrayel d…ôwaca. K…Ē Ňčasut Ňča k…Ē Ňčamb…õl…ôs Ňča haŇč nde Sid…ĒŇč S…ôp…ĒŇč, haŇč Misref…Ēt-Mayim, haŇč nde aranta Ňča Mispe nde m…Ēr…Ē dac…Ē ntende dec d…õmp…õ m…Ē. K…Ē Ňčandif…ôt Ňča, ali fum …õnamulp…ôr f…õ Ňča.
\v 9 K…Ē Yosuwe …Ēy…Ē Ňča p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē MARIKI k…ônasom k…Ē m…Ē: K'oncopu b…ônta ya f…ôl…õs yaŇčan, k'…Ēnc…Ēf…õ cibil c…ôŇčan ca d…ôk…ôwan n…õnc.
\s1 K…ôbaŇč ka dare d…Ēp…ĒŇč da Hac…Ēr
\p 
\v 10 T…õm tat…Ēk…Ē, nt…õ Ňčayi k…ôluks…ôrn…õ m…Ē, k…Ē Yosuwe …õmbaŇč Hac…Ēr, k'endif…õ w…ôb…õ k…ôŇčan dakma. C…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē Hac…Ēr Ňč…õnay…Ēn…õ dare d…Ēp…ĒŇč da s…ôdare ns…õ f…ôp.
\v 11 K…Ē Ňčandif…ôt…õ Ňča sakma, k…Ē Ňčandif afum ak…Ē Ňčanayi di m…Ē f…ôp. Ali paka peŇčes…ôm pin Ňčanasak f…õ, k…Ē Ňčanc…Ēf Hac…Ēr.
\v 12 K…Ē Yosuwe …õmbaŇč s…Ē s…ôdare sa ab…õ akaŇč…õ f…ôp, k'osump…ôr s…Ē ab…õ aŇčan, k'endif…õ Ňča dakma d…Ēn. K'endif Ňča f…ôp, p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē Musa w…ôcar ka MARIKI …õnasom k…Ē ti m…Ē.
\v 13 Mba aka Yisrayel Ňčanac…Ēf…õ f…õ ali dare din nd…õ deyi nde m…Ēr…Ē k…ôroŇč m…Ē, m…õn…õ dare da Hac…Ēr gb…ôc…ôr…ôm nd…õ Yosuwe …õnac…Ēf m…Ē.
\v 14 K…Ē aka Yisrayel Ňčal…õk daka nd…õ Ňčanab…ôp di m…Ē f…ôp k…Ē y…Ēc…Ēl, mba k…Ē Ňčandif…ôt…õ afum f…ôp sakma s…ôŇčan haŇč k…Ē Ňčam…ôl…ôk Ňča. Ali paka Ňčanasak f…õ mp…õ peŇčes…ôm m…Ē.
\v 15 Tosom nt…õ MARIKI k…ônasom w…ôcar k…Ēn Musa m…Ē, Musa …õnaluks…õ k…ôsom kaŇčk…Ē Yosuwe, k…Ē Yosuwe …ĒŇčk…Ēt…õn…õ k…ôsom kaŇčk…Ē. Ali tes tin …õnad…õnc…ôs f…õ nt…õ MARIKI k…ônasom Musa m…Ē.
\s1 Yosuwe k…ôbaŇč k…Ēn ka t…Ēf
\p 
\v 16 K…Ē Yosuwe …õmbaŇč nt…Ēf yay…Ēk…Ē f…ôp, k…ôy…õf…õ d…ôm…Ēr…Ē, ant…Ēf Ňča N…õk…õf f…ôp, ant…Ēf Ňča Kos…õŇč, p…ôtils…ôrn…õ pa nt…Ēf ya tant…Ēf, Araba, ant…Ēf nde m…Ēr…Ē ma Yisrayel k…Ē p…ôtils…ôrn…õ pa ant…Ēf Ňča tant…Ēf ntende dec d…õŇčkal…õ m…Ē.
\v 17 K…ôy…õf…õ ka t…Ēr…Ē mp…õ p…Ēnt…Ēy…Ē t…Ēk peyi k…ôca ka Seyir m…Ē, haŇč Bal Kad, nde m…Ēr…Ē dac…Ē ma LibaŇč nde t…Ēr…Ē ta H…õrm…ĒŇč tant…Ēf, k'osump…ôr…õn…õ ab…õ aŇčan f…ôp, k'endif…ôt Ňča.
\v 18 Yosuwe Ňčanawon k…ôsut…õn…õ k…Ē ab…õ akaŇč…õ.
\v 19 Ali dare d…õnayi f…õ nd…õ deŇčsek k…ôt…ôŇčn…õ k…Ē aka Yisrayel m…Ē, m…õn…õ Kabay…ĒŇč nk…õ aHiwy Ňčanand…õ m…Ē. K…Ē ŇčambaŇč s…ôdare s…ôlp…ôs ns…õ f…ôp k…ôsut…õn…õ disr…õ.
\v 20 Bawo deyeŇčki b…ôk…ôc daŇčan nde MARIKI k…Ē t…õncy…õf…õ, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ Ňčab…õr…õ aka Yisrayel d…õb…ôk…ôc k…ôsut…õn…õ m…Ē, akak…Ē Ňčadif…ôt Ňča, ta ŇčaŇčaŇčn…õn…õ Ňča m…Ē, Ňčam…ôl…ôk Ňča p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē MARIKI k…ônasom ti Musa m…Ē.
\p 
\v 21 K…Ē Yosuwe …ĒŇčk…Ē s…Ē p…ôw…õk…ôrn…õ aka Anak aŇč…õ Ňčanayi nde m…Ēr…Ē ma Heb…ôr…ĒŇč, Debir, Anaba, nde m…Ēr…Ē ma Yuda f…ôp, k…Ē m…Ēr…Ē ma Yisrayel m…Ē. K…Ē Yosuwe endif afum aka di f…ôp k…ôl…õk…õn…õ s…ôdare s…ôŇčan.
\v 22 Ali w…ôka Anak w…ôkin anasak f…õ s…Ē nde ant…Ēf Ňča aYisrayel, m…õn…õ Ňčayi s…Ē nde Kasa, nde Kat, k…Ē nde Asdodi.
\v 23 K…Ē Yosuwe …õmbaŇč ant…Ēf m…ôlm…ôl p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē MARIKI k…ônasom ti Musa m…Ē. K…Ē Yosuwe …Ēs…ĒŇč nt…Ēf ya k…õ yay…Ēk…Ē aka Yisrayel k'eyer yi cusuŇčka nc…õ w…ôco k…Ē m…õr…ôŇč. K…Ē ant…Ēf Ňč…Ēf…Ēr oŇč, k…Ē k…ôwan k…ôsak…õ.
\c 12
\s1 Ab…õ aŇč…õ Ňč…Ē aka Yisrayel Ňčanatam
\p 
\v 1 Ab…õ aŇč…õ Ňč…Ē aka Yisrayel Ňčanatam, ŇčabaŇč…ôr Ňča nt…Ēf yaŇčan nde Yurd…õn k…ôs…ôk ntende dec d…õmp…õ m…Ē, k…ôy…õf…õ ka nde k…ôŇčgb…Ēk…Ē ka Arn…ĒŇč haŇč nde t…Ēr…Ē ta H…õrm…ĒŇč, k…Ē Araba f…ôp nde dec d…õmp…õ m…Ē:
\v 2 Sih…ĒŇč w…ôb…õ ka aka Am…Ēr, nw…õ …õnand…õ Hesbon m…Ē, w…ôkak…Ē …õnay…Ēn…õ w…ôb…õ w…ôka ant…Ēf k…ôy…õf…õ ka Arower nŇč…õ Ňčeyi k…ôca ka nde k…ôŇčgb…Ēk…Ē ka Arn…ĒŇč m…Ē, k…ôy…õf…õ ka nde k…ôŇčgb…Ēk…Ē dac…Ē, k…ôl…õk…õn…õ dare da Kaladu dac…Ē, haŇč k…ôŇčgb…Ēk…Ē ka Yab…Ēk, nde Ňčay…Ē k…ôl…ônc…ôr k…Ē aka Am…ĒŇč m…Ē.
\v 3 D…õb…õ d…Ēn d…õl…õk…õn…õ ant…Ēf Ňča Araba, haŇč nde k…ôba ka Kinarot nde dec d…õmp…õ m…Ē, k…ôk…Ē ka nde k…ôba ka Araba, K…ôba K…ôdok…ôt, k…ôca nk…õ dec d…õmp…õ Bet Yesim…Ēt m…Ē, k…Ē k…ôca k…ôt…Ēt ka p…ôt…ômb…ôl…ôr pa Piska ntende dec d…õmp…õ m…Ē.
\p 
\v 4 Ant…Ēf Ňča Oku w…ôb…õ w…ôka Basan, w…ôRefay w…ôlp…ôs w…ôl…Ēma …õnayi w…ôkak…Ē, nw…õ …õnand…õ Astarot k…Ē Edreyi m…Ē.
\v 5 W…ôkak…Ē …õnay…Ēn…õ w…ôb…õ k…ôy…õf…õ ka t…Ēr…Ē ta H…õrm…ĒŇč k…ôk…Ē ka Salka, k…ôb…ôp ka Basan f…ôp, haŇč nde k…ôl…ônc…ôr ka aka Kesur k…Ē aka Mahaka, k…Ē k…ôy…õf…õ ant…Ēf Ňča Kaladu dac…Ē haŇč k…ôl…ônc…ôr ka ant…Ēf Ňča Sih…ĒŇč w…ôb…õ w…ôka Hesbon.
\v 6 Musa w…ôcar ka MARIKI k…Ē aka Yisrayel Ňčasut Ňča. K…Ē Musa w…ôcar ka MARIKI …Ēs…ĒŇč cusuŇčka cac…Ēk…Ē Ruben, Kadu, k…Ē kusuŇčka dac…Ē ka Manase nt…Ēf yay…Ēk…Ē.
\p 
\v 7 Ab…õ aŇč…õ Ňč…Ē Yosuwe k…Ē aka Yisrayel Ňčanatam nde ant…Ēf Ňča Yurd…õn ntende dec d…õŇčkal…õ m…Ē, k…ôy…õf…õ ka Bal Kad nde aranta Ňča LibaŇč nde m…Ēr…Ē dac…Ē ntende k…ôca k…ômeriya nk…õ dec d…õmp…õ, haŇč t…Ēr…Ē mp…õ p…Ēnt…Ēy…Ē t…Ēk peyi k…ôca ka Seyir m…Ē. K…Ē Yosuwe …Ēs…ĒŇč nt…Ēf yay…Ēk…Ē aka Yisrayel, k'eyer yi cusuŇčka cusuŇčka nt…õ,
\v 8 nde d…ôm…Ēr…Ē, nde p…ôtils…ôrn…õ pa nt…Ēf ya tant…Ēf, nde Araba, nde p…ôt…ômb…ôl…ôr mp…õ p…ôyi m…Ēr…Ē k…Ē aranta dac…Ē, nde d…ôt…õgb…ôr…õ k…Ē N…õk…õf. Ny…õ y…õnay…Ēn…õ nt…Ēf ya aHit, aka Am…Ēr, aKanaŇč, aPerisi, aHiwy k…Ē aYebus.
\v 9 Ab…õ aŇč…õ aka Yisrayel Ňčanatam m…Ē, Ňčanay…Ēn…õ aka s…ôdare ns…õ:
\li2 Yeriko, Hay nde Betel k…ôs…ôk,
\v 10 Yerusal…õm, Heb…ôr…ĒŇč,
\li2 
\v 11 Yarmut, Lakis,
\v 12 Ekil…ĒŇč, Keser,
\li2 
\v 13 Debir, Keder,
\v 14 Horma, Arad,
\li2 
\v 15 Libana, Adulam,
\v 16 Makeda, Betel,
\li2 
\v 17 Tapuwa, Hefer,
\v 18 Afek, Sar…ĒŇč,
\li2 
\v 19 Mad…ĒŇč, Hac…Ēr,
\v 20 Simr…ĒŇč-Mer…ĒŇč, Aksaf,
\li2 
\v 21 Tahanak, Mekido
\v 22 K…õd…õs, Yokonam nde Karm…õl
\li2 
\v 23 D…Ēr nd…õ d…Ēl…Ēt…ôrn…õ Nafat D…Ēr m…Ē, k…Ē Koyim nde Kilkal k…ôs…ôk
\v 24 k…Ē Tirsa.
\m Ti t…õnak…Ē ab…õ w…ôco maas k…Ē tin.
\c 13
\s1 Nt…Ēf ny…õ y…õnc…ôm…õ k…ôbaŇč m…Ē
\p 
\v 1 Yosuwe …õnasik…ôr, p…ôy…Ēn…õ w…ôtem. K…Ē MARIKI k…ôloku k…Ē: ¬ęM…ôsik…ôr, m…ôy…Ēn…õ oŇč w…ôtem, k…Ē nt…Ēf ny…õ p…ômar a m…ôbaŇč m…Ē y…õla.
\v 2 Nt…Ēf ny…õ y…õc…ôm…õ k…ôbaŇč: Nt…Ēf ya aFilisti f…ôp, k…Ē Ňča aka Kesur f…ôp,
\v 3 k…ôy…õf…õ ka k…ôŇčgb…Ēk…Ē ka Sih…Ēr nk…õ k…ôŇčy…õks…õ domun Misira tekiriŇč m…Ē, haŇč nde k…ôl…ônc…ôr ka Ek…ôron k…ôca k…ômeriya ka nde dec d…õmp…õ m…Ē, nk…õ k…ômar k…ôy…Ēn…õ ka aka KanaŇč ak…Ē ab…õ aFilisti aŇč…õ k…ôcam…ôt Ňčayi Ňča k…ôroŇč m…Ē: W…ôb…õ w…ôka Kasa, w…ôb…õ w…ôka Asdodi, w…ôb…õ w…ôka Askal…ĒŇč, w…ôb…õ w…ôka Kat, k…Ē w…ôb…õ w…ôka Ek…ôron, k…ôl…õk…õn…õ ant…Ēf Ňča aka Awi.
\v 4 K…ôca k…ôt…Ēt ka nde dec d…õmp…õ m…Ē, ant…Ēf m…ôlm…ôl Ňča aka KanaŇč, Meyara, mm…õ m…Ēy…Ēn…õ ma aSid…ĒŇč m…Ē, haŇč Afek, haŇč nde k…ôl…ônc…ôr ka aka Am…Ēr.
\v 5 Nt…Ēf y…Ēk…Ē y…õnc…ôm…õ k…ôbaŇč m…Ē y…Ēy…Ēn…õ ant…Ēf Ňča Kebal, k…Ē LibaŇč m…ôlm…ôl ntende dec d…õmp…õ m…Ē, k…ôy…õf…õ Bal Kad nde t…Ēr…Ē ta H…õrm…ĒŇč tant…Ēf haŇč k…ôb…õr…õ ka Hamat.
\v 6 Nt…Ēf ya afum aka d…ôm…Ēr…Ē f…ôp k…ôy…õf…õ LibaŇč haŇč Misref…Ēt-Mayim y…õnc…ôm…õ k…ôbaŇč, aka Sid…ĒŇč Ňč…Ē Ňčay…Ēn…õ. T…Ēk…Ē aka Yisrayel Ňčande k…ôcc…ĒŇč…ôsn…õ m…Ē, it…Ē indek…Ē icliŇč Ňča f…Ēr yaŇčan kiriŇč. M…ôde m…ôs…ĒŇč ant…Ēf Ňčan…Ēk…Ē f…ôp aka Yisrayel, m…ôcyer Ňča Ňči kusuŇčka o kusuŇčka k…Ē da endet…ôŇčn…õ m…Ē t…Ēy…Ēn…õ k…õ k…ôŇčan p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē ilok'…ôm ti m…Ē.
\v 7 M…ôyer ant…Ēf nŇč…õ cusuŇčka nc…õ cam…ôt-maŇčk…ôl…õ k…Ē kusuŇčka dac…Ē ka Manase.¬Ľ
\s1 K…ôyer…õn…õ ka ant…Ēf nŇč…õ Ňčeyi Yurd…õn k…ôs…ôk ntende dec d…õmp…õ m…Ē
\p 
\v 8 KusuŇčka dac…Ē ka Manase, k…Ē cusuŇčka ca Ruben k…Ē Kadu Ňčanas…Ēt…Ē nt…Ēf ya k…õ yaŇčan Yurd…õn k…ôs…ôk ntende dec d…õmp…õ m…Ē, p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē Musa w…ôcar ka MARIKI …õnas…ĒŇč Ňča di m…Ē.
\v 9 Anas…ĒŇč Ňča ant…Ēf k…ôy…õf…õ ka Arower nde k…ôŇčgb…Ēk…Ē ka Arn…ĒŇč k…ôb…ôp ka dare d…Ēk…Ē deyi aranta nde m…Ēr…Ē dac…Ē m…Ē, k…Ē p…ôgbant…ôk…ôla pa Medeba, haŇč Dib…ĒŇč,
\v 10 k…ôb…ôp ka s…ôdare sa Sih…ĒŇč w…ôb…õ w…ôka aka Am…Ēr, nw…õ …õnay…Ēn…õ w…ôb…õ w…ôka Hesbon m…Ē, haŇč nde k…ôl…ônc…ôr ka aka Am…ĒŇč.
\v 11 K…Ē Ňčas…Ēt…Ē s…Ē ant…Ēf Ňča Kaladu, nt…Ēf ya aka Kesur k…Ē aka Mahaka, t…Ēr…Ē ta H…õrm…ĒŇč, k…Ē Basan, haŇč Salka,
\v 12 k…ôl…õk…õn…õ d…õb…õ da Oku f…ôp nde Basan, nw…õ …õnay…Ēn…õ w…ôb…õ w…ôka Astarot k…Ē Edreyi m…Ē, nk…Ēn s…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ fum w…ôlp…ôs w…ôl…Ēma w…ôka aRefay. K…Ē Musa osut ab…õ akak…Ē, k'…õmbaŇč…ôr Ňča nt…Ēf yaŇčan.
\v 13 Mba aka Yisrayel ŇčanabaŇč…ôr f…õ aka Kesur k…Ē aka Mahaka nt…Ēf yaŇčan, bawo haŇč m…Ēk…Ē aka Kesur k…Ē aka Mahaka Ňčand…õ aka Yisrayel dac…Ē.
\p 
\v 14 KusuŇčka ka Lewy gb…ôc…ôr…ôm k'anat…Ēs…ĒŇč ant…Ēf Ňča k…õ. Daka nd…õ anasak…õ Ňča m…Ē d…õnay…Ēn…õ yoloŇčn…õ ny…õ anc…Ēf…õ MARIKI Kanu ka Yisrayel, p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē …õnaloku Ňča ti m…Ē.
\p 
\v 15 K…Ē Musa …Ēs…ĒŇč aka kusuŇčka ka Ruben ant…Ēf nŇč…õ d…ôcor d…ôcor.
\v 16 Ňäa Ňčanas…Ēt…Ē ant…Ēf k…ôy…õf…õ Arower nde k…ôŇčgb…Ēk…Ē ka Arn…ĒŇč k…Ē dare nd…õ deyi m…Ēr…Ē dac…Ē, p…ôgbant…ôk…ôla pa nde Medeba,
\v 17 k…ôl…õk…õn…õ Hesbon k…Ē s…ôdare f…ôp ns…õ s…ôyi nde p…ôgbant…ôk…ôla pa Dib…ĒŇč, Bam…Ēt Bal, Bet Bal Mey…ĒŇč,
\v 18 Yahas, Kedemot, Mefahat,
\v 19 Kiriyatayim, Sibma, S…õr…õt-Sahar nde t…Ēr…Ē teŇčeci mp…õ p…õnayi aranta dac…Ē m…Ē,
\v 20 Bet Pey…Ēr, p…ôt…ômb…ôl…ôr pa Piska, k…Ē Bet Yesim…Ēt,
\v 21 k…Ē s…ôdare sa p…ôgbant…ôk…ôla, k…Ē d…õb…õ da Sih…ĒŇč w…ôb…õ w…ôka Am…Ēr, nw…õ …õnayi aka Hesbon k…ôroŇč m…Ē. Musa …õnasut Ňča, Ňča k…Ē akiriŇč aka MadiyaŇč: Efy, Rekem, Cur, Hur, k…Ē Reba, nde d…õb…õ da Sih…ĒŇč aŇč…õ Ňčanand…õ d…Ēt…Ēf m…Ē.
\v 22 Aka Yisrayel Ňčanadif…õ afum al…Ēma sakma s…ôŇčan. W…ôgbal k…ôs…ônc Balam wan ka Bey…Ēr …õnayi Ňča dac…Ē.
\v 23 K…ôl…ônc…ôr ka ant…Ēf Ňča aka Ruben ntende dec d…õŇčkale m…Ē k…ônay…Ēn…õ k…ôŇčgb…Ēk…Ē ka Yurd…õn. K…õ ka aka Ruben k…ônayi kaŇčk…Ē d…ôcor d…ôcor: S…ôdare s…ôp…ĒŇč k…Ē s…ôdare s…ôf…õt sa si.
\p 
\v 24 Musa …õnas…ĒŇč ant…Ēf aka kusuŇčka ka Kadu d…ôcor d…ôcor.
\v 25 Ňäa Ňčanas…Ēt…Ē dare da Yaser, s…ôdare sa Kaladu, k…Ē ant…Ēf Ňča aka Am…ĒŇč dac…Ē haŇč dare da Arower nd…õ d…õnt…õf…ôrn…õ dare da Raba m…Ē,
\v 26 k…Ē k…ôy…õf…õ ka Hesbon haŇč dare da Ramat-Mispe, k…Ē Betonim, k…ôb…ôp ka dare da Mahanayim haŇč nde k…ôl…ônc…ôr ka ant…Ēf Ňča Debir.
\v 27 K…õ k…ôŇčan k…ôl…õk…õn…õ s…ôdare sa Bet Haram nde daranta, Bet Nimra, Suk…Ēt k…Ē Caf…ĒŇč, k…Ē p…õlp…ôs pa d…õb…õ da Sih…ĒŇč w…ôb…õ w…ôka Hesbon, k…ôl…õk…õn…õ ant…Ēf Ňča Yurd…õn k…ôs…ôk ntende dec d…õmp…õ m…Ē haŇč d…ôk…ôl…ôps…ôr da k…ôba ka Kinarot.\f + \fr 13:27 \fq K…ôba ka Kinarot\ft andeŇč…ôr s…Ē tewe ta ¬ęK…ôba ka Kalile¬Ľ\f*
\v 28 K…õ ka aka Kadu k…ônayi kaŇčk…Ē d…ôcor d…ôcor: S…ôdare s…ôp…ĒŇč k…Ē s…ôdare s…ôf…õt sa si.
\p 
\v 29 Musa …õnas…ĒŇč kusuŇčka dac…Ē ka aka Manase nt…Ēf d…ôcor d…ôcor.
\v 30 Ňäa Ňčanas…Ēt…Ē nt…Ēf ny…õ y…õnay…Ēn…õ k…ôy…õf…õ Mahanayim, Basan m…ôlm…ôl, d…õb…õ da Oku w…ôb…õ w…ôka Basan f…ôp k…ôl…õk…õn…õ ka s…ôdare w…ôco cam…ôt-tin sa c…ôbal ca ant…Ēf Ňča Yahir nde Basan,
\v 31 ant…Ēf dac…Ē Ňča Kaladu, dare da Astarot, k…Ē dare da Edreyi, s…ôdare sa Oku w…ôb…õ w…ôka Basan. Anas…ĒŇč afum dac…Ē a Makir wan ka Manase ant…Ēf ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē d…ôcor d…ôcor.
\p 
\v 32 Nt…Ēf yay…Ēk…Ē y…Ē Musa …õnas…ĒŇč…ôs nde aranta Ňča Mohab, Yurd…õn k…ôs…ôk ntende dec d…õmp…õ m…Ē, p…ônt…õf…ôr…õn…õ k…Ē Yeriko.
\v 33 Musa …õnas…ĒŇč f…õ kusuŇčka ka Lewy ant…Ēf Ňča k…õ: MARIKI, Kanu ka Yisrayel k…ônay…Ēn…õ daka daŇčan, p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē Kanu k…ônaloku Ňča m…Ē.
\c 14
\s1 K…ôyer…õn…õ ka ant…Ēf Ňča KanaŇč
\p 
\v 1 Nt…Ēf yay…Ēk…Ē y…Ē anas…ĒŇč…ôs aka Yisrayel nde ant…Ēf Ňča KanaŇč. W…ôloŇčn…õ Elasar, Yosuwe wan ka Nun, k…Ē ab…õ akiriŇč a cusuŇčka Ňčanas…ĒŇč aka Yisrayel nt…Ēf ya k…õ.
\v 2 K'aŇčkot yampuŇč-puŇč k…ôyer ka nt…Ēf ya k…õ p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē MARIKI k…ônasom Musa k…ôyer yi, cusuŇčka nc…õ cam…ôt-maŇčk…ôl…õ k…Ē kusuŇčka dac…Ē ka Manase m…Ē.
\v 3 Bawo Musa …õnas…ĒŇč ant…Ēf Ňča k…õ cusuŇčka canc…õ m…õr…ôŇč k…ôl…õk…õn…õ ka kusuŇčka dac…Ē ka Manase nde Yurd…õn k…ôs…ôk ntende dec d…õmp…õ m…Ē, mba …õnas…ĒŇč f…õ kusuŇčka ka Lewy nt…Ēf ya k…õ aka Yisrayel dac…Ē.
\v 4 Afum a awut m…õr…ôŇč a Isifu Ňčanayi cusuŇčka m…õr…ôŇč: Manase k…Ē Efrayim. Ali k…ôfo anas…ĒŇč f…õ aka kusuŇčka ka Lewy, m…õn…õ s…ôdare s…ônd…õ k…Ē c…ôs…ôk ca si, teta y…Ēc…Ēl ny…õ Ňčanas…Ēt…Ē m…Ē.
\v 5 K…Ē aka Yisrayel Ňčay…Ē p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē MARIKI k…ônasom Musa a p…ôyer ant…Ēf m…Ē.
\p 
\v 6 K…Ē aka Yuda Ňčal…Ēt…ôrn…õ Yosuwe nde Kilkal. K…Ē Kalebi wan ka Yefune w…ôka Kenisi eyif k…Ē: ¬ęM…ôna m…ônc…ôr…õ t…Ēk…Ē MARIKI k…ôloku Musa fum w…ôka Kanu te tosu m…Ē, ina k…Ē m…ôna, nde Kad…õs-Barneya.
\v 7 Meren w…ôco maŇčk…ôl…õ m'inay…Ē, t…õm nt…õ Musa w…ôcar ka MARIKI oncsom'im k…ôy…õf…õ ka Kad…õs-Barneya k…ôk…Ēt…õn mes y…Ēky…Ēk d…Ēt…Ēf, k'iŇčk…Ē il…Ēm…ôr k…Ē mes mm…õ int…ôŇčn…õ m…Ē ab…ôk…ôc Ňčosoku p…õs.
\v 8 Aw…õnc'im aŇča aŇč…õ s…ônap…õ m…Ē, Ňčanas…ĒŇč…õ afum k…ôtor b…ôk…ôc, mba ina inac…ôm…õ dim da MARIKI, Kanu kem dar…ôŇč.
\v 9 D…Ēs…Ēk dad…Ēk…Ē d…Ē Musa …õnd…õr…ôm nt…õ: ‚ÄĻIlaŇč ti f…Ē nt…Ēf yay…õ m…ônak…Ēt…õn…õ m…Ē, m…õn…õ ant…Ēf Ňčam Ňčeyi yi dac…Ē, ant…Ēf ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē Ňčendey…Ēn'am k…õ, m…ôna k…Ē awut am doru o doru, bawo m…ônc…ôŇčk…ôl dim da MARIKI, Kanu kem.‚Äļ
\v 10 Awa m…ôgb…ôtn…õ nt…õ: Nd…õk…ôl MARIKI k…ôs…ĒŇč em kiyi ka doru, p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē k…ônaloku ti m…Ē. T…õnas…Ēt…Ē meren w…ôco maŇčk…ôl…õ k…Ē k…ôcam…ôt nt…õ MARIKI k…ôncloku Musa nt…õ m…Ē, nt…õ aka Yisrayel Ňčanck…Ēt d…ôt…õgb…ôr…õ m…Ē. Nd…õk…ôl oŇč, in…õw…õ is…Ēt…Ē m…Ēk…Ē meren w…ôco cam…ôt-maas k…Ē k…ôcam…ôt.
\v 11 Is…Ēr…Ētamn…õ p…ôm…Ē d…Ēs…Ēk nd…õ Musa oncsom'im m…Ē. Is…Ēr…Ēy…Ē f…ôn…Ēnt…ôr fa k…ôwan, k…ôb…õr…õ k…Ē k…ôwur p…ôm…Ē t…õm tat…Ēk…Ē.
\v 12 M…ôs…ĒŇč'im oŇč ant…Ēf nde d…ôm…Ēr…Ē nŇč…õ MARIKI k…ônaloku ta Ňči d…Ēs…Ēk dad…Ēk…Ē m…Ē. M…ônane d…Ēs…Ēk dad…Ēk…Ē a aka Anak Ňčand…õ di s…ôdare s…ôp…ĒŇč. K…Ē Ňčalomp…ôs si nt…õ t…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ ta ater…õn…õ aŇčan Ňčantam k…ôb…õr…õ. K…Ē MARIKI k…ôsol em-…õ, indebaŇč…ôr Ňča s…ôdare saŇčan p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē nk…Ēn MARIKI k…ônalok'im ti m…Ē.
\p 
\v 13 K…Ē Yosuwe ontola Kanu teta Kalebi wan ka Yefune, k'…Ēs…ĒŇč k…Ē dare da Heb…ôr…ĒŇč.
\v 14 Ti t…õnas…ĒŇč…õ Kalebi wan ka Yefune w…ôka Kenisi p…ôs…Ēt…Ē d…Ēs…Ēk dad…Ēk…Ē k…õ ka Heb…ôr…ĒŇč, nk…õ k…ôs…Ēr…Ēyi haŇč m…Ēk…Ē bawo Kalebi …õnac…ôm…õ dim da MARIKI Kanu ka Yisrayel dar…ôŇč.
\v 15 Tewe ta Heb…ôr…ĒŇč t…Ēc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē t…õnay…Ēn…õ Kiriyat-Arba. Arba fum w…ôp…ĒŇč …õnayi aka Anak dac…Ē.
\p K…ôy…õf…õ t…õm tat…Ēk…Ē k…Ē ant…Ēf Ňč…Ēf…Ēr, k…ôwan k…ôyi f…õ s…Ē.
\c 15
\s1 Ant…Ēf Ňča kusuŇčka ka Yuda
\p 
\v 1 Ant…Ēf nŇč…õ kusuŇčka ka Yuda Ňčas…Ēt…Ē d…ôcor d…ôcor m…Ē Ňč…õnay…Ēn…õ k…ôy…õf…õ ka k…ôl…ônc…ôr ka Ed…Ēm nde t…õgb…ôr…õ ta Cin nde N…õk…õf poŇč d…ôndo k…ôca k…ôt…Ēt ka nde dec d…õmp…õ m…Ē.
\v 2 K…ôl…ônc…ôr k…ôŇčan k…ôy…õf…õ k…ôs…õr ka K…ôba K…ôdok…ôt nde k…ôca k…ôt…Ēt, k…ôb…ôp dobo da k…ôba d…Ēk…Ē d…õnt…õf…ôr…õn…õ k…Ē N…õk…õf m…Ē.
\v 3 Ip…Ēk…Ē p…õb…ôp nde k…ôca k…ôt…Ēt ka D…ôk…ôp…õ da Mek…ôlenc…ôr, k…ôcep…ôr ka Cin, k…ôp…õrn…õ ta Kad…õs Barneya, k…ôcep…ôr haŇč H…õc…ôron, k…ôp…õrn…õ ta Adar, k…Ē k…ôkaf…ôl…ôr Karka.
\v 4 Ki k…ôcep…ôr s…Ē ta Asm…ĒŇč, k…ôk…Ē s…Ē k…ônarn…õ k…ôŇčgb…Ēk…Ē ka Misira, k…ôl…ônc…ôr kayi k…ôfut…ôr nde d…ôk…ôba. K…ôl…ônc…ôr konu k…ôndeyi kaŇčk…Ē nde k…ôca k…ôt…Ēt ka nde dec d…õmp…õ m…Ē.
\p 
\v 5 Ntende dec d…õmp…õ m…Ē, k…ôl…ônc…ôr k…ônay…Ēn…õ K…ôba K…ôdok…ôt haŇč nde dobo da k…ôŇčgb…Ēk…Ē ka Yurd…õn. K…ôca k…ômeriya ka nde dec d…õmp…õ m…Ē, k…ôl…ônc…ôr k…ônccop k…ôy…õf…õ ka nde temer ta k…ôba, mp…õ peyi nde dobo da Yurd…õn m…Ē.
\v 6 K…ôl…ônc…ôr k…ôŇčan k…ôp…õrn…õ k…ôca ka Bet Hok…ôla, k…ôcep…ôr ntende k…ôca k…ômeriya haŇč Bet Araba m…Ē, k…Ē k…ôp…õrn…õ haŇč nde Tasar ta Bohan wan ka Ruben.
\v 7 K…ôy…õf…õ di k…ôl…ônc…ôr k…ôŇčk…Ē Debir k…ôcep…ôr ta m…Ēr…Ē dac…Ē nde aranta Ňča Ak…Ēr, k…ôkaf…ôl…ôr k…ôca k…ômeriya ntende Kilkal, nde p…ônt…õf…ôr…õn…õ k…Ē K…ôp…õ ka Adumim k…ôca k…ôt…Ēt ka k…ôŇčgb…Ēk…Ē. K…ôccep…ôr domun da En-S…õm…õs k…ôs…ôk, k…ôk…Ē k…ôfut…ôr nde En-Rok…õl.
\v 8 K…ôl…ônc…ôr k…ônap…õrn…õ k…ôy…õf…õ ka nde aranta Ňča B…õn-Hin…Ēm haŇč p…ôt…ômb…ôl…ôr pa aka Yebus k…ôca k…ôt…Ēt, nde p…ôy…Ēn…õ Yerusal…õm m…Ē, k…ôp…õrn…õ haŇč nde telempan pa t…Ēr…Ē mp…õ peyi aranta Ňča Hin…Ēm k…ôca nk…õ dec d…õŇčkal…õ m…Ē, k…Ē d…ôk…ôl…ôps…ôr da aranta Ňča aka Refay nde m…Ēr…Ē dac…Ē ntende k…ôca k…ômeriya.
\v 9 K…ôy…õf…õ ka nde d…ôtelempan, k…Ē k…ôl…ônc…ôr k…ônder k…ôkaf…ôl…ôr nde domun d…õncp…õ m…Ē nde N…õftowa, k…Ē k…ôsoln…õ s…ôdare sa t…Ēr…Ē ta Efr…ĒŇč, k…Ē k…ôŇčkaf…ôl…ôr s…Ē Bala nde p…ôy…Ēn…õ Kiriyat-Yeyarim m…Ē.
\v 10 Nt…õ k…ôŇčkaf…ôl…ôr Bala ntende dec d…õŇčkal…õ m…Ē, k…ôca ka nde m…Ēr…Ē ma Seyir, k…Ē k…ôncep…ôr p…ôt…ômb…ôl…ôr pa T…Ēr…Ē ta Yeyarim ntende k…ôca k…ômeriya, it'…Ēy…Ēn…õ K…õsal…ĒŇč, k…ôtor Bet S…õm…õs, k…Ē k…ôcep…ôr…õn…õ Timna.
\v 11 K…ônarn…õ p…ôt…ômb…ôl…ôr pa Ek…ôron k…ôca k…ômeriya, k…ôkaf…ôl…ôr ntende dec d…õŇčkal…õ m…Ē nde Sik…ôr…ĒŇč, k…ôcep…ôr…õn…õ nde T…Ēr…Ē ta Bala, k…ôk…Ē k…ônarn…õ Yabanel, k…Ē k…ôc…ĒŇčn…õ k…ôfut…ôr nde d…ôk…ôba.
\p 
\v 12 C…ôl…ônc…ôr ca ntende dec d…õŇčkal…õ m…Ē c…ônay…Ēn…õ K…ôba K…ôp…ĒŇč k…Ē agb…õp Ňča ki. Tant…õ t…Ē aka kusuŇčka ka Yuda Ňčanay…Ē c…ôl…ônc…ôr ca ant…Ēf ŇčaŇčan d…ôcor d…ôcor.
\p 
\v 13 K'as…ĒŇč Kalebi wan ka Yefune dare da Kiriyat Arba aka kusuŇčka ka Yuda dac…Ē, p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē MARIKI k…ônaloku ti Yosuwe m…Ē. Kiriyat-Arba k…ôy…Ēn…õ Heb…ôr…ĒŇč. Arba …õnay…Ēn…õ papa w…ôka aka Anak.
\v 14 K…Ē Kalebi …õmbaŇč…ôr at…Ēf Ňča aka Anak aŇč…õ maas d…ôndo: Sesay, Ahiman, k…Ē Talmay, Ňča Ňčanay…Ēn…õ afum a Anak.
\v 15 K…õy…õf…õ d…ôndo k…Ē Kalebi …õmp…õrn…õ k…ôk…Ēw…õk…ôrn…õ afum a dare da Debir. Debir d…Ē ancwe c…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē Kiriyat-Sefer.
\v 16 K…Ē Kalebi oloku: ¬ęM…ôna nw…õ m…ôŇčsut aka Kiriyat-Sefer m…ôbaŇč…ôr Ňča di m…Ē, is…ĒŇč'…ôm Aksa wan kem w…ôran m…ôn…õnc…õ.¬Ľ
\v 17 Otniyel wan ka Kenas w…õnc ka Kalebi …õmbaŇč…ôr Ňča di. K…Ē Kalebi …Ēs…ĒŇč k…Ē wan k…Ēn w…ôran Aksa k…ôn…õnc…õ.
\v 18 Nt…õ Aksa ender m…Ē, k'…õmp…õn…õ wos ab…ôk…ôc k…ôk…Ēwer ka kas Kalebi ab…Ēf. Aksa …ĒŇčk…Ētor s…Ēfale k…ôroŇč, k…Ē kas Kalebi eyif k…Ē: ¬ęAke m…ôfaŇč-…õ?¬Ľ
\v 19 K…Ē wan w…ôran nw…õ oloku kas f…Ē: ¬ęM…ôtolan'em, bawo m…ôs…ĒŇč'im ant…Ēf nde k…ôca k…ôt…Ēt, m…ôpoc'em s…Ē ant…Ēf nde domun d…õncp…õ m…Ē.¬Ľ K…Ē Kalebi …Ēs…ĒŇč k…Ē ant…Ēf Ňč…Ēt…Ēt nŇč…õ domun d…õncp…õ d…ônt…Ēf nde d…ôt…Ēr…Ē k…Ē nde daranta m…Ē.
\p 
\v 20 Nt…Ēf yay…Ēk…Ē y…Ē kusuŇčka ka aka Yuda Ňčanas…Ēt…Ē k…ôyer ka k…õ disr…õ d…ôcor d…ôcor.
\p 
\v 21 S…ôdare ns…õ s…ôyi d…ôk…ôl…ôps…ôr da ant…Ēf Ňča kusuŇčka ka Yuda m…Ē ntende k…ôl…ônc…ôr ka Ed…Ēm nde N…õk…õf k…ôca k…ôt…Ēt ntende dec d…õmp…õ m…Ē. Si s…ônay…Ēn…õ: Kab…ôcel, Eder, Yakur,
\v 22 Kina, Dimona, Adada,
\v 23 K…õd…õs, Hac…Ēr, Yitnan,
\v 24 Sif, Telem, Beyal…Ēt,
\v 25 Hac…Ēr-Hadata, Keriy…Ēt-H…õc…ôron nk…õ k…ôy…Ēn…õ Hac…Ēr m…Ē,
\v 26 Amam, Sema, Molada,
\v 27 Hasar-Kada, Hesbon, Bet Palet,
\v 28 Hasar-Suhal, Berseba, Bisiyoteya,
\v 29 Bala, Hiyim, H…õs…õm,
\v 30 ∆źltoladu, Kesil, Horma,
\v 31 Cik…ôlak, Madamana, SaŇčsana,
\v 32 Lebayot, Silhim, Ayin k…Ē Rimon. K…ôb…õr…õn…õ ka s…ôdare sas…Ēk…Ē f…ôp s…ôk…Ē s…ôdare w…ôco m…õr…ôŇč k…Ē cam…ôt-maŇčk…ôl…õ (29) k…Ē s…ôdare s…ôf…õt sa si.
\p 
\v 33 S…ôdare ns…õ s…ôyi aranta nde p…ôntils…ôrn…õ pa ant…Ēf Ňča tant…Ēf m…Ē: ∆źst…Ēl, Corha, Asna,
\v 34 Sanowa, En-Kanim, Tapuwa, Enam,
\v 35 Yarmut, Adulam, Soko, Aseka,
\v 36 Sarayim, Aditayim, k…Ē Kedera nk…õ aŇčwe s…Ē Kederotayim m…Ē. S…ôdare w…ôco k…Ē maŇčk…ôl…õ (14) k…Ē s…ôdare s…ôf…õt sa si.
\p 
\v 37 Cenan, Hadasa, Mik…ôdal-Kad
\v 38 Dilhan, Mispe, Yok…ôtel,
\v 39 Lakis, Boc…ôkat, Ekil…ĒŇč,
\v 40 Kabon, Lahamas, Kit…ôlis,
\v 41 Keder…Ēt, Bet Dak…ĒŇč, Nahama, k…Ē Makeda. Si s…ônay…Ēn…õ s…ôdare w…ôco k…Ē cam…ôt-tin (16) k…Ē s…ôdare s…ôf…õt sa si.
\p 
\v 42 Libana, H…õt…õr, Asan,
\v 43 Yifta, Asna, Necibi,
\v 44 Keyila, Ak…ôsibu k…Ē Maresa. Si s…ônay…Ēn…õ s…ôdare cam…ôt-maŇčk…ôl…õ (9) k…Ē s…ôdare s…ôf…õt sa si.
\p 
\v 45 Ek…ôron, k…Ē s…ôdare s…ôf…õt sa di,
\v 46 k…ôy…õf…õ ka Ek…ôron s…ôdare ns…õ s…ôyi Asdodi k…ôs…ôk m…Ē f…ôp,
\v 47 Asdodi k…Ē s…ôdare s…ôf…õt sa di, Kasa k…Ē s…ôdare s…ôf…õt ns…õ s…ôyi di k…ôs…ôk m…Ē, haŇč nde k…ôŇčgb…Ēk…Ē ka Misira, haŇč nde K…ôba K…ôp…ĒŇč k…Ē agb…õp Ňča ki.
\p 
\v 48 Nde d…ôm…Ēr…Ē: Samir, Yatir, Soko,
\v 49 Dana, Kiriyat-Sana, nde p…ôy…Ēn…õ Debir m…Ē,
\v 50 Anaba, Esitemo, Anim,
\v 51 Kos…õŇč, Holon k…Ē Kilo. Si s…ôy…Ēn…õ s…ôdare w…ôco k…Ē pin (11) k…Ē s…ôdare s…ôf…õt sa si.
\p 
\v 52 Araba, Ruma, ∆źsaŇč,
\v 53 Yanum, Bet Tapuwa, Afeka,
\v 54 Humeta, Kiriyat-Arba nde p…ôy…Ēn…õ Heb…ôr…ĒŇč m…Ē, k…Ē Cih…Ēr. Si s…ôy…Ēn…õ s…ôdare cam…ôt-maŇčk…ôl…õ (9) k…Ē s…ôdare s…ôf…õt sa si.
\p 
\v 55 Mahon, Karm…õl, Sif, Yuta,
\v 56 Yisrel, Y…Ēkdeham, Sanowa,
\v 57 Kayin, Kibeya, k…Ē Timna. Si s…ôy…Ēn…õ s…ôdare w…ôco (10) k…Ē s…ôdare s…ôf…õt sa si.
\p 
\v 58 Halhul, Bet Cur, Ked…Ēr,
\v 59 Maharat, Bet Anot, k…Ē ∆źlt…ôkon. Si s…ônay…Ēn…õ s…ôdare cam…ôt-tin (6) k…Ē s…ôdare s…ôf…õt sa si.
\p 
\v 60 Kiriyat Bal nde p…ôy…Ēn…õ Kiriyat-Yeyarim m…Ē, k…Ē Raba, si s…ônay…Ēn…õ s…ôdare m…õr…ôŇč (2) k…Ē s…ôdare s…ôf…õt sa si.
\p 
\v 61 Nde d…ôt…õgb…ôr…õ: Bet Araba, Midin, Sekaka,
\v 62 Nib…ôsan, Hir-Mela\f + \fr 15:62 \fq Hir-Mela\ft ti t…Ēy…Ēn…õ ¬ęDare da M…õr.¬Ľ\f*, k…Ē En-Kedi, si s…ônay…Ēn…õ s…ôdare cam…ôt-tin (6) k…Ē s…ôdare s…ôf…õt sa si.
\p 
\v 63 Aka kusuŇčka ka Yuda Ňčanatam f…õ k…ôbaŇč…ôr aYebus aŇč…õ Ňčanand…õ Yerusal…õm m…Ē, k…Ē aYebus Ňčand…õ k…Ē aka kusuŇčka ka Yuda nde Yerusal…õm haŇč m…Ēk…Ē.
\c 16
\s1 Ant…Ēf Ňča k…õ Ňča kusuŇčka ka Isifu
\p 
\v 1 Nt…Ēf ny…õ anas…ĒŇč aka kusuŇčka ka Isifu m…Ē y…õnay…Ēn…õ, nt…õ aŇčkot yampuŇč-puŇč m…Ē, k…ôy…õf…õ ka Yurd…õn nde Yeriko k…ôs…ôk k…ôca ka ntende domun da Yeriko ntende dec d…õmp…õ m…Ē, k…ôcep…ôr ka d…ôt…õgb…ôr…õ k…ôp…õrn…õ ka Yeriko k…ôk…Ē ka nde d…ôm…Ēr…Ē ma Betel.
\v 2 Ki k…ôcep…ôr Betel k…Ē Lus, k…ôk…Ē k…ôcep…ôr k…ôca ka k…ôl…ônc…ôr ka aka Arki nde Atarot,
\v 3 k…ôtor ntende dec d…õŇčkal…õ m…Ē, k…ôca ka k…ôl…ônc…ôr ka aYaf…ôlet haŇč nde ant…Ēf Ňča Bet Horon-Tant…Ēf, haŇč Keser k…ôk…Ēfut…ôr nde d…ôk…ôba.
\v 4 K…õ kaŇčk…Ē cusuŇčka ca Efrayim k…Ē Manase awut a Isifu Ňčanas…Ēt…Ē.
\p 
\v 5 Ant…Ēf Ňča aka Efrayim Ňč…Ē ŇčaŇč…õ d…ôcor d…ôcor: K…ôl…ônc…ôr k…Ē k…õ k…ôŇčan k…ônay…Ēn…õ ntende dec d…õmp…õ m…Ē, Atarot Adar haŇč Bet Horon Tak…ôroŇč.
\v 6 K…ôl…ônc…ôr k…ônab…ôp K…ôba K…ôp…ĒŇč ntende dec d…õŇčkal…õ m…Ē, k…ôca ka Mik…ômetat ntende k…ôca k…ômeriya. K…ôkaf…ôl…ôr ntende dec d…õmp…õ m…Ē, k…ôca ka Tahanat-Silo, k…ôcali ntende dec d…õmp…õ m…Ē, k…ôca ka Yanoha.
\v 7 K…Ē k…ôy…õf…õ Yanoha, k…Ē k…ôntor Atarot k…Ē Nahara, k…Ē k…ôŇčk…Ē k…ôs…ôŇčk…ôl…ôr Yeriko, k…Ē k…ôŇčk…Ē k…ônarn…õ Yurd…õn.
\v 8 K…ôy…õf…õ Tapuwa , k…Ē k…ôl…ônc…ôr k…ôŇčk…Ē k…ôca nk…õ dec d…õŇčkal…õ m…Ē, ntende k…ôŇčgb…Ēk…Ē ka Kana k…ôk…Ēnarn…õ nde d…ôk…ôba. K…õ kaŇčk…Ē k…Ē kusuŇčka ka Efrayim Ňčanas…Ēt…Ē d…ôcor d…ôcor,
\v 9 k…ôl…õk…õn…õ ka s…ôdare ns…õ anac…ômb…ôr…õ aka Efrayim nde ant…Ēf Ňča k…õ ka Manase m…Ē, k…ôl…õk…õn…õ s…ôdare s…ôf…õt sa si.
\v 10 Ňäa s…Ē ŇčanabaŇč…ôr f…õ aKanaŇč aŇč…õ Ňčand…õ Keser m…Ē, aKanaŇč Ňčand…õ afum a Efrayim dac…Ē haŇč m…Ēk…Ē, mba Ňčayi acar aŇč…õ Ňčamb…ôc…õ afum a Efrayim m…Ē dac…Ē.
\c 17
\p 
\v 1 Anac…ômb…ôr…õ s…Ē kusuŇčka ka Manase coco ca Isifu at…Ēf Ňča k…õ. Awut a Makir coco ca Manase papa w…ôka Kaladu, Ňčanas…Ēt…Ē ant…Ēf, bawo fum w…ôka k…ôwan …õnayi. Anac…ômb…ôr…õ Ňča Kaladu k…Ē Basan.
\v 2 Anac…ômb…ôr…õ s…Ē afum a Manase alp…ôs ant…Ēf Ňča k…õ d…ôcor d…ôcor, k…ôl…õk…õn…õ afum a Abiyeser, a Helek, a Asriyel, a S…õk…õm, a Hefer, k…Ē afum a Semida. Awut arkun a Manase wan ka Isifu Ňčanayi akak…Ē d…ôcor d…ôcor.
\p 
\v 3 Celofahad wan ka Hefer, wan ka Kaladu, wan ka Makir, wan ka Manase, …õnay…Ē f…õ wan w…ôrkun, m…õn…õ awut aran. Mewe maŇčan m…õm…õ: Mahala, Noha, Hok…ôla, Milka, k…Ē Tirsa.
\v 4 K…Ē awut aran aŇč…õ ŇčaŇčk…Ē f…Ēr ya w…ôloŇčn…õ Elasar, Yosuwe wan ka Nun k…Ē akiriŇč, k…Ē Ňčaloku: ¬ęMARIKI k…ônasom Musa a pas…ĒŇč s…Ē s…ôna k…õ aw…õnc asu dac…Ē.¬Ľ K'as…ĒŇč Ňča k…õ aw…õnc aŇčan dac…Ē p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē MARIKI k…ônaloku ti m…Ē.
\v 5 K'anac…ômb…ôr…õ Manase nt…Ēf w…ôco, k…ôl…õk…õn…õ ant…Ēf Ňča Kaladu k…Ē Ňča Basan nŇč…õ Ňčeyi Yurd…õn k…ôca k…ôŇčk…Ē ntende dec d…õmp…õ m…Ē,
\v 6 bawo awut aran a kusuŇčka ka Manase Ňčanas…Ēt…Ē k…õ awut arkun a kusuŇčka …Ēn dac…Ē. K…Ē ant…Ēf Ňča Kaladu Ňč…Ēy…Ēn…õ Ňča awut arkun alp…ôs a kusuŇčka ka Manase ak…Ē.
\p 
\v 7 K…ôl…ônc…ôr ka Manase k…ônck…Ē k…ôy…õf…õ As…õr haŇč Mik…ômetat, nde p…ônt…õf…ôr…õn…õ k…Ē S…õk…õm, k…ôk…Ē k…ôca k…ôt…Ēt ntende ant…Ēf Ňča aka En-Tapuwa.
\v 8 At…Ēf Ňča Tapuwa Ňča Manase Ňč…õnayi, mba dare da Tapuwa, nd…õ d…õnayi k…ôl…ônc…ôr ka Manase k…ôroŇč m…Ē, aka kusuŇčka ka Efrayim Ňč…Ē ŇčanapaŇčn…õ di.
\v 9 K…ôl…ônc…ôr kaŇčk…Ē k…ônctor nde k…ôŇčgb…Ēk…Ē ka Kana. S…ôdare s…ôl…Ēma sa Efrayim s…ônayi s…ôdare sa Manase dac…Ē nde k…ôca k…ôt…Ēt ka k…ôŇčgb…Ēk…Ē ntende dec d…õmp…õ m…Ē. Ntende dec d…õŇčkal…õ m…Ē, k…ôl…ônc…ôr ka Manase k…ôncfut…ôr d…ôk…ôba.
\v 10 It…Ē tat…Ēk…Ē ant…Ēf Ňča kusuŇčka ka Efrayim Ňč…õnayi k…ôca k…ôt…Ēt ka nde dec d…õmp…õ m…Ē, k'ant…Ēf Ňča Manase Ňčeyi k…ôca k…ômeriya. K…ôba k…ônay…Ēn…õ Ňča k…ôl…ônc…ôr ka nde dec d…õŇčkal…õ m…Ē, ant…Ēf ŇčaŇčan Ňč…õmb…ôp ant…Ēf Ňča As…õr ntende k…ôca k…ômeriya, k…Ē Ňč…õmb…ôp ant…Ēf Ňča Yisakar ntende dec d…õmp…õ m…Ē.
\v 11 Anac…ômb…ôr…õ kusuŇčka ka Manase s…ôdare ns…õ nde nt…Ēf ya As…õr k…Ē Yisakar: Bet San, Yib…ôleham, afum aka D…Ēr , afum aka En-D…Ēr, afum aka Tahanak, k…Ē afum aka Mekido, s…ôdare sa Nafet maas, k…Ē s…ôdare s…ôf…õt s…ôf…õt sa si f…ôp.
\v 12 Aka Manase Ňčanatam f…õ k…ôbaŇč ka s…ôdare sas…Ēk…Ē, bawo aka KanaŇč s…Ē ŇčafaŇč k…ôyi ka at…Ēf ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē.
\v 13 Nt…õ aka Yisrayel Ňčandes…Ēt…Ē f…ôn…Ēnt…ôr m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčanc…ômb…ôr aka KanaŇč y…õb…ôc yaŇčan, mba Ňčanatam f…õ k…ôbaŇč…ôr Ňča ant…Ēf m…ôlm…ôl.
\p 
\v 14 K…Ē afum a Isifu Ňčaloku Yosuwe nt…õ m…Ē: ¬ęTa ake t…Ē m…ôs…ĒŇč em tofo tin gboŇč k…õ-…õ? M…ônc…ôr…õ a afum em Ňčala, bawo k…ôtolan…õ ka MARIKI k…ôs…Ēr…Ēy'im dar…ôŇč haŇč nd…õk…ôl.¬Ľ
\v 15 K…Ē Yosuwe oloku Ňča: ¬ęK…Ē m…ôy…Ē afum alar…ôm-…õ, m…ôp…õ nde d…ôkulum, m…ôk…Ē m…ôc…õp…ôs k…ôfo nde nt…Ēf ya aPerisi k…Ē aRefay, bawo ant…Ēf nde m…Ēr…Ē ma Efrayim Ňč…õw…õk…õn'am.¬Ľ
\v 16 K…Ē aka Isifu Ňčaloku: ¬ęAnt…Ēf Ňča nde m…Ēr…Ē nŇč…õ Ňč…Ēf…Ēt…ôŇčn…õ su k…ônd…õ. Ta m…õr…ôŇč ta ti, cibil ca k…ôwan ca f…õc c…ôyi nda aKanaŇč aŇč…õ Ňčayi nde aranta Ňča di m…Ē, aŇč…õ Ňčayi aranta Ňča Bet San k…Ē s…ôdare s…ôf…õt sa di, k…Ē ak…Ē Ňčayi nde aranta Ňča Yisrel nde m…Ēr…Ē dac…Ē m…Ē.¬Ľ
\v 17 K…Ē Yosuwe oloku aka cusuŇčka ca Isifu, Manase k…Ē Efrayim: ¬ęAfum alar…ôm Ňč…Ē n…ôy…Ēn…õ, k…Ē n…ôy…Ē s…Ē f…ôn…Ēnt…ôr. N…ôf…Ēdey…Ē k…ôfo kin gboŇč,
\v 18 mba n…ôŇčy…Ē ant…Ēf Ňča d…ôm…Ēr…Ē m…ôlm…ôl. Ali nt…õ Ňč…Ēy…Ēn…õ kulum m…Ē, n…ôndec…õp…ôs ki, nt…Ēf f…ôp yendey…Ēn…õ yonu. N…ôndebaŇč…ôr aKanaŇč ant…Ēf ŇčaŇčan, ali nt…õ Ňčay…Ē cibil ca f…õc k…Ē Ňčay…Ē s…Ē f…ôn…Ēnt…ôr m…Ē.¬Ľ
\c 18
\s1 K…ôyer ka nt…Ēf cusuŇčka c…ôlp…ôs
\p 
\v 1 K…Ē aka Yisrayel f…ôp ŇčaloŇčkan…õ Silo, k…Ē Ňčac…ômb…ôr di aŇčgbancan Ňča d…ôk…ôb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē Kanu. ŇäanabaŇč ant…Ēf, Ňčeyi oŇč kiyi k…ôŇčan.
\v 2 Mba p…ônc…ôm…õ cusuŇčka cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč ca aka Yisrayel aŇč…õ Ňčanat…Ē-s…Ēt…Ē k…ôr…õsna k…õ k…ôŇčan m…Ē.
\v 3 K…Ē Yosuwe oloku aka Yisrayel: ¬ęAke t…õm t…Ē n…ôndesak k…ôd…õnc…ôs k…ôl…õk ka k…õ nk…õ MARIKI, Kanu ka awisi aŇča k…ôs…ĒŇč'un m…Ē?
\v 4 N…ôwur…õ afum maas maas d…ôcusuŇčka d…ôcusuŇčka. Isom Ňča Ňčandey…õf…õ Ňčak…Ēt…õn…õ ant…Ēf Ňčak…Ēkc…õ Ňčapirint Ňči, Ňčader Ňčas…ĒŇč'im.
\v 5 Ňäandeyer…õn…õ ant…Ēf mopoc cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč. Aka Yuda ŇčaŇčk…Ēyi N…õk…õf, ant…Ēf ŇčaŇčan ntende k…ôca k…ôt…Ēt ka nde dec d…õmp…õ m…Ē, k…Ē aka kusuŇčka ka Isifu Ňča Ňčayi nde ant…Ēf ŇčaŇčan ntende k…ôca k…ômeriya.
\v 6 K…Ē n…ôna n…ôk…Ē n…ôk…Ēkc…õ at…Ēf mofo cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč, n…ôde n…ôlok'im ti nn…Ē. K…ôkot'on k'inder yampuŇč-puŇč f…Ēr ya MARIKI Kanu kosu kiriŇč.
\v 7 Mba aLewy Ňča Ňčaf…Ēs…Ēt…Ē ant…Ēf Ňča k…õ n…ôna dac…Ē, bawo Ňča Ňčat…Ēmp…ôr teta MARIKI, ti t…Ēy…Ēn…õ k…õ k…ôŇčan. K…Ē Kadu, Ruben k…Ē kusuŇčka dac…Ē ka Manase Ňčanas…Ēt…Ē nde Yurd…õn k…ôs…ôk ntende dec d…õmp…õ m…Ē k…õ k…ôŇčan nk…õ Musa w…ôcar ka MARIKI …õnas…ĒŇč Ňča m…Ē.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 8 K…Ē afum aŇč…õ Ňčay…õf…õ, k…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē. Yosuwe …õnaloku ak…Ē …õnasom k…ôk…Ēcic m…õgb…õk…ôr…õ maŇčan ma ant…Ēf m…Ē nt…õ: ¬ęN…ôk…Ē n…ôn…ĒŇčk…ôr ant…Ēf, n…ôk…Ēkc…õ n…ôder n…ôlok'im, bawo k…ôkot'on k'inder yampuŇč-puŇč f…Ēr ya MARIKI kiriŇč teta k…ôyer…õn…õ ka ant…Ēf nde Silo.¬Ľ
\v 9 K…Ē afum aŇč…õ ŇčaŇčk…Ē, k…Ē Ňčancali ant…Ēf, k…Ē Ňčacic d…ôbuk t…Ēk…Ēkc…õ ta mofo mm…õ cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč, s…ôdare s…ôdare. K…Ē Ňčaluks…ôrn…õ nn…Ē Yosuwe eyi m…Ē, nde saŇčka sa Silo.
\v 10 K…Ē Yosuwe oŇčkot…õ Ňča yampuŇč-puŇč f…Ēr ya MARIKI kiriŇč nde Silo, k'eyer ant…Ēf Ňča Yisrayel afum akaŇč…õ dac…Ē, p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē anayer m…Ē.
\s1 Ant…Ēf Ňča BeŇčyamin
\p 
\v 11 K'aŇčkot yampuŇč-puŇč k…ôyer ka k…õ ka kusuŇčka ka aka BeŇčyamin d…ôcor d…ôcor, anc…ômb…ôr Ňča ant…Ēf nde kusuŇčka ka Yuda k…Ē kusuŇčka ka Isifu dac…Ē.
\v 12 K…ôca k…ômeriya ka nde dec d…õmp…õ m…Ē, k…Ē k…ôl…ônc…ôr k…ôŇčan k…ôncop k…ôy…õf…õ ka Yurd…õn. K…Ē k…ômp…õrn…õ p…ôt…ômb…ôl…ôr pa Yeriko k…ôca k…ômeriya, k…Ē k…ômp…õrn…õ m…Ēr…Ē ntende dec d…õŇčkal…õ m…Ē, k…ôk…Ē k…ôfut…ôr ntende d…ôt…õgb…ôr…õ ta Bet Aw…õn.
\v 13 K…ôl…ônc…ôr k…ôŇčan k…ôccep…ôr Lus, k…Ē nde p…ôt…ômb…ôl…ôr pa Lus, nde p…ôy…Ēn…õ Betel k…ôca k…ôt…Ēt ka ntende dec d…õmp…õ m…Ē, k…Ē k…ôntor Atarot Adar, k…Ē k…ômp…õ t…Ēr…Ē t…Ēk…Ē teyi k…ôca k…ôt…Ēt Bet Horon-Tant…Ēf m…Ē.
\v 14 Ntende dec d…õŇčkal…õ m…Ē, k…Ē k…ôl…ônc…ôr k…ôŇčkaf…ôl…ôr ntende k…ôca k…ôt…Ēt k…ôy…õf…õ ka t…Ēr…Ē nt…õ t…õnt…õf…ôr…õn…õ k…Ē Bet Horon k…ôca k…ôt…Ēt m…Ē, k…Ē k…ôŇčk…Ē k…ônarn…õ Kiriyat Bal, nde p…ôy…Ēn…õ Kiriyat-Yeyarim, dare da aka kusuŇčka ka Yuda. Tat…Ēk…Ē t…Ē k…ôl…ônc…ôr ka ntende dec d…õŇčkal…õ m…Ē k…ônaf…ônt…ôr…õ.
\p 
\v 15 K…ôl…ônc…ôr ka k…ôca k…ôt…Ēt nde dec d…õmp…õ m…Ē k…ôcy…õf…õ Kiriyat-Yeyarim, k…ôk…Ēnarn…õ nde domun d…õncp…õ m…Ē nde N…õftowa.
\v 16 K…ôl…ônc…ôr kaŇčk…Ē k…ôctor d…ôk…ôl…ôps…ôr da m…Ēr…Ē mm…õ m…õnt…õf…ôr…õn…õ k…Ē aranta Ňča B…õn-Hin…Ēm m…Ē, k…ôca k…ômeriya ka nde dec d…õmp…õ aranta Ňča aRefay m…Ē. K…ôsoln…õ aranta Ňča Hin…Ēm nde m…Ēr…Ē dac…Ē, p…ôt…ômb…ôl…ôr pa aYebus ntende k…ôca k…ôt…Ēt ka nde dec d…õmp…õ m…Ē, ki k…ôtor haŇč En-Rok…õl.
\v 17 K…Ē k…ôŇčkaf…ôl…ôr k…ôca k…ômeriya ka nde dec d…õmp…õ m…Ē, k…ôk…Ē k…ônarn…õ En-S…õm…õs, k…ôcep…ôr k…ôk…Ē k…ôsump…ôr Kelilot, nde p…ônt…õf…ôr…õn…õ k…Ē K…ôp…õ ka Adumim, k…ôk…Ē k…ôtor nde Tasar ta Bohan wan ka Ruben.
\v 18 K…ôk…Ē k…ôcep…ôr p…ôt…ômb…ôl…ôr pa k…ôca k…ômeriya ka t…Ēr…Ē nde dec d…õmp…õ m…Ē, nde p…ônt…õf…ôr…õn…õ k…Ē Araba, k…Ē k…ôntor nde Araba disr…õ.
\v 19 K…ôl…ônc…ôr kaŇčk…Ē k…ôccep…ôr nde p…ôt…ômb…ôl…ôr pa k…ôca k…ômeriya ka nde dec d…õmp…õ Bet Hok…ôla m…Ē, k…ôk…Ēfut…ôr nde dobo da K…ôba K…ôdok…ôt ntende k…ôca k…ômeriya ka nde dec demp…õ m…Ē, ntende dobo da k…ôŇčgb…Ēk…Ē ka Yurd…õn k…ôca k…ôt…Ēt ka nde dec d…õŇčkal…õ m…Ē, tat…Ēk…Ē t…Ē k…ôl…ônc…ôr ka k…ôca k…ôt…Ēt k…ônaf…ônt…ôr…õ.
\v 20 Ntende dec d…õmp…õ m…Ē, Yurd…õn y…õnay…Ēn…õ k…ôl…ônc…ôr.
\p K…õ ka aka kusuŇčka ka BeŇčyamin k…ônayi kaŇčk…Ē d…ôcor d…ôcor, k…Ē c…ôl…ônc…ôr c…ôŇčan f…ôp.
\p 
\v 21 S…ôdare sa kusuŇčka ka BeŇčyamin s…ônayi ns…õ d…ôcor d…ôcor: Yeriko, Bet Hok…ôla, Hemek-Kecic,
\v 22 Bet Araba, Cemarayim, Betel,
\v 23 Awim, Para, Hofra,
\v 24 Kefar-Amoni, Hofni k…Ē Keba, s…ôdare w…ôco k…Ē m…õr…ôŇč (12) k…Ē s…ôdare s…ôf…õt sa si.
\p 
\v 25 Kabay…ĒŇč, Rama, Beyerot,
\v 26 Mispe, Kefira, Mosa,
\v 27 Rek…õm, Yirpel, Tarala,
\v 28 Cela, Helef, Yebus yi y…Ēy…Ēn…õ Yerusal…õm, Kibeya k…Ē Kiriyat, s…ôdare w…ôco k…Ē maŇčk…ôl…õ (14) k…Ē s…ôdare s…ôf…õt sa si. K…õ ka aka kusuŇčka ka BeŇčyamin k…ônayi kaŇčk…Ē d…ôcor d…ôcor.
\c 19
\s1 Ant…Ēf Ňča kusuŇčka ka Simey…ĒŇč
\p 
\v 1 Topoc ta m…õr…ôŇč mp…õ anawur…õ m…Ē p…õnay…Ēn…õ pa kusuŇčka ka Simey…ĒŇč d…ôcor d…ôcor. Ňäa Ňčanas…Ēt…Ē k…õ k…ôŇčan awut a Yuda dac…Ē.
\v 2 K…Ē Ňča Ňčas…Ēt…Ē k…õ nk…õ k…ôy…Ēn…õ s…ôdare sa Berseba, Seba, Molada,
\v 3 Hasar-Suhala, Bala, H…õs…õm,
\v 4 ∆źltoladu, Betula, Horma,
\v 5 Cik…ôlak, Bet Markabot, Hasar-Susa,
\v 6 Bet Lebayot k…Ē Saruh…õn, s…ôdare w…ôco k…Ē maas (13) k…Ē s…ôdare s…ôf…õt sa si.
\v 7 Ayin, Rimon, H…õt…õr k…Ē Asan, s…ôdare maŇčk…ôl…õ k…Ē s…ôdare s…ôf…õt sa si,
\v 8 k…ôl…õk…õn…õ ka s…ôdare s…ôf…õt s…ôf…õt s…ôk…Ē s…ôn…ĒŇčk…ôr s…ôdare sas…Ēk…Ē m…Ē f…ôp, haŇč nde Balat-Ber nde p…ôy…Ēn…õ Ramat-N…õk…õf m…Ē. K…õ ka aka kusuŇčka ka Simey…ĒŇč k…ônayi kaŇčk…Ē d…ôcor d…ôcor.
\v 9 At…Ēf Ňča k…õ ka kusuŇčka ka Simey…ĒŇč, k…õ ka kusuŇčka ka Yuda Ňč'anabel…ôr ki, bawo k…õ k…ôŇčan k…ônab…õk…ôr Ňča p…ôp…ĒŇč, k…õ k…ôŇčan disr…õ anas…Ēt…Ēn…õ kusuŇčka ka Simey…ĒŇč k…õ k…ôŇčan.
\s1 Ant…Ēf Ňča Sabulon
\p 
\v 10 Topoc ta maas p…õnay…Ēn…õ k…õ ka kusuŇčka ka Sabulon d…ôcor d…ôcor. K…ôl…ônc…ôr k…ôŇčan k…ônak…Ē haŇč Saridi.
\v 11 K…ôp…õrn…õ k…ôca nk…õ dec d…õŇčkal…õ m…Ē, k…Ē k…ôca ka Marala, k…ôk…Ē k…ôgbuŇč…õn…õ Dabas…õt, k…ôy…õf…õ d…ônda k…ôk…Ē nde k…ôŇčgb…Ēk…Ē ka Yokonam tekiriŇč m…Ē.
\v 12 Nt…õ k…ôy…õf…õ Saridi m…Ē, k…Ē k…ôl…ônc…ôr k…ôŇčkaf…ôl…õ k…ôca nk…õ dec d…õmp…õ m…Ē ntende k…ôl…ônc…ôr ka Kisl…Ēt-Tabor, k…ôk…Ē k…ônarn…õ Daberat, k…Ē k…ôp…õrn…õ Yafiya.
\v 13 K…Ē k…ôy…õf…õ d…ôndo k…Ē k…ôncep…ôr ntende dec d…õmp…õ Kat-Hefer, k…Ē Et-Katsin, k…ôk…Ē k…ônarn…õ Rimon, k…Ē k…ôkaf…ôl…ôr haŇč Neha.
\v 14 K…Ē k…ôl…ônc…ôr kaŇčk…Ē k…ôŇčk…Ē k…ôkaf…ôl…ôr ntende k…ôca k…ômeriya ka nde dec d…õmp…õ Hanaton m…Ē, k…ôk…Ē k…ôfut…ôr nde m…Ēr…Ē dac…Ē nde aranta Ňča Yifta-El.
\v 15 K…õ k…ôŇčan k…ôl…õk…õn…õ Katat, Nahalal, Simr…ĒŇč, Yidala, k…Ē Bet L…õh…õm. Ňäanas…Ēt…Ē s…ôdare w…ôco k…Ē m…õr…ôŇč (12), k…Ē s…ôdare s…ôf…õt sa si.
\v 16 Ant…Ēf Ňča k…õ Ňča aka Sabulon k…ônayi kaŇčk…Ē d…ôcor d…ôcor, s…ôdare s…ôp…ĒŇč sas…Ēk…Ē k…Ē s…ôdare s…ôf…õt sa si.
\s1 Ant…Ēf Ňča Yisakar
\p 
\v 17 Topoc ta maŇčk…ôl…õ p…õnay…Ēn…õ pa Yisakar, k…õ ka kusuŇčka ka Yisakar d…ôcor d…ôcor.
\v 18 K…ôl…ônc…ôr k…ôŇčan k…ônak…Ē haŇč Yisrel, Kesul…Ēt, Sunem,
\v 19 Hafarayim, Siy…ĒŇč, Anaharat,
\v 20 Rabit, Kisiyon, Ab…õc,
\v 21 R…õm…õt, En-Kanim, En-Hada k…Ē Bet Pac…õc.
\v 22 K…ôl…ônc…ôr k…ôŇčan k…ôŇčk…Ē k…ôgbuŇč…õn…õ Tabor, Sahacima, Bet S…õm…õs, k…ôk…Ē k…ôfut…ôr Yurd…õn, s…ôdare w…ôco k…Ē cam…ôt-tin (16) k…Ē s…ôdare s…ôf…õt sa si.
\v 23 K…õ ka kusuŇčka ka aka Yisakar k…ônayi kaŇčk…Ē d…ôcor d…ôcor, s…ôdare s…ôp…ĒŇč sas…Ēk…Ē k…Ē s…ôf…õt sa si.
\s1 Ant…Ēf Ňča As…õr
\p 
\v 24 Topoc ta k…ôcam…ôt mp…õ p…õnawur m…Ē p…õnay…Ēn…õ pa kusuŇčka ka As…õr d…ôcor d…ôcor.
\v 25 Ňäa Ňčanay…Ē k…ôl…ônc…ôr k…ôy…õf…õ ka H…õlkat, k…ôk…Ē Hali, B…õt…õn, Aksaf,
\v 26 Alamelek, Hamhadu k…Ē Misal, k…ôk…Ē k…ôgbuŇč…õn…õ t…Ēr…Ē ta Karm…õl k…Ē Sih…Ēr-Libnat,
\v 27 k…Ē k…ôŇčk…Ē k…ôkaf…ôl…ôr k…ôca nk…õ dec d…õmp…õ m…Ē, nde Bet Dak…ĒŇč, k…ôk…Ē s…Ē k…ôgbuŇč…õn…õ Sabulon, k…Ē nde aranta Ňča Yifta-El nde m…Ēr…Ē dac…Ē ntende k…ôca k…ômeriya ka nde dec d…õmp…õ Bet Hemek k…Ē Neyel m…Ē, k…ôk…Ē k…ônarn…õ Kabul, k…ôca k…ômeriya,
\v 28 k…Ē k…ôca ka Eb…ôr…ĒŇč, Rehobo, Hamon k…Ē Kana, haŇč Sid…ĒŇč dare d…Ēp…ĒŇč.
\v 29 K…Ē k…ôl…ônc…ôr kaŇčk…Ē k…ôŇčk…Ē k…ôkaf…ôl…ôr k…ôca ka Rama haŇč nde dare da saŇčka da Tir, k…Ē k…ôca ka Hosa, k…Ē k…ôŇčk…Ē k…ôfut…ôr nde d…ôk…ôba, k…ôcep…ôr…õn…õ ta Ak…ôsibu,
\v 30 k…ôl…õk…õn…õ ka Huma, Afek k…Ē Rehobo, s…ôdare w…ôco m…õr…ôŇč k…Ē m…õr…ôŇč (22) k…Ē s…ôdare s…ôf…õt sa si.
\v 31 K…õ ka kusuŇčka ka As…õr k…ônayi kaŇčk…Ē d…ôcor d…ôcor, s…ôdare s…ôp…ĒŇč sas…Ēk…Ē k…Ē s…ôf…õt sa si.
\s1 Ant…Ēf Ňča Naftali
\p 
\v 32 Topoc ta cam…ôt-tin p…õnay…Ēn…õ k…õ ka kusuŇčka ka Naftali d…ôcor d…ôcor.
\v 33 K…ôl…ônc…ôr k…ôŇčan k…ônck…Ē k…ôy…õf…õ ka Helef k…Ē k…ôt…Ēk k…ôp…ĒŇč k…ôŇčk…Ē k…ôyi Cananim k…ôs…ôk m…Ē, k…ôcep…ôr ta Adami N…õk…õb k…Ē Yabanel, haŇč Lakum, k…Ē k…ôŇčk…Ē k…ôfut…ôr Yurd…õn.
\v 34 K…Ē k…ôl…ônc…ôr kaŇčk…Ē k…ôŇčk…Ē k…ôkaf…ôl…ôr ntende dec d…õŇčkal…õ Asn…Ēt-Tabor m…Ē, k…Ē k…ôŇčk…Ē k…ônarn…õ Huk…Ēk, k…Ē k…ôŇčkaf…ôl…ôr Sabulon k…ôca k…ôt…Ēt ka ntende dec d…õmp…õ m…Ē, nde As…õr k…ôca nk…õ dec d…õŇčkal…õ m…Ē, k…Ē Yuda. Yurd…õn yeyi k…ôl…ônc…ôr kaŇčk…Ē nde dec d…õmp…õ m…Ē.
\v 35 S…ôdare sa saŇčka sas…Ēk…Ē s…ônay…Ēn…õ: Cidim, Cer, Hamat, Rakat, Kineret,
\v 36 Adama, Rama, Hac…Ēr,
\v 37 K…õd…õs, Edreyi, En-Hac…Ēr,
\v 38 Yiron, Mik…ôdal-El, Horem, Bet Hanat k…Ē Bet S…õm…õs, s…ôdare w…ôco k…Ē cam…ôt-maŇčk…ôl…õ (19) k…Ē s…ôdare s…ôf…õt sa si.
\v 39 K…õ ka kusuŇčka ka Naftali k…ônayi kaŇčk…Ē d…ôcor d…ôcor, s…ôdare s…ôp…ĒŇč k…Ē s…ôdare s…ôf…õt sa si.
\s1 Ant…Ēf Ňča Dan
\p 
\v 40 Topoc ta cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč mp…õ p…õnawur m…Ē p…õnay…Ēn…õ k…õ ka kusuŇčka ka Dan d…ôcor d…ôcor.
\v 41 Anac…ômb…ôr…õ Ňča Corha, ∆źst…Ēl, Hir-S…õm…õs,
\v 42 Sahalabin, Ayalon, Yitala,
\v 43 Elon, Timna, Ek…ôron,
\v 44 Elteke, Kibeton, Balat,
\v 45 Yehudu, Bene Berak, Kat-Rimon,
\v 46 Domun da Yarkon k…Ē Rakon, k…Ē ant…Ēf Ňč…Ēk…Ē Ňč…õnt…õf…ôr…õn…õ k…Ē Yafa m…Ē.
\p 
\v 47 Nt…õ k…õ k…ôŇčan, at…Ēf ŇčaŇčan Ňčende Ňč…Ēs…Ēl…ôr Ňča m…Ē, k…Ē awut a Dan ŇčaŇčk…Ē Ňčaw…õk…ôrn…õ aka L…õs…õm k…Ē Ňčandif Ňča. K…Ē ŇčambaŇč ant…Ēf ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē, k…Ē Ňč…Ēy…Ēn…õ ŇčaŇčan, k…Ē Ňčand…õ di, k…Ē Ňčawe di Dan, tewe ta kas k…ôŇčan.
\v 48 K…õ ka kusuŇčka ka Dan k…ônayi kaŇčk…Ē d…ôcor d…ôcor, s…ôdare sas…Ēk…Ē k…Ē s…ôdare s…ôf…õt sa si.
\p 
\v 49 Nt…õ aka Yisrayel Ňčalip k…ôyer…õn…õ c…ôgb…õ ca ant…Ēf m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčampoc…õ Yosuwe wan ka Nun ant…Ēf Ňča k…õ Ňča dac…Ē,
\v 50 p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē MARIKI k…ônasom ti m…Ē. K…Ē Ňčas…ĒŇč k…Ē dare d…Ēk…Ē …õnafaŇč m…Ē, Timnat-Sera, nde m…Ēr…Ē ma Efrayim. Yosuwe oluks…ôrn…õ k…ôc…ômb…ôr dare dad…Ēk…Ē, k'…õnd…õ.
\p 
\v 51 Ant…Ēf Ňča k…õ ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē Ňč…Ē w…ôloŇčn…õ Elasar, Yosuwe wan ka Nun, k…Ē ab…õ a cusuŇčka ca Yisrayel Ňčanakot yampuŇč-puŇč, anac…ômb…ôr mopoc f…Ēr ya MARIKI kiriŇč nde Silo, nde d…ôk…ôb…õr…õ da aŇčgbancan Ňča d…ôk…ôb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē Kanu. Nt…õ t…Ē Ňčanalip k…ôyer ant…Ēf.
\c 20
\s1 S…ôdare ns…õ anay…õk-y…õk k…ôgb…Ēp…ôn…õ teta ay…õk Ňča mecir m…Ē
\p 
\v 1 K…Ē MARIKI k…ôloku Yosuwe:
\v 2 ¬ęM…ôloku aka Yisrayel: N…ônd…õs-d…õs s…ôdare ns…õ w…ôdif fum ta …õy…õf…õn…õ ti …õntam k…ôyacn…õ m…Ē ns…õ isom Musa k…ôs…ĒŇč'un m…Ē.
\v 3 Nw…õ endif fum ta …õy…õf…õn…õ ti m…Ē, …õntam k…ôy…õks…õ p…ôde p…ônd…õ di. Nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ w…ôkayi p…ôyacn…õ ta w…ôk…Ē p…ôluks…õ k…Ē ay…õk Ňča mecir m…Ē.
\v 4 W…ôdif ka fum w…ôkak…Ē …õntam k…ôy…õks…õ p…ôk…Ē dare din s…ôdare sas…Ēk…Ē dac…Ē, k'…ĒŇčk…Ē-…õ, p…ôk…Ē p…ôc…ôm…õ dare d…ôkusu, p…ôloku abeki a dare tes t…Ēk…Ē …õl…ôs…ôr m…Ē. ŇäambaŇč k…Ē dare dad…Ēk…Ē disr…õ, Ňčament…ôr'k…Ē k…ôfo nk…õ …ĒŇčk…Ēnd…õ Ňča dac…Ē m…Ē.
\v 5 K…Ē w…ôluks…õ ay…õk …õnc…õps…õ k…Ē dar…ôŇč k…ôb…õl…ôs-…õ, abeki a dare Ňčaf…Ēwos…õ k…ôs…ĒŇč k…Ē k…Ē, bawo …õy…õf…õn…õ f…õ k…ôdif ka w…õnc, nw…õ …õnat…Ē-y…Ēn…õ w…ôter…õn…õ k…Ēn m…Ē.
\v 6 P…ôyi dare dad…Ēk…Ē haŇč t…õm nt…õ aka Yisrayel Ňčandek…Ē kiti k…Ē m…Ē, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti-…õ w…ôloŇčn…õ w…ôp…ĒŇč p…ôfi. T…õm tat…Ēk…Ē, w…ôdif fum w…ôk…Ē …õy…õks…õ m…Ē, …õntam k…ôlukus nde dare d…Ēn, nde k…ôl…Ē k…Ēn, nde dare d…Ēk…Ē …õnay…õks…õ m…Ē.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 7 K…Ē Ňčal…õk s…ôdare ns…õ: K…õd…õs ka Kalile nde m…Ēr…Ē ma Naftali, S…õk…õm nde m…Ēr…Ē ma Efrayim, k…Ē Kiriyat-Arba nde p…ôy…Ēn…õ Heb…ôr…ĒŇč m…Ē, nde m…Ēr…Ē ma Yuda.
\v 8 K…ôca k…ôŇčk…Ē ntende Yurd…õn ntende dec d…õmp…õ Yeriko m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčal…õk B…õc…õr nde d…ôt…õgb…ôr…õ, p…ôgbant…ôk…ôla mp…õ p…Ēy…Ēn…õ pa kusuŇčka ka Ruben m…Ē, Ramot da Kaladu nde kusuŇčka ka Kadu disr…õ, k…Ē Kolan ka Basan nde kusuŇčka ka Manase disr…õ.
\v 9 S…ôdare sas…Ēk…Ē s…Ē aka Yisrayel Ňčanat…ôŇčn…õ k…ôy…Ēn…õ ka s…ôdare ns…õ, w…ôka Yisrayel k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti-…õ, w…ôcik…ôra, k…Ē endif fum ta …õy…õf…õn…õ ti-…õ, w…ôkak…Ē …õntam k…ôy…õks…õ p…ôde p…ônd…õ di ta aluks…õ k…Ē ay…õk Ňča mecir k…ôdif k…Ēn fum haŇč k…ôloŇčkan…õ ka afum a Yisrayel k…ôb…ôp Ňčaboc…õ k…Ē kiti.
\c 21
\s1 Anac…ômb…ôr…õ aLewy s…ôdare k…Ē culum
\p 
\v 1 K…Ē ab…õ a kusuŇčka ka aLewy Ňčanc…ĒŇčn…õ w…ôloŇčn…õ Elasar k…ôs…ôk, k…Ē Yosuwe wan ka Nun, k…Ē abeki a d…ôcor d…ôcor ca cusuŇčka ca aka Yisrayel.
\v 2 K…Ē Ňčaloku Ňča nt…õ nde Silo ant…Ēf Ňča KanaŇč: ¬ęMARIKI k…ôsom Musa a k…ôs…ĒŇč su s…ôdare a pand…õ si, k…Ē culum ca si a pack…õk ci y…Ēc…Ēl yosu.¬Ľ
\v 3 K…Ē aka Yisrayel Ňčas…ĒŇč aLewy s…ôdare s…ôl…Ēma k…Ē culum ca si k…ôb…õr…õn…õ ka nt…Ēf yaŇčan p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē MARIKI k…ônaloku ti m…Ē.
\p 
\v 4 K'aŇčkot…õ yampuŇč-puŇč aka cor ca Kehat. K'awur…õ aLewy afum a w…ôloŇčn…õ Aruna s…ôdare w…ôco k…Ē maas (13) nde cusuŇčka ca Yuda, Simey…ĒŇč k…Ē BeŇčyamin, k'as…ĒŇč Ňča si.
\v 5 K…Ē cusuŇčka c…ôlp…ôs ca Kehat Ňčas…Ēt…Ē s…ôdare w…ôco (10) nde ant…Ēf Ňča cusuŇčka ca Efrayim, Dan, k…Ē kusuŇčka dac…Ē ka Manase.
\v 6 K'aŇčkot yampuŇč-puŇč, k…Ē afum a Kerson Ňčas…Ēt…Ē s…ôdare w…ôco k…Ē maas (13) nde ant…Ēf Ňča aka cusuŇčka ca Yisakar, As…õr, Naftali, k…Ē aka kusuŇčka dac…Ē ka Manase nde Basan.
\v 7 K…Ē afum a Merari d…ôcor d…ôcor, Ňčas…Ēt…ôr s…ôdare w…ôco k…Ē m…õr…ôŇč (12) aka cusuŇčka ca Ruben, Kadu, k…Ē Sabulon.
\v 8 K…Ē aka Yisrayel ŇčaŇčkot yampuŇč-puŇč k…Ē Ňčas…ĒŇč aLewy s…ôdare sas…Ēk…Ē k…ôl…õk…õn…õ culum ca si, p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē MARIKI k…ônasom ti Musa m…Ē.
\p 
\v 9 Nde nt…Ēf ya cusuŇčka ca Yuda k…Ē Simey…ĒŇč anas…ĒŇč s…ôdare
\v 10 afum a Aruna, aka kor ka Kehat wan ka Lewy, bawo Ňča Ňč…Ē yampuŇč-puŇč y…õnanuŇčk…õn…õ k…ôment…ôr. K'anabonc…ôr Ňča s…ôdare sas…Ēk…Ē mewe.
\v 11 K…Ē aka Yisrayel Ňčas…ĒŇč aka Kehat Kiriyat-Arba ant…Ēf d…ôndo d…ôm…Ēr…Ē da Yuda, k…Ē culum cac…Ēk…Ē c…ôn…ĒŇčk…ôr di m…Ē. AŇčwe s…Ē dare dand…õ tewe ta Heb…ôr…ĒŇč. Arba …õnay…Ēn…õ papa w…ôka Anak.
\v 12 Mba dal…õ da dare d…Ēp…ĒŇč k…Ē s…ôdare s…ôf…õt sa si k'as…ĒŇč Kalebi wan ka Yefune.
\v 13 K…Ē Ňčas…ĒŇč awut a w…ôloŇčn…õ Aruna Heb…ôr…ĒŇč, dare da k…ôgb…Ēp…ôn…õ nd…õ w…ôdif fum ta …õy…õf…õn…õ ti …õntam k…ôyacn…õ m…Ē, Libana,
\v 14 Yatir, Esitemo,
\v 15 Holon, Debir,
\v 16 Ayin, Yuta k…Ē Bet S…õm…õs, s…ôdare cam…ôt-maŇčk…ôl…õ (9) ca cusuŇčka ca Simey…ĒŇč k…Ē BeŇčyamin k…ôl…õk…õn…õ culum ca si.
\v 17 Nde at…Ēf Ňča BeŇčyamin k…Ē Ňčas…Ēt…Ē Kabay…ĒŇč, Keba,
\v 18 Anatot, k…Ē Halmon. It…Ē tat…Ēk…Ē s…ôdare maŇčk…ôl…õ k…Ē culum ca si.
\v 19 AloŇčn…õ aŇč…õ Ňčanay…Ēn…õ aka kusuŇčka ka Aruna m…Ē Ňčanas…Ēt…Ē s…ôdare w…ôco k…Ē maas (13) k…Ē culum ca si.
\p 
\v 20 Cor ca aka Kehat c…ôlp…ôs aŇč…õ Ňčanay…Ēn…õ kusuŇčka ka Lewy m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčas…Ēt…Ē s…ôdare nde ant…Ēf Ňča kusuŇčka ka Efrayim.
\v 21 K'as…ĒŇč Ňča S…õk…õm dare da k…ôgb…Ēp…ôn…õ nde m…Ēr…Ē ma Efrayim, Keser,
\v 22 Kibasayim, k…Ē Bet Horon, s…ôdare maŇčk…ôl…õ (4) k…ôl…õk…õn…õ culum ca si.
\v 23 K'as…ĒŇč kusuŇčka ka Dan: Elteke, Kibeton,
\v 24 Ayalon, k…Ē Kat-Rimon, s…ôdare maŇčk…ôl…õ (4) k…ôl…õk…õn…õ culum ca si.
\v 25 K'as…ĒŇč kusuŇčka dac…Ē ka Manase: Tahanak k…Ē Kat-Rimon, s…ôdare m…õr…ôŇč (2) k…ôl…õk…õn…õ culum ca si.
\v 26 Cor ca afum a Kehat al…Ēma c…ônas…Ēt…Ē s…ôdare w…ôco (10) k…Ē culum ca si.
\p 
\v 27 K'as…ĒŇč afum a Kerson cor ca aLewy dac…Ē: Ňäas…Ēt…ôr aka kusuŇčka dac…Ē ka Manase nde Yurd…õn k…ôs…ôk ntende dec d…õmp…õ m…Ē s…ôdare m…õr…ôŇč (2) k…Ē culum ca si: Kolan nde Basan disr…õ, dare da k…ôgb…Ēp…ôn…õ, k…Ē B…õstara.
\v 28 K'as…ĒŇč kusuŇčka ka Yisakar: Kisiyon, Daberat,
\v 29 Yarmut, k…Ē En-Kanim, s…ôdare maŇčk…ôl…õ (4) k…ôl…õk…õn…õ culum ca si.
\v 30 K'as…ĒŇč kusuŇčka ka As…õr: Misal, Abadon,
\v 31 H…õlkat, k…Ē Rehobo, s…ôdare maŇčk…ôl…õ (4) k…ôl…õk…õn…õ culum ca si.
\v 32 K'as…ĒŇč kusuŇčka ka Naftali: K…õd…õs nde Kalile, dare da k…ôgb…Ēp…ôn…õ, Hamot-D…Ēr, k…Ē Kartan, s…ôdare maas (3) k…ôl…õk…õn…õ culum ca si.
\v 33 S…ôdare sa aka Kerson d…ôcor d…ôcor s…ônak…Ē s…ôdare w…ôco k…Ē maas (13) k…Ē culum ca si.
\p 
\v 34 K'as…ĒŇč aLewy alp…ôs ak…Ē Ňčanay…Ēn…õ cor ca afum a Merari m…Ē, k…Ē Ňča Ňčas…Ēt…ôr aka kusuŇčka ka Sabulon: Yokonam, Karta,
\v 35 Dimna, k…Ē Nahalal, s…ôdare maŇčk…ôl…õ (4) k…ôl…õk…õn…õ culum ca si.
\v 36 K'as…ĒŇč kusuŇčka ka Ruben: B…õc…õr, Yahas,
\v 37 Kedemot, k…Ē Mefahat, s…ôdare maŇčk…ôl…õ (4) k…ôl…õk…õn…õ culum ca si.
\v 38 K'as…ĒŇč kusuŇčka ka Kadu: Ramot nde Kaladu dare da k…ôgb…Ēp…ôn…õ, Mahanayim,
\v 39 Hesbon, k…Ē Yaser, s…ôdare maŇčk…ôl…õ (4) k…ôl…õk…õn…õ culum ca si.
\v 40 Nt…õ aŇčkot yampuŇč-puŇč m…Ē k…Ē afum a Merari Ňčawur…õ d…ôcor d…ôcor ak…Ē Ňčanay…Ēn…õ aka kusuŇčka ka Lewy alp…ôs m…Ē, Ňčas…Ēt…Ē s…ôdare w…ôco k…Ē m…õr…ôŇč (12).
\p 
\v 41 S…ôdare sa kusuŇčka ka aLewy nt…Ēf ya aka Yisrayel dac…Ē s…ônak…Ē s…ôdare w…ôco maŇčk…ôl…õ k…Ē cam…ôt-maas (48) k…Ē culum ca si.
\v 42 S…ôdare sas…Ēk…Ē f…ôp s…ônay…Ē culum nc…õ c…ôncn…ĒŇčk…ôr si m…Ē, it…Ē s…ôdare s…ôk…Ē f…ôp s…ônayi.
\p 
\v 43 Tat…Ēk…Ē t…Ē MARIKI k…ônas…ĒŇč…ôs aka Yisrayel at…Ēf m…ôlm…ôl nŇč…õ k…ônad…õrm…õ atem aŇčan k…ôdes…ĒŇč Ňča m…Ē, k…Ē ŇčambaŇč Ňči k…Ē Ňčand…õ.
\v 44 K…Ē MARIKI k…ôs…ĒŇč Ňča k…ôŇčes…ôm, mofo f…ôp p…ôforu tuŇč p…Ē Ňčanayin…õ, p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē …õnad…õrm…õ ti atem aŇčan m…Ē. Ali ater aŇčan akin Ňčanatam f…õ k…ôc…ôm…õ Ňča f…Ēr kiriŇč, k…Ē MARIKI k…ôl…õk ater aŇčan k…Ē k…ômb…õr Ňča d…ôwaca.
\v 45 Moloku m…Ēt…Ēt mm…õ MARIKI k…ônaloku aka Yisrayel m…Ē, ali tin t…õnayi f…õ nt…õ …õnat…Ē-y…Ēn…õ Ňča m…Ē, k…Ē k…ôlas mi f…ôp.
\c 22
\s1 CusuŇčka ca Yisrayel nde dec d…õmp…õ Yurd…õn m…Ē
\p 
\v 1 K…Ē Yosuwe ewe aRuben, aKadu, k…Ē aka kusuŇčka dac…Ē ka Manase.
\v 2 K'oloku Ňča: ¬ęN…ôy…Ē t…Ēk…Ē Musa w…ôcar ka MARIKI …õnalok'un m…Ē f…ôp, k…Ē n…ônc…ôŇčk…ôl s…Ē dim dem, t…Ēk…Ē ilok'un m…Ē.
\v 3 N…ôsump…ôr aw…õnc un aŇča k…ôy…õf…õ nt…õ t…õnayi m…Ē haŇč nd…õk…ôl, k…Ē n…ôlel…ôs s…Ē dim nd…õ MARIKI Kanu konu k…ônalok'un m…Ē.
\v 4 Nd…õk…ôl oŇč nt…õ MARIKI k…ôs…ĒŇč aw…õnc un aŇča p…ôforu m…Ē p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē …õnaloku Ňča ti m…Ē, n…ôl…õk oŇč s…ôp…Ē sa c…ôbal conu nde nt…Ēf y…Ēk…Ē y…Ēy…Ēn…õ yonu m…Ē, ny…õ Musa w…ôcar ka MARIKI …õnas…ĒŇč un nde Yurd…õn k…ôs…ôk ntende dec d…õmp…õ m…Ē.
\v 5 Ta n…ôgbaym…õ m…õt…ôks…õ k…Ē sariy…õ y…Ēk…Ē Musa w…ôcar ka MARIKI …õnalok'un m…Ē: N…ôb…Ēt…ôr MARIKI Kanu konu, n…ôsoln…õ s…ôp…Ē s…Ēn f…ôp, n…ôc…ôm…õ dim d…Ēn dar…ôŇč, n…ôl…Ēt…ôrn…õ k…Ē, n…ôb…ôc…õ k…Ē b…ôk…ôc yosoku p…õs doru o doru.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 6 K…Ē Yosuwe ontola Kanu te taŇčan, k'oloku Ňča nw…õ o nw…õ a p…ôk…Ē nde abal Ňč…Ēn, k…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ēk…Ēs-k…Ēs nde c…ôbal c…ôŇčan.
\v 7 Musa …õnas…ĒŇč kusuŇčka dac…Ē ka Manase k…ôfo k…ôl…Ēma Basan, k…Ē Yosuwe nk…Ēn …Ēs…ĒŇč kusuŇčka dac…Ē k…ôŇčk…Ē k…ôfo k…ôl…Ēma aw…õnc aŇča k…ôs…ôk nde Yurd…õn ntende dec d…õŇčkal…õ m…Ē. Nt…õ Yosuwe oloku Ňča k…ôk…Ē ka nde c…ôbal c…ôŇčan m…Ē, k'ontolan…õ Ňča,
\v 8 k'oloku Ňča: ¬ęN…ôlukus nde c…ôbal conu k…Ē daka d…Ēp…ĒŇč, k…Ē y…Ēc…Ēl y…õlar…ôm, k…Ē p…ôsam, k…õma, k…Ēp…ôr, f…õc k…Ē yamos y…õlar…ôm. N…ôyer…õn…õ k…Ē aw…õnc un aŇč…õ y…Ēs…Ēt…Ē ya ater…õn…õ anu.¬Ľ
\s1 Anc…ômb…ôr tetek toloŇčn…õ Kanu Yurd…õn k…ôs…ôk
\p 
\v 9 K…Ē kusuŇčka ka aka Ruben, aka Kadu, k…Ē aka kusuŇčka dac…Ē ka Manase Ňčalukus, k…Ē Ňčasak aka Yisrayel nde Silo ant…Ēf Ňča KanaŇč, k…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē nde ant…Ēf Ňča Kaladu, ant…Ēf Ňča k…õ nŇč…õ Ňčanas…Ēt…Ē m…Ē MARIKI k…ônasom Musa k…ôdes…ĒŇč Ňča Ňči.
\v 10 Nt…õ Ňčamb…õr…õ s…ôdare ns…õ s…ôyi Yurd…õn nde ant…Ēf Ňča KanaŇč m…Ē, k…Ē aRuben, aKadu k…Ē aka kusuŇčka dac…Ē ka Manase Ňčanc…ômb…ôr tetek toloŇčn…õ Kanu Yurd…õn k…ôs…ôk, tetek toloŇčn…õ Mariki p…Ēp…ĒŇč.
\v 11 K'aka Yisrayel Ňčane pacloku: ¬ę aRuben, aKadu k…Ē aka kusuŇčka dac…Ē ka Manase Ňčanc…ômb…ôr tetek toloŇčn…õ Kanu p…õt…õf…ôr…õn…õ k…Ē KanaŇč, nde Yurd…õn k…ôs…ôk k…ôca ka aka Yisrayel.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 12 Nt…õ Ňčane ti m…Ē, k…Ē aka Yisrayel f…ôp ŇčaloŇčkan…õ Silo k…ôk…Ēsut…õn…õ k…Ē Ňča.
\v 13 K…Ē aka Yisrayel Ňčasom Pinahas wan ka w…ôloŇčn…õ Elasar nda aka Ruben, aka Kadu, k…Ē afum a kusuŇčka dac…Ē ka Manase nde ant…Ēf Ňča Kaladu,
\v 14 k…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē k…Ē akiriŇč w…ôco akin akin aka cusuŇčka cac…Ēk…Ē d…ôcor d…ôcor. F…ôp faŇčan akiriŇč a d…ôcusuŇčka Ňč…Ē Ňčanay…Ēn…õ afum alar…ôm aka Yisrayel akak…Ē dac…Ē.
\v 15 K…Ē afum aŇč…õ ŇčaŇčk…Ē nde aRuben, aKadu, k…Ē aka kusuŇčka dac…Ē ka Manase nde ant…Ēf Ňča Kaladu, k…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē Ňčaloku Ňča:
\v 16 ¬ęNt…õ t…Ē k…ôloŇčkan…õ ka afum a Mariki f…ôp Ňčaloku: Ake d…õtaŇči l…ôŇč…ôs d…Ē n…ôy…Ē Kanu ka aka Yisrayel tant…õ-…õ? N…ôlukus m…Ēk…Ē Mariki dar…ôŇč nt…õ n…ônc…ômb…ôr tetek toloŇčn…õ Kanu, n…ôyeŇčk…ôr m…Ēk…Ē Mariki domp!
\v 17 Kiciya nk…õ s…ônay…Ē nde Pey…Ēr m…Ē k…ônay…Ēn…õ mes m…õl…õc. HaŇč m…Ēk…Ē antas…Ēk…ôsn…õ f…õ. Kiciya kosu k…ônas…ĒŇč…õ k…ôloŇčkan…õ ka afum …Ēn arom Ňč…õl…õc.
\v 18 K…Ē n…ôna n…ôŇčyeŇčk m…Ēk…Ē k…ôlukus dim da MARIKI dar…ôŇč! K…Ē n…ôyeŇčk…ôr m…Ēk…Ē MARIKI domp-…õ, alna aka Yisrayel f…ôp Ňč…Ē endewur…ôr m…õt…õl…õ mam…Ēk…Ē.
\v 19 K…Ē t…Ēy…Ēn…õ at…Ēf nŇč…õ Ňč…Ēy…Ēn…õ Ňčonu m…Ē, Ňč…Ēs…Ēk f…õ-…õ, n…ôcep…ôr oŇč at…Ēf nŇč…õ Ňč…Ēy…Ēn…õ Ňča Mariki m…Ē, nde Mariki eyi m…Ē, t…õm tat…Ēk…Ē n…ônd…õ su dac…Ē, mba ta n…ôyeŇčk…ôr Mariki s…ôbomp, ta n…ôyeŇčk…ôr s…ôna s…Ē s…ôbomp k…ôc…ôr…õ a n…ôc…ômb…ôr tetek toloŇčn…õ p…Ēl…Ēma mp…õ p…Ēnt…Ēy…Ēn…õ tetek toloŇč…õ pa Mariki, Kanu kosu m…Ē.
\v 20 Nt…õ AkaŇč wan ka Sera …õnalukus k…ôc…ôm…õ Kanu dar…ôŇč teta ca c…ôk…Ē MARIKI k…ônam…Ēn…õ k…ôl…õk m…Ē, aka Yisrayel f…ôp Ňč…Ē MARIKI k…ônawur…ôr m…õt…õl…õ m…Ēn. N…ônc…ôr…õ ti belbel a baf…Ē AkaŇč sona …õnafin…õ kiciya kaŇčk…Ē.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 21 K…Ē afum a Ruben, Kadu, k…Ē aka kusuŇčka dac…Ē ka Manase Ňčaloku ab…õ akiriŇč aka cor ca Yisrayel:
\v 22 ¬ęKanu ka canu, MARIKI! Kanu ka canu, MARIKI, Ki k…ônc…ôr…õ ti! Aka Yisrayel Ňčandec…ôr…õ ti! K…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…Ē k…ôt…Ē-c…ôŇčk…ôl k…Ē k…ôyeŇčk…ôr domp k…Ē-…õ, ta p…ôdeyac su d…Ēs…Ēk dad…Ēk…Ē!
\v 23 K…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ a s…ônc…ômb…ôr tetek toloŇčn…õ posu teta k…ôdegb…õk…ôl Mariki-…õ, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ s…ônde s…ôcloŇčn…õ di yoloŇčn…õ y…Ēc…Ēf-…õ, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti yoloŇčn…õ ya yokom ya y…Ēb…Ēf, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ a yoloŇčn…õ ya p…ôforu-…õ, awa, Mariki endegb…õk…ôr…õ ti!
\v 24 Baf…Ē it…Ē teyi! S…ôlomp…ôs tetek toloŇčn…õ Kanu pamp…õ bawo s…ônes…õ ta alna awut anu Ňčade Ňčacyif akosu f…Ē: ‚ÄĻAk'eyi nu dac…Ē k…Ē MARIKI, Kanu ka Yisrayel-…õ?
\v 25 MARIKI k…ômboc k…ôl…ônc…ôr Yurd…õn n…ôna k…Ē s…ôna dac…Ē, aRuben, k…Ē aKadu, ali tes teyi f'on s…Ē dac…Ē k…Ē MARIKI!‚Äļ Teta awut anu tendes…ĒŇč…õ ta awut asu ŇčaŇčnes…õ s…Ē MARIKI-…õ.
\v 26 It…Ē s…ônc…õm-c…õmn…õ a: S…ômar…õn…õ s…ôc…ômb…ôr tetek toloŇčn…õ, baf…Ē s…ôde s…ôcloŇčn…õ di y…Ēc…Ēl y…Ēc…Ēf k…Ē k…ôloŇčn…õ k…ôl…Ēma de,
\v 27 mba Ňčeyi su dac…Ē k…Ē n…ôna p…ôm…Ē sede. Ňäeyi s…Ē awut asu dac…Ē k…Ē awut anu ŇčacloŇčn…õ yoloŇčn…õ ya y…Ēc…Ēf k…Ē yoloŇčn…õ ya p…ôforu MARIKI f…Ēr y…Ēn kiriŇč, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ ta Ňčade Ňčacloku d…Ēs…Ēk d…Ēl…Ēma a t…Ēl…Ēm o t…Ēl…Ēm teyi f…õ awut asu dac…Ē k…Ē MARIKI!
\v 28 K…Ē s…ôloku: ‚ÄĻK…Ē Ňčande Ňčaloku su tant…õ, k…Ē p…ôy…Ē f…õ ti Ňčaloku awut asu ti-…õ, moloku mam…õ m…Ē s…ôndeluks…õ Ňča: ¬ęN…ôgb…ôtn…õ teyi ta tetek toloŇčn…õ Mariki mp…õ atem asu Ňčanac…ômb…ôr m…Ē, baf…Ē teta k…ôloŇčn…õ ka y…Ēc…Ēl y…Ēc…Ēf k…Ē k…ôloŇčn…õ ka yokom y…Ēb…Ēf y…Ēl…Ēma t…Ē anac…ômb…ôr…õ Ňči de, mba Ňč…Ēy…Ēn…õ sede su dac…Ē k…Ē n…ôna Ňč…õcc…õm-c…õm…ôs su.¬Ľ‚Äļ
\v 29 S…ômb…Ēl…õn…õ k…ôyeŇčk…ôr Mariki s…ôbomp, tes o tes doru dand…õ t…Ēf…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ su m…Ēk…Ē k…ôlukus k…Ē dar…ôŇč, k…ôc…ômb…ôr kosu tetek toloŇčn…õ p…Ēc…Ēl p…Ēc…Ēf k…ôloŇčn…õ yokom y…Ēb…Ēf k…Ē k…ôloŇčn…õ k…ôl…Ēma, s…ôf…ĒloŇčn…õ k…ôfo k…ôcuru ta p…ôy…Ēn…õ nde tetek toloŇčn…õ Mariki Kanu kosu nw…õ eyi tekiriŇč ta k…ôfo nk…õ as…Ēk…ôs m…Ē!
\p 
\v 30 Nt…õ w…ôloŇčn…õ Pinahas, k…Ē ab…õ akiriŇč a k…ôloŇčkan…õ k…Ē abeki a cor ca Yisrayel aŇč…õ Ňčanayi di Ňčane moloku mam…Ēk…Ē afum a Ruben, Kadu, k…Ē kusuŇčka dac…Ē ka Manase Ňčanaloku m…Ē, k…Ē moloku mam…Ēk…Ē m…Ēmb…Ēt Ňča.
\v 31 K…Ē Pinahas wan ka w…ôloŇčn…õ Elasar oloku afum a Ruben, Kadu, k…Ē afum a Manase: ¬ęS…ônc…ôr…õ m…Ēk…Ē a MARIKI k…ôyi su dac…Ē, bawo n…ôntalukus f…õ k…ôc…ôm…õ MARIKI dar…ôŇč, k…Ē n…ôyac s…Ē aka Yisrayel ta MARIKI k…ôboc Ňča kiti.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 32 K…Ē Pinahas wan ka w…ôloŇčn…õ Elasar k…Ē akiriŇč a cor c…ôŇčan Ňčalukus k…ôy…õf…õ ndena afum a Ruben k…Ē Kadu nde at…Ēf Ňča Kaladu k…ôk…Ē nde ant…Ēf Ňča KanaŇč ndena aka Yisrayel aŇč…õ Ňčanak…Ē Ňčaluks…õ moloku m…Ēk…Ē Ňčanas…Ēt…ôr Ňča m…Ē.
\v 33 K…Ē moloku mam…Ēk…Ē m…Ēmb…Ēt aka Yisrayel, k…Ē ŇčaŇčkor-koru Kanu. Ňäaloku f…õ s…Ē k…ôk…Ēm…ôl…ôk ant…Ēf nŇč…õ afum a Ruben k…Ē afum a Kadu Ňčanand…õ m…Ē.
\v 34 Afum a Ruben k…Ē afum a Kadu Ňčas…ĒŇč tetek toloŇčn…õ Kanu pap…Ēk…Ē tewe, Ňčacloku: ¬ęT…Ēy…Ēn…õ su sede a Mariki …Ēy…Ēn…õ Kanu.¬Ľ
\c 23
\s1 Moloku m…õlp…ôs ma Yosuwe
\p 
\v 1 T…õm tobolu-bolu t…õnacep…ôr k…ôy…õf…õ ka nt…õ MARIKI k…ônas…ĒŇč aka Yisrayel k…ôŇčes…ôm m…Ē, k…ôb…õr Ňča ater…õn…õ aŇčan ac…ôs…ôk f…ôp d…ôwaca. Yosuwe …õnasik…ôr oŇč t…õm tat…Ēk…Ē.
\v 2 K…Ē Yosuwe ewe aka Yisrayel f…ôp k…ôy…õf…õ abeki, ab…õ af…õt d…ôcor d…ôcor, aboc kiti, k…ôb…ôp ka ab…õ akiriŇč aŇčan, k'oloku Ňča: ¬ęIy…Ēn…õ oŇč w…ôtem.
\v 3 K…Ē n…ôn…ôŇčk t…Ēk…Ē MARIKI Kanu konu k…ônay…Ē afum aka t…Ēf ny…õ f…ôp m…Ē te tonu, bawo MARIKI k…ôsutn…õn'on.
\v 4 N…ôn…ôŇčk nt…õ iŇčkot yampuŇč-puŇč a k'iyer un t…Ēf ya k…õ konu d…ôcusuŇčka d…ôcusuŇčka m…Ē, t…Ēf ny…õ y…õnc…ôm…õ k…ôbaŇč Yurd…õn ntende dec d…õŇčkal…õ m…Ē, k…Ē t…Ēf ny…õ inim haŇč nde K…ôba K…ôp…ĒŇč m…Ē.
\v 5 MARIKI k…ôndew…õn…ôs afum aka t…Ēf yay…Ēk…Ē, k…Ē n…ônde n…ôcl…Ēt…ôs yi-…õ, n…ôndend…õ nt…Ēf yay…Ēk…Ē p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē nk…Ēn MARIKI Kanu konu k…ônas…ĒŇč un temer ta ti m…Ē.
\v 6 N…ôwur…õ f…ôn…Ēnt…ôr, n…ôsump…ôr n…ôlel…ôs moloku mm…õ acic…ôs buk ba sariy…õ sa Musa m…Ē, ta n…ôgbaym…õ k…ôca k…ômeriya, ta n…ôgbaym…õ k…ôca k…ôt…Ēt,
\v 7 ta n…ôden…ĒŇčk…ôl…õn…õ afum a t…Ēf akak…Ē Ňčayi nu dac…Ē m…Ē! Ta n…ôbonc canu c…ôŇčan, ta n…ôkorn…õ ci k…ôd…õr…ôm. Ta n…ôkor-koru ci, ta n…ôtontn…õ ci f…Ēr kiriŇč!
\v 8 Mba n…ôsump…ôr MARIKI Kanu konu p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē n…ônal…õk ti k…ôy…Ē haŇč m…Ēk…Ē m…Ē.
\v 9 MARIKI k…ômbaŇč…ôr t…Ēf y…Ēp…ĒŇč aka f…ôn…Ēnt…ôr, ali fum …õntatam f…õ haŇč m…Ēk…Ē k…ôc…ôm…õ konu f…Ēr kiriŇč.
\v 10 N…ôna fum w…ôkin gboŇč …õncb…õl…ôs ater…õn…õ anu p…õc…ôp pin, bawo MARIKI Kanu konu k…ôncsutn…õn'on, p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē k…ônalok'un m…Ē.
\v 11 N…ôk…õmb…ôrn…õ n…ôb…Ēt…ôr MARIKI Kanu konu!
\v 12 K…Ē n…ôlukus MARIKI dar…ôŇč-…õ, k…Ē n…ôc…ôm…õ afum acuru aŇč…õ Ňčayi nu dac…Ē m…Ē dar…ôŇč-…õ, k…Ē n…ôn…õnc…õn…õ-…õ, k…Ē n…ôn…ĒŇčk…ôl…õn…õ-…õ,
\v 13 n…ôc…ôr…õ a MARIKI Kanu konu k…ôf…Ēdec…ôm…õ s…Ē k…ôbaŇčs…ôr Ňča afum akak…Ē t…Ēf yaŇčan f…Ēr yonu kiriŇč, mba afum akak…Ē Ňčandey…Ēn'on mowul, m…õn…ômp, yala, c…ôŇčgban-gban ca c…ôs…ôk conu, k…Ē gb…õc d…ôf…Ēr yonu, haŇč n…ôlip k…ôm…ôlk…õ at…Ēf Ňčobotu ŇčaŇč…õ MARIKI Kanu konu k…ôs…ĒŇč'un m…Ē.
\p 
\v 14 ¬ęAwa, n…ôc…ôŇčk…ôl im! M…Ēk…Ē t…õm t…õmb…ôp k…ôk…Ē ka nde ca ca doru f…ôp yendek…Ē m…Ē. N…ôc…ôr…õ ti b…ôk…ôc yonu yosoku p…õs, a moloku mobotu mm…õ MARIKI Kanu konu k…ônalok'un m…Ē, ali tin teyi f…õ nt…õ …Ēnt…Ēy…Ēn'on m…Ē, ali tin teyi f…õ nt…õ …Ēnt…Ēlas m…Ē.
\v 15 MARIKI k…ôlas k…ôy…Ēn…õ ka p…ôt…Ēt p…Ēk…Ē …õnaloku k…ôy…Ēn'on m…Ē, mba …õntam s…Ē k…ôlas ka p…ôl…õc p…Ēk…Ē eyi k…ôn…õps'on m…Ē, p…ôm…ôl…ôk un ant…Ēf Ňčobotu ŇčaŇč…õ …Ēs…ĒŇč'un m…Ē.
\v 16 K…Ē n…ôsak m…õt…ôŇčn…õ mosu mm…õ MARIKI k…ônd…ôŇčk'on m…Ē-…õ, k…Ē n…ôŇčk…Ē n…ôcloŇčn…õ canu c…ôl…Ēma-…õ, k…Ē n…ôŇčk…Ē n…ôctontn…õ canu c…ôl…Ēma f…Ēr kiriŇč-…õ, ab…ôk…ôc Ňča MARIKI Ňč…õmp…õ nn…Ē n…ôyi m…Ē. T…õm tat…Ēk…Ē n…ôŇčm…ôlk…õ ant…Ēf Ňčobotu ŇčaŇč…õ MARIKI k…ôs…ĒŇč'un m…Ē, n…ôlip.
\c 24
\s1 Aka Yisrayel f…ôp k…ôd…õr…ôm k…ôŇčan k…ôkorn…õ MARIKI
\p 
\v 1 K…Ē Yosuwe oloŇčka cusuŇčka ca Yisrayel f…ôp S…õk…õm. K'ewen…õn…õ s…Ē abeki a Yisrayel, ab…õ aŇčan, aboc aŇčan kiti, k…Ē akiriŇč aŇčan, k…Ē Ňčament…ôrn…õ nn…Ē Kanu k…ôyi m…Ē.
\v 2 K…Ē Yosuwe oloku afum f…ôp: ¬ęNt…õ t…Ē MARIKI Kanu ka Yisrayel k…ôloku: ‚ÄĻT…õm tobol-bolu atem anu, Terah papa w…ôka Abraham k…Ē papa w…ôka Nahor nde k…ôŇčgb…Ēk…Ē ka ∆źf…ôrat ntende dec d…õmp…õ m…Ē k…Ē Ňčanand…õ, Ňčackorn…õ canu c…ôl…Ēma.
\v 3 K'il…õk w…ôtem konu Abraham d…ôndo k…ôŇčgb…Ēk…Ē ntende dec d…õmp…õ m…Ē, k'iŇčk…Ēt…õn…õ k…Ē ant…Ēf Ňča KanaŇč f…ôp. K'is…ĒŇč…õ afum …Ēn k…ôla, k'is…ĒŇč k…Ē Siyaka.
\v 4 K'is…ĒŇč Siyaka awut: Yakuba k…Ē Esayu. K'is…ĒŇč Esayu m…Ēr…Ē ma Seyir nt…õ t…Ēy…Ēn…õ ant…Ēf Ňč…Ēn, k…Ē Yakuba k…Ē awut …Ēn Ňča Ňčantor Misira.
\v 5 K'isom Musa k…Ē Aruna k…ôdemar afum anu. K'isut Misira f…Ēr yonu kiriŇč a k'indewur…õn…õ afum anu di.
\v 6 Nt…õ iwur…õ awisi aŇča Misira, k…Ē n…ômb…ôp d…ôk…ôba m…Ē. K…Ē aka Misira Ňčanc…ôm…õ Ňča dar…ôŇč k…ôb…õl…ôs haŇč nde K…ôba ka C…ôŇčk…Ēlma, Ňčacb…õl…ôs Ňča d…ôf…ôl…õs k…ôroŇč k…Ē cibil ca k…ôwan.
\v 7 Nt…õ awisi aŇča Ňčawes-wes k…ômar ka MARIKI m…Ē, k…Ē k…ôntor…õ kubump k…ôp…ĒŇč aka Misira k…Ē n…ôna dac…Ē. K…Ē Kanu k…ôŇčgb…ôt…ôs Ňča d…ôk…ôba. N…ônat…ôŇčn…õ mes mm…õ inay…Ē Misira m…Ē f…Ēr yonu kiriŇč. K…Ē n…ôwon k…ônd…õ d…ôt…õgb…ôr…õ meren m…õlar…ôm.
\v 8 T…õm tat…Ēk…Ē t'inakek…ôr'on ant…Ēf Ňča aka Am…Ēr aŇč…õ Ňčanand…õ Yurd…õn k…ôs…ôk ntende dec d…õmp…õ m…Ē. K…Ē n…ôsut…õn…õ k…Ē Ňča, mba k'il…õk aka Am…Ēr k'imb…õr'un Ňča d…ôwaca. K…Ē n…ômbaŇč…ôr Ňča ant…Ēf ŇčaŇčan, k'im…ôl…ôk Ňča f…Ēr yonu kiriŇč.
\v 9 K…Ē Balak wan w…ôka Sip…Ēr w…ôb…õ w…ôka Mohab …õw…õk…ôrn…õ aka Yisrayel. K'osom Balam wan w…ôka Bey…Ēr a p…ôtolan'on p…ôl…õc,
\v 10 mba k'ifati k…ôc…ôŇčk…ôl k…Ē. P…ôt…Ēt gb…ôc…ôr…ôm p…Ē Balam onctolan'on, k'iyac nu f…ôn…Ēnt…ôr f…Ēn.
\v 11 K…Ē n…ôncali k…ôŇčgb…Ēk…Ē ka Yurd…õn, k…Ē n…ônder Yeriko. K…Ē aka Yeriko k…ôl…õk…õn…õ aka Am…Ēr, aPerisi, aKanaŇč, aHit, aKirkasa, aHiwy, k…Ē aYebus Ňčasut…õn…õ k…Ē n…ôna, k'il…õk Ňča k'imb…õr'un d…ôwaca.
\v 12 K'isom deme nd…õ d…õnayi nu kiriŇč k…Ē d…õmb…õl…ôs ab…õ a Am…Ēr m…õr…ôŇč m…Ē. In'…õnas…ĒŇč on k…ôtam Ňča. Baf…Ē sakma sonu, baf…Ē mb…ônc…ôran yonu y…Ē n…ônatam…õ ater…õn…õ anu de!
\v 13 In'…Ēs…ĒŇč un ant…Ēf nŇč…õ n…ônt…Ēb…ôc haŇč n…ôtaka m…Ē, k…Ē n…ônd…õ s…ôdare ns…õ n…ônt…Ēc…ômb…ôr…õ waca wonu m…Ē. K…Ē n…ôndi yeri ya dal…õ nd…õ n…ônt…Ēbifti m…Ē, n…ôcdi yokom ya t…Ēk ny…õ n…ônt…Ēb…Ēf m…Ē.‚Äļ
\p 
\v 14 Nd…õk…ôl oŇč n…ônes…õ MARIKI, n…ôkorn…õ MARIKI k…Ē b…ôk…ôc yosoku p…õs! N…ôc…ôm…õ k…Ē dar…ôŇč t…õm f…ôp. N…ôce canu nc…õ atem anu Ňčanckorn…õ nde k…ôŇčgb…Ēk…Ē ka ∆źf…ôrat ntende dec d…õmp…õ k…Ē nde Misira m…Ē. N…ôkorn…õ oŇč MARIKI!
\v 15 K…Ē n…ônt…Ēwos…õ oŇč k…ôkorn…õ MARIKI-…õ, n…ôbonc m…Ēk…Ē an…Ē n…ônde n…ôckorn…õ-…õ, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ canu nc…õ atem anu Ňčanckorn…õ ntende ∆źf…ôrat k…ôca ka ntende dec d…õmp…õ m…Ē, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti-…õ, canu ca aka Am…Ēr aŇč…õ n…ôyi k…ônd…õ ant…Ēf ŇčaŇčan m…Ē. Mba ina k…Ē aka k…ôl…Ē kem disr…õ MARIKI k…Ē s…ônde s…ôckorn…õ!¬Ľ
\p 
\v 16 K…Ē afum Ňčaluks…õ k…Ē: ¬ęS…ômb…Ēl…õn…õ k…ôsak MARIKI a s…ôckorn…õ canu c…ôl…Ēma! S…ôf…Ētam k…ôy…Ē tat…Ēk…Ē!
\v 17 MARIKI k…ônawur…õ atem asu k…Ē s…ôna dacar d…ôndo ant…Ēf Ňča Misira, K…ônay…Ē m…õgb…õk…ôr…õ m…Ēp…ĒŇč nde f…Ēr yosu kiriŇč. K…ôcbum su d…Ēp…Ē k…ôcmar su k…ôcep…ôr t…Ēf ya afum alar…ôm.
\v 18 MARIKI k…ônab…õl…ôs afum aka t…Ēf yay…Ēk…Ē f…ôp, k…ôl…õk…õn…õ aka Am…Ēr aŇč…õ Ňčanand…õ di m…Ē. S…ôna s…Ē s…ôndekorn…õ MARIKI, bawo Kanu kosu k'…Ēy…Ēn…õ!¬Ľ
\p 
\v 19 K…Ē Yosuwe oloku afum: ¬ęN…ôf…Ēdetam k…ôckorn…õ MARIKI, bawo k…ôcempi k…Ē …Ēy…Ēn…õ! Kanu k…Ē nk…õ k…ôy…Ē k…ôraca m…Ē nk…õ k…ôt…ĒŇčaŇčn…õn…õ k…ôtaŇč konu l…ôŇč…ôs, k…Ē kiciya konu m…Ē.
\v 20 K…Ē n…ôlukus MARIKI dar…ôŇč-…õ, k…Ē n…ôkorn…õ canu c…ôcuru-…õ, MARIKI k…ôndekaf…ôl…õ k…ôt…õf…ôrn…õ n…ôna. K…ôndel…ôs…ôr on mes, k…ôndem…ôl…ôk nu, ali nt…õ c…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē k…ônay'on p…ôt…Ēt m…Ē.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 21 K'afum Ňčaluks…õ Yosuwe nt…õ: ¬ęAla, s…ôndekorn…õ MARIKI!¬Ľ
\v 22 K…Ē Yosuwe oloku afum: ¬ęN…ôwos…õ k…ôy…Ēn…õ sede sa nt…õ n…ôloku m…Ē ba? Ant…ôŇčn…õ oŇč a MARIKI k…Ē n…ônde n…ôckorn…õ!¬Ľ K…Ē afum Ňčaloku: ¬ęAt…ôŇčn…õ a ti Ňč…Ē s…ôy…Ēn…õ!¬Ľ
\v 23 K…Ē Yosuwe oloku: ¬ęAwa, n…ôsak canu c…ôcuru nc…õ c…ôyi nu dac…Ē m…Ē, n…ôc…ôm…õ MARIKI Kanu ka Yisrayel dar…ôŇč k…Ē ab…ôk…ôc Ňčosoku p…õs!¬Ľ
\p 
\v 24 K…Ē afum Ňčaloku Yosuwe: ¬ęS…ôndekorn…õ MARIKI Kanu kosu, Ki k…Ē s…ôndec…ôŇčk…ôl!¬Ľ
\p 
\v 25 D…Ēs…Ēk dad…Ēk…Ē d…ôndo S…õk…õm k…Ē Yosuwe encic…ôs mes ma danapa nd…õ Ňčasek m…Ē, k'…Ēl…Ēm…ôr afum a Yisrayel tiŇč tiŇč tiŇč m…õfaŇč f…ôp k…Ē sariy…õ ns…õ Kanu k…ônaboc…ôr k…Ē m…Ē.
\v 26 K…Ē Yosuwe encic…ôs moloku mm…õ d…ôbuk ba sariy…õ sa Kanu. K'…õl…õk tasar t…Ēp…ĒŇč k'…õnc…ômb…ôr pi k…ôt…Ēk tant…Ēf nde aŇčgbancan Ňča Kanu.
\v 27 K…Ē Yosuwe oloku afum f…ôp: ¬ęN…ôgb…ôtn…õ pi, tasar pamp…õ peyi su dac…Ē, bawo pi p…õt…ôŇčn…õ moloku mm…õ MARIKI k…ônaloku su m…Ē f…ôp. Sede s…Ē p…Ēy…Ēn…õ k…Ē n…ôlukus Kanu dar…ôŇč-…õ.
\v 28 Nt…õ Yosuwe elip k…ôloku m…Ē k'…õsak afum k…ôk…Ē, k…Ē f…ôp f…ôlukus nde ant…Ēf Ňča k…õ Ňč…Ēn.
\s1 Defi da Yosuwe
\p 
\v 29 Nt…õ mes mam…Ēk…Ē mencep…ôr m…Ē, Yosuwe wan ka Nun w…ôcar w…ôka MARIKI efi. Meren m…Ēn m…õnak…Ē tasar tin k…Ē w…ôco (110).
\v 30 Anawup k…Ē nde ant…Ēf Ňča k…õ k…Ēn, nde Timnat-Sera nde m…Ēr…Ē ma Efrayim, k…ôca k…ômeriya ka T…Ēr…Ē ta Kahas.
\v 31 Aka Yisrayel Ňčanckorn…õ MARIKI mata ma Yosuwe f…ôp, haŇč k…Ē abeki aŇč…õ Ňčanasol k…Ē Yosuwe m…Ē Ňčalip k…ôfi. Abeki aŇč…õ Ňčanat…ôŇčn…õ mes f…ôp mm…õ MARIKI k…ônay…Ēn…õ aka Yisrayel m…Ē.
\p 
\v 32 B…õnt ya Isifu ny…õ aka Yisrayel Ňčanak…õr…õ k…ôy…õf…õ Misira m…Ē, anawup yi nde S…õk…õm nde dal…õ nd…õ Yakuba …õnaway…ôr awut a Ham…Ēr papa w…ôka S…õk…õm m…õnc…ômb…ôl ma gbeti tasar tin (100). It…Ē dal…õ dand…õ d…õnay…Ēn…õ k…õ ka kusuŇčka ka Isifu.
\p 
\v 33 K…Ē Elasar wan w…ôka Aruna efi, k'awup k…Ē nde Kibeya nde m…Ēr…Ē ma Efrayim, ant…Ēf nŇč…õ anas…ĒŇč wan k…Ēn Pinahas m…Ē.
